\id JER - Biblica® Open Luganda Contemporary Bible 2014 
\h Yeremiya 
\toc1 Yeremiya 
\toc2 Yeremiya 
\toc3 Yer 
\mt2 Ekitabo Ekiyitibwa 
\mt1 Yeremiya 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Ebigambo ebyayogerwa Yeremiya, mutabani wa Kirukiya, ow’oku bakabona abaali mu Anasosi mu nsi ya Benyamini.  
\v 2 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda yayogera naye mu mirembe gya Yosiya, kabaka wa Yuda, mutabani wa Amoni, nga yakafugira emyaka kkumi n’esatu,  
\v 3 ne mu biro bya Yekoyakimu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda, okutuusa mu mwezi ogwokutaano, ogw’omwaka ogw’ekkumi n’ogumu ogw’obufuzi bwa Zeddekiya mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda, abantu b’e Yerusaalemi lwe baatwalibwa mu buwaŋŋanguse. 
\s1 Okuyitibwa kwa Yeremiya 
\p  
\v 4 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ne kinzijira, ng’agamba nti, 
\q1  
\v 5 “Nakumanya bwe nnali sinnakubumba mu lubuto lwa maama wo; 
\q2 nga tonnava mu lubuto n’akutukuza. 
\q2 Nakulonda okubeera nnabbi eri amawanga.” 
\p  
\v 6 Ne ndyoka ŋŋamba nti, “Laba nno, \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda! Simanyi kwogera mu bantu, ndi mwana muto.”  
\v 7 Naye \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda n’aŋŋamba nti, “Toyogera nti, ‘Ndi mwana bwana;’ kubanga yonna gye nnaakutumanga gy’onoogendanga, era byonna bye nnaakulagiranga by’onooyogeranga.  
\v 8 Tobatyanga, kubanga nze ndi naawe okukuwonya,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\p  
\v 9 Awo \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda n’agolola omukono gwe, n’akwata ku mimwa gyange, n’aŋŋamba, nti, “Wuliriza. Nkuwa ebigambo by’onooyogeranga.  
\v 10 Leero nkutaddewo okuba n’obuyinza ku mawanga era ne ku bwakabaka. Okusimbula n’okumenya, okuzikiriza n’okuwamba; okuzimba n’okusimba.”  
\v 11 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ate ne kinzijira nga kigamba nti, “Yeremiya kiki ekyo ky’olaba?” 
\p Ne ŋŋamba nti, “Ndaba ettabi ly’omuti ogw’omulozi.” 
\p  
\v 12 Awo \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda n’aŋŋamba nti, “Olabye bulungi, kubanga neetegereza ndabe ng’ekigambo kyange kituukirira.” 
\p  
\v 13 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ne kinzijjira nate nti, “Kiki ky’olaba, kaakano?” 
\p Ne ŋŋamba nti, “Ndaba ensuwa ey’amazzi ageesera, ng’etunudde waggulu mu bukiikakkono.” 
\p  
\v 14 Awo \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda n’aŋŋamba nti, “Okuzikirira kujja kubaawo nga kutandikira mu bukiikakkono kutuuke ku bantu bonna abali mu ggwanga.  
\v 15 Kubanga laba nnaatera okuyita abantu bonna ab’omu bwakabaka obuli mu bukiikakkono,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1 Bakabaka baabwe balyoke bajje bateeke entebe zaabwe ez’obwakabaka 
\q2 mu miryango egiyingira ekibuga Yerusaalemi, 
\q1 balizinda bbugwe waakyo yenna 
\q2 era bazinde n’ebibuga byonna ebya Yuda. 
\q1  
\v 16 Era ndibonereza abantu bange olw’ebibi byabwe byonna, 
\q2 kubanga banvaako ne booteeza obubaane eri bakatonda abalala, 
\q1 era ne basinza ebibajje bye beekolera 
\q2 n’emikono gyabwe. 
\p  
\v 17 “Naye ggwe weetegeke! Yimirira obabuulire byonna bye nkulagira. Tobatya kubanga bw’onoobatya nzija kubakutiisa.  
\v 18 Kubanga leero nze nkufudde ekibuga ekiriko enkomera ez’amaanyi, era empagi ey’ekyuma, era bbugwe ow’ekikomo eri ensi yonna, eri bakabaka ba Yuda, eri abakungu baayo, ne bakabona n’abantu ab’omu nsi.  
\v 19 Balirwana naawe naye tebalikuwangula; kubanga nze ndi wamu naawe okukununula,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\c 2  
\s1 Isirayiri eva ku Katonda 
\p  
\v 1 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ne kinzijira nga kigamba nti,  
\v 2 “Genda olangirire nga Yerusaalemi ewulira nti: 
\b  
\p “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Nzijukira okwewaayo kwe weewaayo ng’okyali muto, 
\q2 engeri gye wanjagalamu nga twakafumbiriganwa, 
\q1 wangoberera mu ddungu 
\q2 mu nsi etali nnime. 
\q1  
\v 3 Isirayiri wali mutukuvu wa \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 ebibala ebibereberye ebyamakungula ge; 
\q1 bonna abaakulyangako nga bazzizza omusango, 
\q2 akabi nga kabatuukako,’ ” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Muwulirize ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* mwe ezzadde lya Yakobo, 
\q2 era n’ab’enju zonna ez’ebika eby’omu Isirayiri. 
\p  
\v 5 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 Kibi ki bakitammwe kye bansangamu ne banvaako 
\q2 ne bagenda ewala ennyo bwe batyo? 
\q1 Baagoberera ebifaananyi bya bakatonda abakole n’emikono ebitaliimu 
\q2 nabo bennyini ne bafuuka ebitaliimu. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ne batagamba nako nti; “Ali ludda wa \nd Mukama\nd* eyatuggya mu nsi y’e Misiri; 
\q2 eyatuyisa mu lukoola, 
\q1 mu nsi ey’amalungu n’obunnya, mu nsi enkalu n’ekisiikirize eky’okufa, 
\q2 mu nsi omutali muntu n’omu, so n’omuntu yenna mw’atayinza kuyita?” 
\q1  
\v 7 Ne mbaleeta mu nsi engimu, 
\q2 mulye ebibala byamu n’ebintu ebirungi. 
\q1 Naye bwe mwajja ne mwonoona ensi yange, 
\q2 ne mufuula omugabo gwange ekivume. 
\q1  
\v 8 Bakabona ne batabuuzaako nti, “\nd Mukama\nd* ali ludda wa?” 
\q2 Abo abakola ku mateeka tebammanya. 
\q1 Abakulembeze ne banjeemera. 
\q2 Bannabbi nga baweereza ku lwa Baali, ne bagoberera ebitagasa. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 “Kyenva nnyongera okubalumiriza,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 “Era ndirumiriza n’abaana b’abaana bammwe. 
\q1  
\v 10 Muwunguke ennyanja mugende ku bizinga bya Kittimu mulabe; 
\q2 era mutume e Kedali, mwetegereze. 
\q2 Mujja kulaba nga tekibangawo. 
\q1  
\v 11 Waali wabaddewo eggwanga erikyusa bakatonda baalyo, 
\q2 wadde nga si bakatonda, naye nga bitaliimu? 
\q1 Naye abantu bange baawaanyisa ekitiibwa kyabwe 
\q2 n’ebitagasa. 
\q1  
\v 12 Wewuunye ggwe eggulu, 
\q2 era okankane n’entiisa ey’amaanyi,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 13 “Kubanga abantu bange bakoze ebibi bibiri, 
\q1 banvuddeko 
\q2 nze ensulo ey’amazzi amalamu 
\q1 ne beesimira ettanka ez’omu ttaka, 
\q2 ettanka ez’omu ttaka ezirimu enjatika ezitanyweeramu mazzi.” 
\s1 Ebyava mu Kubula kwa Isirayiri 
\q1  
\v 14 “Isirayiri muddu, omuddu omuzaale? 
\q2 Kale lwaki afuuse omuyiggo? 
\q1  
\v 15 Bamuwulugumirako ng’empologoma bw’ewuluguma, 
\q2 abalabe bawulugumye nnyo. 
\q1 Ensi ye efuuse matongo, 
\q2 ebibuga bye bigyiridde ddala omuliro birekeddwa ttayo, nga temukyali muntu n’omu. 
\q1  
\v 16 Ate era abasajja b’e Noofu n’e Tapeneesi 
\q2 bamaliddewo ddala ekitiibwa kyo. 
\q1  
\v 17 Si ggwe weeretedde bino ng’ova ku \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo, 
\q2 eyakukulemberanga 
\q2 akulage ekkubo? 
\q1  
\v 18 Kaakano olowooza onooganyulwamu ki 
\q2 okugenda okukolagana ne Misiri? 
\q1 Olowooza kiki ky’onoganyulwa 
\q2 bw’onogenda okukolagana ne Bwasuli? 
\q1  
\v 19 Ebibi byo byennyini bye biri kubonereza, 
\q2 n’okudda kwo emabega kwe kulikusalira omusango. 
\q1 Kale lowooza era otegeere nga bwe kiri ekibi era eky’omutawaana gy’oli bw’ova ku \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo, 
\q2 n’oba nga tokyantya,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda ow’eggye. 
\s1 Isirayiri Ebonerezebwa olw’Okusinza Bakatonda Abalala 
\p  
\v 20 \nd Mukama\nd* ow’eggye agamba nti, 
\q1 “Isirayiri, ebbanga ddene eriyiseewo bukya weggya mu buyinza bwange, 
\q2 n’ogamba nti, ‘Sijja kukugondera.’ 
\q1 Era ddala, ku buli kasozi era na buli wansi w’omuti oguyimiridde 
\q2 wakuba obwamalaaya 
\q2 ng’ovuunamira bakatonda abalala. 
\q1  
\v 21 Songa nnali nkusimbye ng’oli muzabbibu omulungi, 
\q2 ensigo eteriimu kikyamu n’akatono, 
\q1 naye ate lwaki oyonoonese 
\q2 n’ofuuka ng’omuzabbibu ogw’omu nsiko? 
\q1  
\v 22 Kubanga ne bw’onaaba n’oluvu n’okozesa ne sabbuuni omungi, 
\q2 naye era ebbala lyo n’obutali butuukirivu bwo 
\q2 bisigala bikyalabika,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 23 Oyinza otya okugamba nti, “Sseeyonoonanga, 
\q2 sigobereranga ba Baali?” 
\q1 Jjukira bwe weeyisa ng’oli mu kiwonvu; 
\q2 tegeera kye wakola. 
\q1 Oli ng’eŋŋamira enkazi efuumuuka embiro 
\q2 ngeraga eno n’eri, 
\q1  
\v 24 ng’endogoyi ey’omu nsiko 
\q2 eddukira mu ddungu mw’emanyidde, 
\q1 ng’ewunyiriza mu bbanga eno n’eri mu kwaka kwayo, 
\q2 mu kiseera ekyo ani ayinza okugiziyiza? 
\q1 Ensajja zonna ezigyetaaga tezeetaaga kwekooya; 
\q2 mu biseera by’okulabaganiramu za kugifuna. 
\q1  
\v 25 Tokooya bigere byo, 
\q2 era tokaza mimiro gyo. 
\q1 Naye n’oddamu nti, “Ebyo bya bwereere, 
\q2 sisobola kukyuka, nayagala bakatonda abalala, 
\q2 nteekwa okubanoonya.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 Ng’omubbi bw’aswala ng’akwatiddwa, 
\q2 n’ennyumba ya Isirayiri bw’eswala bw’etyo, 
\q1 bakabaka baayo, n’abalangira baayo, ne bakabona baayo, 
\q2 era ne bannabbi baayo, 
\q1  
\v 27 nga bagamba emiti nti, “Ggwe kitange,” 
\q2 era n’ejjinja nti, “Ggwe wanzaala.” 
\q1 Bankubye amabega, 
\q2 naye bwe balaba ennaku bankaabirira nti, “Yimuka ojje otulokole.” 
\q1  
\v 28 Kale bakatonda be weekolera baluwa? 
\q2 Leka bajje, bwe baba basobola okukulokola mu biseera eby’emitawaana. 
\q1 Kubanga obungi bwa bakatonda bammwe 
\q2 bwenkanankana n’ebibuga byo ggwe Yuda. 
\s1 Okubonerezebwa Kutuuse 
\q1  
\v 29 “Lwaki munneemulugunyiza? 
\q2 Mwenna mwanneeddiimira,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 30 Abaana bammwe nababonereza naye nga bwerere, 
\q2 tebakkiriza kugololwa. 
\q1 Mmwe bennyini ne mwettira bannabbi bammwe 
\q2 ng’empologoma bw’etta. 
\p  
\v 31 Mmwe ab’omulembe guno muwulirize ekigambo kya Katonda. 
\q1 Mbadde nga ddungu gye muli 
\q2 ng’ensi ejjudde ekizikiza eky’amaanyi? 
\q1 Kale lwaki abantu bange bagamba nti, 
\q2 “Tulina eddembe, tetukyadda gy’oli?” 
\q1  
\v 32 Omuwala omuto ayinza okwerabira ebikomo, 
\q2 oba omugole okwerabira ekyambalo kye? 
\q1 Naye ng’ate abantu bange 
\q2 Bannerabidde! 
\q1  
\v 33 Ng’omanyi nnyo okukuba amakubo ag’okunoonya abanaakwagala! 
\q2 N’asembayo okuba omukugu mu bamalaaya aba alina kuyigira ku ggwe. 
\q1  
\v 34 Engoye zo zijjudde omusaayi gw’abaavu 
\q2 n’abatalina musango, 
\q1 awatali kugamba nti 
\q2 bakwatibwa nga babba. 
\q1 Ate nga wadde byonna biri bwe bityo 
\q2  
\v 35 ogamba nti, “Sirina musango, 
\q2 ddala takyanninako busungu!” 
\q1 Laba, ŋŋenda kukusalira omusango 
\q2 olw’okugamba nti, “Sirina kibi kye nkoze.” 
\q1  
\v 36 Lwaki ogenda ng’okyusakyusa 
\q2 amakubo go! 
\q1 Misiri ejja kukuswaza 
\q2 nga Bwasuli bwe yakuswaza. 
\q1  
\v 37 Era n’eyo olivaayo 
\q2 ng’emikono ogyetisse ku mutwe, 
\q1 kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* agaanye abo be weesiga; 
\q2 tagenda kukuyamba. 
\c 3  
\s1 Yuda Omukazi Atali Mwesigwa 
\q1  
\v 1 “Omusajja bw’agoba mukazi we, 
\q2 omukazi oyo n’agenda n’afuuka ow’omusajja omulala, 
\q1 omusajja we alimukomyawo nate? 
\q2 Ensi eba teyonoonekedde ddala nnyo? 
\q1 Naye obadde nga malaaya, ng’olina abasajja bangi; 
\q2 naye kaakano oyagala okukomawo gye ndi?” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 2 Yimusa amaaso go olabe ku ntikko y’obusozi. 
\q2 Waliwo ekifo we bateebakira naawe? 
\q1 Ku mabbali g’ekkubo we watulanga 
\q2 n’olinda abasajja ng’oli nga Omuwalabu mu ddungu; 
\q1 n’olyoka oyonoona ensi 
\q2 n’obwenzi bwo n’ekibi kyo. 
\q1  
\v 3 Noolwekyo enkuba kyevudde eziyizibwa, 
\q2 n’enkuba eya ttoggo n’etetonnya. 
\q1 Naye era otemya nga malaaya 
\q2 tokwatibwa nsonyi. 
\q1  
\v 4 Tewakaŋŋamba nti Kitange ggwe mukwano gwange 
\q2 okuva mu buto bwange, 
\q1  
\v 5 onoonyiigira ddala emirembe gyonna, 
\q2 olisunguwala emirembe gyonna? 
\q1 Bw’otyo bw’oyogera, 
\q2 naye okoze ebibi byonna ebisoboka. 
\s1 Isirayiri, Atali Mwesigwa 
\p  
\v 6 Mu nnaku z’obufuzi bwa kabaka Yosiya \nd Mukama\nd* yayogera nange n’aŋŋamba nti, “Olabye Isirayiri etali neesigwa ky’ekoze? Agenze ku buli kasozi na buli wansi w’omuti oguyimiridde ne yeeyisa ng’omukazi omwenzi.  
\v 7 Nalowooza nti, Bw’alimala okukola bino byonna agenda kudda gye ndi naye teyadda, era muganda we atali mwesigwa Yuda n’akiraba.  
\v 8 Yalaba nti bwe namala okugoba Isirayiri eyanvaako, ne muwa n’ebbaluwa ey’okumugoba olw’obwenzi bwe. Naye ate ne ndaba muganda we atali mwesigwa Yuda nga taliimu kutya, naye n’agenda n’akola obwenzi.  
\v 9 Awo obwenzi bwe bwatuuka ne bumwanguyira nnyo n’ayenda n’asinza amayinja n’ebikonge.  
\v 10 Naye wadde nga byonna bimaze okubaawo, muganda we Yuda atali mwesigwa, teyakomawo gye ndi na mutima gwe gwonna, naye yali alimbalimba,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 11 \nd Mukama\nd* n’aŋŋamba nti, Isirayiri asudde obwesigwa, mutukuvu okusinga Yuda atali mwesigwa.  
\v 12 Genda obuulire abantu b’omu bukiikakkono obubaka buno, obagambe nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Komawo ggwe Isirayiri, 
\q2 eyanvaako,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 ‘Siribatunuuliza busungu kubanga ndi waakisa,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*; 
\q2 ‘Sirisiba busungu ku mwoyo emirembe gyonna. 
\q1  
\v 13 Mukkirize bukkiriza ekibi kyammwe, 
\q2 mwajeemera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wammwe, 
\q1 mwasinza bakatonda abalala, 
\q2 wansi wa buli muti oguyimiridde, 
\q2 era ne mutaŋŋondera,’ ” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 14 “Mukomeewo mmwe abaana abanvaako,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*; “kubanga nze bbammwe, era ndibalondamu omu ku omu okuva mu buli kibuga, babiri babiri okuva mu buli kika mbaleete ku lusozi Sayuuni.  
\v 15 Era ndibawa abasumba abakola ng’omutima gwange bwe gwagala, abalibakulembera mu kumanya era ne mu kutegeera.  
\v 16 Ennaku bwe zirituuka nga mwaze era nga muli bangi nnyo mu nsi,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, “abantu baliba tebakyayogera ku Ssanduuko y’Endagaano. Baliba tebakyagirowooza nako, okugijjukira; oba okulumwa emitima olw’obutaba nayo wadde okukola endala.  
\v 17 Ebbanga lyonna Yerusaalemi kiriyitibwa Entebe ya \nd Mukama\nd* ey’Obwakabaka, amawanga gonna mwe ganaakuŋŋaaniranga okumugulumiza \nd Mukama\nd* mu Yerusaalemi era tebaliddayo kugoberera mitima gyabwe minyoomi.  
\v 18 Mu nnaku ezo ennyumba ya Yuda eryegatta ku nnyumba ya Isirayiri, era bombi awamu baliva mu nsi ey’omu bukiikakkono ne bajja mu nsi gye ndiwa bakitammwe okuba omugabo. 
\p  
\v 19 “Nze kennyini nalowooza 
\q1 “nga nayagala okubayisanga nga batabani bange, 
\q2 era mbawe ensi eyeegombebwa, 
\q2 nga gwe mugabo ogusinga obulungi mu mawanga gonna. 
\q1 Nalowooza nti mulimpita ‘Kitammwe,’ 
\q2 ne mutanvaako ne mwongera okungoberera. 
\q1  
\v 20 Naye ng’omukazi atali mwesigwa eri bba bw’abeera, 
\q2 bwe mutyo bwe mutabadde beesigwa gye ndi, mmwe ennyumba ya Isirayiri,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\s1 Okuyitibwa Okwenenya 
\q1  
\v 21 Okukaaba kw’Abaana ba Isirayiri 
\q2 kuwuliddwa ku ntikko z’ensozi ezitaliiko kantu, 
\q1 nga bakaaba n’okwegayirira, kubanga baatambulira mu kukola ebibi, 
\q2 ne beerabira \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 22 “Mukomeewo mmwe abantu abatali beesigwa, 
\q2 nnaabawonya ne mbafuula abeesigwa.” 
\q1 Ne mugamba nti, “Weewaawo tujja kudda gy’oli, 
\q2 kubanga ggwe \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe. 
\q1  
\v 23 Ddala okusuubira obuyambi okuva mu nsozi gye twasinzizanga bakatonda abalala 
\q2 temuli kantu. 
\q1 Ddala mu \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe 
\q2 mwe muli obulokozi bwa Isirayiri. 
\q1  
\v 24 Naye okuva mu buto bwaffe 
\q2 bakatonda abo abalala abatagasa balidde ne bamalawo ebibala 
\q1 bakitaffe bye baamalirako amaanyi gaabwe, embuzi zaabwe, n’ente zaabwe, 
\q2 batabani baabwe ne bawala baabwe. 
\q1  
\v 25 Leka tugalamire, ng’ensonyi zitutta, n’obuswavu bwaffe butuyitiridde 
\q2 kubanga twonoonye eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe, ffe ne bakadde baffe, 
\q1 okuva mu buto bwaffe n’okutuusa ku lunaku luno; 
\q2 kubanga tetugondedde ddoboozi lya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe.” 
\c 4  
\q1  
\v 1 “Bw’oba odda, ggwe Isirayiri,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 “eri nze gy’olina okudda. 
\q1 Bw’oneggyako eby’omuzizo byonna 
\q2 n’otosagaasagana, 
\q1  
\v 2 era singa olayira mu mazima, mu bwenkanya 
\q2 era mu ngeri entuufu yennyini nti, ‘Ddala nga \nd Mukama\nd* bw’ali omulamu,’ 
\q1 olwo amawanga gonna mu ye mwe gajja okuweerwa omukisa 
\q2 era mu ye mwe ganeenyumiririzanga.” 
\p  
\v 3 Kubanga bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* eri abantu ba Yuda era n’eri abantu b’omu Yerusaalemi nti, 
\q1 “Mulime ennimiro zammwe ezitali nnime, 
\q2 temusiga mu maggwa. 
\q1  
\v 4 Mukoowoole \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 mweweeyo mutukuze emitima gyammwe 
\q2 mwe abantu ba Yuda ne Yerusaalemi, 
\q1 obusungu bwange buleme okubuubuuka ng’omuliro, olw’ebikolwa byammwe ebibi, 
\q2 ne wataba ayinza kubuzikiza.” 
\s1 Yuda Erumbibwa 
\q1  
\v 5 “Kirangirire mu Yuda 
\q2 era okitegeeze mu Yerusaalemi ogambe nti, 
\q1 ‘Mufuuwe ekkondeere mu nsi yonna! 
\q2 Mulangirire nga mugamba nti, Mukuŋŋaane, 
\q2 tuddukire mu bibuga ebiriko ebigo!’ 
\q1  
\v 6 Weereza obubaka eri Sayuuni nti, 
\q2 Mudduke temulwa, 
\q1 kubanga ndireeta okuzikiriza okuva mu bukiikakkono, 
\q2 okuzikiriza okw’amaanyi.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Empologoma evudde mu kisaka kyayo, 
\q2 omuzikiriza w’amawanga afulumye gy’abeera, azze okumalawo ensi yo. 
\q1 Ebibuga byammwe bijja kuzikirizibwa 
\q2 bibuleko abibeeramu. 
\q1  
\v 8 Noolwekyo mwambale ebibukutu mukungubage, 
\q2 mukube ebiwoobe 
\q1 kubanga obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* obw’amaanyi tebutuvuddeeko. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 \nd Mukama\nd* n’agamba nti, “Ku lunaku olwo, 
\q2 kabaka n’omukungu baliggwaamu omwoyo, 
\q1 bakabona basamaalirire 
\q2 ne bannabbi beewuunye.” 
\p  
\v 10 Ne ndyoka ŋŋamba nti, “Woowe \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, mazima olimbidde ddala abantu bano ne Yerusaalemi ng’ogamba nti, ‘Mulibeera n’emirembe,’ ate nga ekitala kiri ddala ku mimiro gyaffe.” 
\p  
\v 11 Mu biseera ebyo abantu bano ne Yerusaalemi balibuulirwa nti, “Embuyaga ezookya eziva ku nsozi ezaakala ez’omu ddungu zifuuwa abantu bange nga teziwujja buwuzzi wadde okulongoosa obulongoosa  
\v 12 embuyaga ezisingako awo ze ziriva gye ndi. Era kaakano mbasalira emisango.” 
\q1  
\v 13 Laba ajja ng’ebire, 
\q2 amagaali ge ng’empewo y’akazimu, 
\q1 embalaasi ze zidduka okusinga empungu; 
\q2 zitusanze ffe kubanga tuzikiridde! 
\q1  
\v 14 Ayi Yerusaalemi, naaza omutima gwo guve mu kukola ebibi olyoke olokolebwe. 
\q2 Olikomya ddi ebirowoozo ebibi? 
\q1  
\v 15 Eddoboozi lyawulirwa okuva mu Ddaani, 
\q2 nga lirangirira okuzikirizibwa okuva mu nsozi za Efulayimu. 
\q1  
\v 16 “Labula amawanga nti ajja: 
\q2 kirangirirwe mu Yerusaalemi nti, 
\q1 ‘Abalabe bajja okuva mu nsi ey’ewala nga bayimba ennyimba ez’entalo 
\q2 nga balumba ebibuga bya Yuda. 
\q1  
\v 17 Bakyetoolodde ng’abasajja abakuuma ennimiro 
\q2 kubanga Yuda yanjeemera,’ ” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 18 “Empisa zammwe, 
\q2 n’ebikolwa byammwe bye bibaleeseeko bino. 
\q1 Kino kye kibonerezo kyammwe. 
\q2 Nga kya bulumi! 
\q2 Nga kifumita omutima.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Obulumi, Ayi Obulumi! 
\q2 Neenyoolera mu bulumi! 
\q1 Ayi obulumi bw’omutima gwange! 
\q2 Omutima gunkubagana munda, sisobola kusirika, 
\q1 kubanga mpulidde eddoboozi ly’ekkondeere, 
\q2 mpulidde enduulu z’olutalo. 
\q1  
\v 20 Okuzikirizibwa kweyongeddeko 
\q2 era ensi yonna eyonooneddwa. 
\q1 Eweema zange zisaanyiziddwawo mu kaseera buseera, 
\q2 n’entimbe zange nga kutemya kikowe. 
\q1  
\v 21 Ndituusa ddi nga ndaba bbendera z’olutalo 
\q2 n’okuwulira amaloboozi g’amakondeere? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 22 “Kubanga abantu bange basirusiru, 
\q2 tebammanyi. 
\q1 Baana abatalina magezi; 
\q2 abatategeera. 
\q1 Bakagezimunnyu mu kukola ebibi, 
\q2 tebamanyi kukola birungi.” 
\q1  
\v 23 Natunuulira ensi, 
\q2 nga njereere, 
\q1 ate ne ntunula ne ku ggulu, 
\q2 ng’ekitangaala kigenze. 
\q1  
\v 24 Natunuulira agasozi 
\q2 nga gajugumira, 
\q2 n’ensozi zonna zaali ziyuuguuma. 
\q1  
\v 25 Natunula, era laba, waali tewasigadde muntu n’omu, 
\q2 era n’ebinyonyi byonna eby’omu bbanga byali bidduse. 
\q1  
\v 26 Natunula, era laba, ensi ey’ebibala ebingi ng’efuuse ddungu, 
\q2 era n’ebibuga byayo byonna nga byonoonese, mu maaso ga \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 olw’obusungu bwe obungi. 
\p  
\v 27 Kubanga bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Ensi yonna eriyonoonebwa, 
\q2 wadde nga sirigizikiririza ddala. 
\q1  
\v 28 Noolwekyo ensi erikungubaga 
\q2 era n’eggulu waggulu lirikwata ekizikiza, 
\q1 kubanga njogedde 
\q2 era maliridde sijja kwejjusa wadde okukyusaamu.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 29 Olw’okuyoogona kw’abeebagazi b’embalaasi n’abalasa obusaale, 
\q2 ebibuga byonna biribuna emiwabo, 
\q1 abamu beesogge ebisaka; 
\q2 n’abalala balinnye waggulu ku njazi. 
\q1 Ebibuga byonna birekeddwa ttayo; 
\q2 tewali abibeeramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 30 Okola ki ggwe, 
\q2 ggwe eyayonoonebwa? 
\q2 Lwaki oyambala engoye entwakaavu, 
\q1 ne weeteekako eby’obugagga ebya zaabu, 
\q2 n’amaaso n’ogasiiga langi? 
\q1 Omala biseera nga weeyonja. 
\q2 Baganzi bo bakunyoomoola; era baagala kukutta. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 31 Mpulira okukaaba ng’okw’omukazi alumwa okuzaala, 
\q2 okusinda ng’okw’oyo asindika omwana we asooka, 
\q1 okukaaba kw’omuwala wa Sayuuni ng’awejjawejja anoonya w’anassiza omukka, 
\q2 ng’agolola emikono gye ng’agamba nti, 
\q1 “Zinsanze nze, nzirika. 
\q2 Obulamu bwange buweereddwayo mu batemu.” 
\c 5  
\s1 Tewali n’Omu Mugolokofu 
\q1  
\v 1 “Dduka ogende eno n’eri mu nguudo za Yerusaalemi, 
\q2 tunulatunula olabe, 
\q2 noonya wonna we bakuŋŋaanira, 
\q1 bw’onoosanga omuntu omu bw’ati 
\q2 omwesimbu ow’amazima, 
\q2 nnaasonyiwa ekibuga kino. 
\q1  
\v 2 Ne bwe boogera nti, ‘Nga \nd Mukama\nd* bwali omulamu;’ 
\q2 baba balayirira bwereere.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, amaaso go teganoonya mazima? 
\q2 Wabakuba naye ne batawulira bulumi wababetenta, 
\q2 naye ne bagaana okukangavvulwa. 
\q1 Beeyongedde kukakanyala, bagubye obwenyi okusinga n’amayinja; 
\q2 era bagaanyi okwenenya. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ne njogera nti, 
\q2 “Bano baavu abasirusiru. 
\q1 Kubanga tebamanyi kkubo lya \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 amateeka ga Katonda waabwe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kale ndigenda eri abakulembeze 
\q2 njogere nabo; 
\q1 Kubanga bamanyi ekkubo lya \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 amateeka ga Katonda waabwe.” 
\q1 Naye nabo bwe batyo baali baamenya dda ekikoligo 
\q2 nga baakutula ebisiba. 
\q1  
\v 6 Noolwekyo empologoma eriva mu kibira n’ebalya, 
\q2 n’omusege ogw’omu ddungu gulibasaanyaawo. 
\q1 Engo erikuumira okumpi n’ebibuga byabwe, 
\q2 buli muntu abifuluma ayuzibweyuzibwe; 
\q1 Kubanga ebibi byabwe bingi, 
\q2 okudda ennyuma kunene. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 “Mbasonyiwe ntya? 
\q2 Abaana bammwe banvuddeko, 
\q2 ne balayiririra bakatonda abatali bakatonda. 
\q1 Bwe nabaliisa ne bakkuta, badda mu kwenda, 
\q2 ne beekuŋŋaanya ku nnyumba z’abenzi. 
\q1  
\v 8 Baali ng’embalaasi ennume ezikkuse ezitaamye, 
\q2 buli muntu ng’akaayanira muka munne. 
\q1  
\v 9 Lwaki sibabonereza olw’ebintu ebyo? 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q1 Lwaki siwoolera ggwanga ku nsi 
\q2 efaanana bw’etyo?” 
\s1 Ekiragiro ky’Okulumba Yuda 
\q1  
\v 10 “Yita mu nnimiro z’emizabbibu gyabwe ogyonooneyonoone, 
\q2 naye togimalirawo ddala. 
\q1 Giggyeeko amatabi gaagyo, 
\q2 kubanga si bantu ba \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 11 Kubanga ennyumba ya Isirayiri n’ennyumba ya Yuda 
\q2 zifuukidde ddala njeemu gye ndi,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Boogedde eby’obulimba ku \nd Mukama\nd* ne bagamba nti, 
\q2 “Talina kyajja kukola, 
\q1 tewali kabi kanaatugwako, 
\q2 era tetujja kulaba wadde kitala oba kyeya. 
\q1  
\v 13 Bannabbi mpewo buwewo 
\q2 era ekigambo tekibaliimu; 
\q2 noolwekyo leka kye boogera kikolebwe ku bo.” 
\p  
\v 14 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Kubanga abantu boogedde ebigambo bino, 
\q2 ndifuula ekigambo kyange mu kamwa kammwe okuba ng’omuliro, 
\q2 n’abantu bano okuba enku era omuliro gubookye. 
\q1  
\v 15 Laba, mbaleetera eggwanga eriva ewala, 
\q2 ggwe ennyumba ya Isirayiri,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 Ensi eyaguma ey’edda, 
\q2 abantu ab’olulimi lwe mutamanyi 
\q2 aboogera bye mutategeera 
\q1  
\v 16 omufuko gwabwe ogw’obusaale guli ng’entaana eyasaamiridde, 
\q2 bonna balwanyi nnamige. 
\q1  
\v 17 Balirya amakungula gammwe n’emmere yammwe; 
\q2 balirya batabani bammwe era ne bawala bammwe; 
\q1 balye emizabbibu n’emitiini gyammwe, 
\q2 ebibuga byammwe ebiriko bbugwe bye mwesiga birizikirizibwa n’ebitala. 
\p  
\v 18 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Naye ne mu nnaku ezo sigenda kubazikiririza ddala kubamalawo.  
\v 19 Era abantu bammwe bwe bagamba nti, ‘Lwaki Katonda waffe atukoze ebintu bino byonna?’ Onoobagamba nti, ‘Nga bwe mwanvaako ne muweereza bakatonda abalala mu nsi yammwe, mujja kuweereza bakatonda abagwira mu nsi eteri yammwe.’ 
\q1  
\v 20 “Langirira kino mu nnyumba ya Yakobo, 
\q2 kirangirire mu Yuda. 
\q1  
\v 21 Wulira kino, mmwe abantu abasirusiru abatalina kutegeera, 
\q2 abalina amaaso naye nga tebalaba, 
\q2 abalina amatu naye nga tebawulira. 
\q1  
\v 22 Temuntya?” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*; 
\q2 “temunkankanira? 
\q1 Nateeka omusenyu okuba ensalo y’ennyanja, 
\q2 olukomera olutaliggwaawo, lwetasobola kuvvuunuka; 
\q1 wadde ng’amayengo galukubaakuba, tegasobola kuluwaguza, 
\q2 gayinza okuwuluguma, naye tegasobola kuluyitako. 
\q1  
\v 23 Naye abantu bano balina omutima omwewagguze era omujeemu. 
\q2 Bajeemye banvuddeko. 
\q1  
\v 24 Abateekuba mu kifuba kugamba nti, ‘Tutye \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe agaba enkuba, 
\q1 eya ddumbi n’eya ttoggo, 
\q2 mu ntuuko zaayo; 
\q2 atugerekera ssabbiiti ez’okukunguliramu.’ ” 
\q1  
\v 25 Obutali butuukirivu bwammwe bubibakwese 
\q2 ebibi byammwe bibaggyeeko ebirungi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 “Kubanga abasajja abakozi b’ebibi basangibwa mu bantu bange; 
\q2 abagalamira ne balindirira ng’abasajja abatezi b’obunyonyi. 
\q2 Batega abantu omutego. 
\q1  
\v 27 Ng’ebisero ebijjudde ebinyonyi, 
\q2 enju zaabwe bwe zijjudde eby’enkwe. 
\q1 Noolwekyo bafuuse ab’amaanyi abagagga, 
\q2 ne bagejja era ne banyirira. 
\q1  
\v 28 Ekibi kyabwe tekiriiko kkomo, tebasala misango mu bwenkanya, 
\q2 abatawolereza bataliiko ba kitaabwe okubayamba basinge emisango, 
\q2 era abatafaayo ku ddembe lya bakateeyamba. 
\q1  
\v 29 Lwaki sibabonereza olw’ebintu ebyo?” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 “Nneme okwesasuza ku ggwanga 
\q2 eriri nga eryo? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 30 “Ekigambo eky’ekitalo 
\q2 era eky’ekivve kigudde mu nsi: 
\q1  
\v 31 Bannabbi bawa obunnabbi obw’obulimba, 
\q2 bakabona bafugisa buyinza bwabwe ate abantu bange bwe batyo bwe bakyagala. 
\q1 Naye ku nkomerero 
\q2 munaakola mutya?” 
\c 6  
\s1 Abeesigwa Bagambibwa Okudduka 
\q1  
\v 1 Mwekuŋŋaanye mudduke mmwe abantu ba Benyamini! 
\q2 Mmudduke muve mu Yerusaalemi. 
\q1 Fuuwa ekkondeere mu Tekowa, 
\q2 era yimusa ebbendera mu Besukakkeremu: 
\q1 kubanga akacwano kasinzidde mu bukiikakkono, 
\q2 okuzikirira okw’entiisa. 
\q1  
\v 2 Ndizikiriza omuwala wa Sayuuni, 
\q2 omulungi oyo omubalagavu. 
\q1  
\v 3 Abasumba balimulumba n’ebisibo byabwe. 
\q2 Balimwetoolooza weema zaabwe zimwolekere enjuuyi zonna, 
\q2 buli omu yeezimbire w’ayagala. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 “Mwetegeke mumulwanyise! 
\q2 Muyimuke, tumulumbe mu ttuntu! 
\q1 Naye, nedda, omusana gugenda guggwaayo, 
\q2 n’ebisiikirize by’akawungeezi biwanvuye! 
\q1  
\v 5 Tugende, tulumbe kiro 
\q2 tuzikirize amayumba ge.” 
\p  
\v 6 Bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye bw’agamba nti, 
\q1 “Muteme emiti mukole entuumo 
\q2 muzingize Yerusaalemi. 
\q1 Ekibuga kino kiteekwa okubonerezebwa kyonna, 
\q2 kubanga kijjudde bujoozi bwerere. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ng’oluzzi bwe lukulukusa amazzi, bwe kityo bwe kikulukusa ebibi byakyo, 
\q2 entalo era n’okuzikirira biwulirwa munda waakyo. 
\q1 Obulwadde n’ebiwundu 
\q2 bye ndaba buli bbanga. 
\q1  
\v 8 Nkulabula, 
\q2 ggwe Yerusaalemi, 
\q1 emmeeme yange ereme okwawukana naawe, 
\q2 si kulwa ng’ofuuka amatongo.” 
\p  
\v 9 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Balisusumbulira ddala n’abo abatono 
\q2 abaliba basigaddewo mu Isirayiri. 
\q1 Ddamu oyise omukono mu matabi 
\q2 ng’omunozi we zabbibu bw’akola.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Ndyogera eri ani gwe ndirabula? 
\q2 Ani alimpuliriza? 
\q1 Amatu gaabwe gagaddwa 
\q2 ne batasobola kuwulira. 
\q1 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kiri nga kyakusesa gye bali, 
\q2 tebakisanyukira n’akamu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Kyenva nzijula ekiruyi 
\q2 sikyasobola kukizibiikiriza. 
\b  
\q1 “Kiyiwe ku baana abali mu luguudo, 
\q2 ne ku bavubuka abakuŋŋaanye; 
\q1 abaami awamu n’abakazi n’abakadde 
\q2 abo abawezezza emyaka emingi baliwambibwa. 
\q1  
\v 12 Enju zaabwe 
\q2 ziritwalibwa abalala, 
\q1 n’ennimiro zaabwe awamu ne bakazi baabwe; 
\q2 kubanga ndigolola omukono gwange ku abo abali mu nsi,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 13 “Kubanga okuva ku asembayo wansi okutuusa ku asingayo waggulu, 
\q2 buli omu alulunkanira kufuna. 
\q1 Nnabbi ne kabona bonna 
\q2 boogera eby’obulimba. 
\q1  
\v 14 Ekiwundu ky’abantu bange 
\q2 bakijjanjaba ng’ekitali ky’amaanyi. 
\q1 Boogera nti, ‘Mirembe, mirembe.’ 
\q2 So nga tewali mirembe. 
\q1  
\v 15 Bakwatibwa ensonyi olw’ebikolwa byabwe eby’emizizo? 
\q2 Nedda. 
\q2 Tebakwatibwa nsonyi n’akatono. 
\q1 Noolwekyo baligwira wamu n’abo abaligwa; 
\q2 balisuulibwa wansi bwe ndibabonereza,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 16 Kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba nti, 
\q1 “Yimirira mu masaŋŋanzira otunule. 
\q2 Buuza amakubo ag’edda, buuza ekkubo eddungi gye liri, 
\q1 era otambulire omwo, 
\q2 emmeeme yammwe erifuna ekiwummulo. 
\q2 Naye ne mugamba nti, ‘Tetujja kulitambuliramu.’ 
\q1  
\v 17 Nabateerawo abakuumi babategeeze nti, 
\q2 Muwulirize eddoboozi ly’ekkondeere, 
\q2 naye ne mugamba nti, ‘Tetujja kuwuliriza.’ 
\q1  
\v 18 Kale muwulire, 
\q2 mmwe amawanga 
\q2 era mulabe mmwe ab’ekkuŋŋaaniro ekyo ekiribatuukako. 
\q1  
\v 19 Wuliriza, ggwe ensi: 
\q1 laba, ndeeta akabi ku bantu bano, 
\q2 by’ebibala by’enkwe zaabwe, 
\q1 kubanga tebafuddeeyo ku bigambo byange 
\q2 n’etteeka lyange baligaanye. 
\q1  
\v 20 Omugavu oguva e Seeba bampa gwa ki? 
\q2 Oba zino emmuli ezakaloosa eziva mu nsi ey’ewala? 
\q1 Ebiweebwayo byammwe ebyokebwa sijja kubikkiriza, 
\q2 n’essaddaaka zammwe tezinsanyusa.” 
\p  
\v 21 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Laba nditeeka enkonge mu maaso g’abantu bano; 
\q2 bakitaabwe ne batabani baabwe bonna bazesittaleko. 
\q2 Muliraanwa we ne mukwano gwe balizikirira.” 
\p  
\v 22 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, nti, 
\q1 “Laba, eggye lijja 
\q2 eriva mu nsi ey’omu bukiikakkono, 
\q1 eggwanga ery’amaanyi 
\q2 liyimusibwa okuva ku nkomerero z’ensi. 
\q1  
\v 23 Bakutte omutego n’effumu, 
\q2 abakambwe abatalina kusaasira. 
\q1 Bawulikika ng’ennyanja ewuuma, 
\q2 nga beebagadde embalaasi zaabwe: 
\q1 bajja ng’abalwanyi mu byambalo by’olutalo 
\q2 okulumba ggwe Muwala wa Sayuuni!” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 24 Tuwulidde ettutumu lyabwe; 
\q2 era emikono gyaffe giweddemu amaanyi 
\q1 okulumwa okunene kutukutte 
\q2 n’okulumwa ng’okw’omukazi alumwa okuzaala. 
\q1  
\v 25 Togeza kugenda mu nnimiro 
\q2 newaakubadde okutambulira mu kkubo; 
\q1 kubanga omulabe abunye wonna wonna 
\q2 n’entiisa ejjudde mu bantu. 
\q1  
\v 26 Kale nno mmwe abantu, 
\q2 mwambale ebibukutu era mwevulunge mu vvu; 
\q1 mukungubage ng’abakaabira 
\q2 omwana owoobulenzi omu yekka. 
\q1 Kubanga oyo agenda okuzikiriza 
\q2 ajja kutugwako mavumbavumba. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 27 “Nkufudde ekigezesa 
\q2 abantu bange n’ekyuma, 
\q1 osobole okulaba n’okugezesa 
\q2 amakubo gaabwe. 
\q1  
\v 28 Bonna bakyewaggula 
\q2 abakakanyavu abagenda bawaayiriza, 
\q1 bikomo era kyuma, 
\q2 bonna boonoonefu. 
\q1  
\v 29 Emivubo bagifukuta n’amaanyi, 
\q2 omuliro gumalawo essasi, 
\q1 naye balongoosereza bwereere 
\q2 kubanga ababi tebaggyibwamu. 
\q1  
\v 30 Baliyitibwa masengere ga ffeeza, 
\q2 kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* abalese.” 
\c 7  
\s1 Yeremiya Abuulira mu Yeekaalu 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo ekyajjira Yeremiya okuva eri \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 2 Yimirira ku mulyango gw’ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* otegeeze abantu obubaka buno. 
\p Muwuliriza ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*, mmwe mwenna abantu ba Yuda abayita mu miryango gino okusinza \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 3 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, “Mulongoose amakubo gammwe n’ebikolwa byammwe, nange ndibalekera ekifo kino ne mubeeramu.  
\v 4 Teweesiga bigambo bino ebibuzaabuza ne mwogera nti, ‘Eno ye yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*, yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*, yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*!’  
\v 5 Kubanga bwe munaalongoosezanga ddala amakubo gammwe n’ebikolwa byammwe; era bwe munaalaganga obwenkanya eri omuntu ne munne,  
\v 6 ne mulekayo okunyigiriza omugwira, ne mulekwa, ne nnamwandu, ne mulekayo n’okutta abataliiko musango mu kifo ekyo, era ne mutasinza bakatonda abalala okwereetera emisango mmwe bennyini,  
\v 7 kale ndibatuuza mu kifo ekyo mu nsi gye nawa bajjajjammwe ebeere yammwe emirembe n’emirembe.  
\v 8 Kale laba, mwesiga ebigambo ebitaliimu, ebitagasa. 
\p  
\v 9 “Munabba ne mutta, ne mukola obwenzi ne mulayira eby’obulimba, ne mwoteza obubaane eri Baali, ne mutambula okugoberera bakatonda abalala be mutamanyanga;  
\v 10 ne mulyoka mujja ne muyimirira mu maaso gange mu nnyumba eno, eyitibwa Erinnya lyange, ne mugamba nti, ‘Tuli bulungi, tuli bulungi,’ ne mulyoka mukola eby’emizizo byonna?  
\v 11 Mulowooza nti ennyumba eno eyitibwa ennyumba yange, mpuku y’abanyazi? Laba, nze kennyini nkirabye,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 12 “Mugende kaakano mu kifo kyange ekyali e Siiro ekifo gye nasooka okuteeka essinzizo ly’erinnya lyange, mulabe kye nakikola olw’ekibi ky’abantu bange Isirayiri.  
\v 13 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Bwe mwali mukola ebintu bino byonna, nayogera nammwe emirundi mingi naye ne mutampulira; nabakoowoola ne mutampitaba.  
\v 14 Noolwekyo, ekyo kye nakola e Siiro nzija kukikola kaakano ku nnyumba eyitibwa Erinnya lyange, era gye mwesiga, era n’ebifo bye nabawa mmwe ne bakitammwe.  
\v 15 Ndibagoba ne mu maaso gange, nga bwe nagoba baganda bammwe bonna, ezzadde lya Efulayimu lyonna. 
\p  
\v 16 “Noolwekyo tosabira bantu abo wadde okubegayiririra newaakubadde okubasabira oba okubawolereza, kubanga siikuwulire.  
\v 17 Tolaba bye bakola mu bibuga bya Yuda era ne mu nguudo za Yerusaalemi?  
\v 18 Abaana balonda enku, bakitaabwe ne bakuma omuliro, olwo abakazi ne bakanda eŋŋaano ne bakolera kabaka w’eggulu omukazi emigaati. Bafuka ekiweebwayo ekyokunywa eri bakatonda abalala okunkwasa obusungu.  
\v 19 Naye nze gwe balumya?” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. “Tebeerumya bokka, ne beeswazaswaza?” 
\p  
\v 20 Noolwekyo bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Laba obusungu bwange n’ekiruyi kyange bijja kufukibwa ku kifo kino, ku bantu ne ku nsolo, ku miti egy’omu ttale era ne ku bibala eby’omu ttaka; bujja kubuubuuka era tebujja kukoma.” 
\s1 Okugaana Okuwulira Bannabbi 
\p  
\v 21 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Mugatte ebiweebwayo byammwe ebyokebwa ku ssaddaaka zammwe, ennyama mugyeriire.  
\v 22 Kubanga ku lunaku lwe nabaggya mu Misiri saayogera eri bakitammwe wadde okubalagira ebikwata ku biweebwayo ebyokebwa wadde ssaddaaka.  
\v 23 Naye etteeka lino lye nabawa ligamba nti, ‘Muŋŋondere, nange nnaabeera Katonda wammwe, nammwe munaabeera bantu bange. Mutambulire mu makubo gonna ge mbalagira, mulyoke mubeere bulungi.’  
\v 24 Naye tebampulira wadde okunzisaako omwoyo, wabula bagoberera okuteesa kw’emitima gyabwe egijjudde ebibi. Badda emabega so tebaalaga mu maaso.  
\v 25 Okuva mu biseera bajjajjammwe bye baaviiramu e Misiri okutuusa kaakano, mbadde mpeereza abaddu bange bannabbi emirundi n’emirundi.  
\v 26 Naye tebampuliriza wadde okunzisaako omwoyo, bakakanyaza ensingo zaabwe era ne bakola ebibi ne basinga ne bajjajjaabwe. 
\p  
\v 27 “Kale ojja kubagamba bino byonna naye tebajja kukuwuliriza, bw’onoobayita tebajja kukwanukula.  
\v 28 Noolwekyo bagambe nti, ‘Lino ly’eggwanga eritagondera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waalyo oba okufaayo ku kugololwa. Amazima gabulawo, tegali ku mimwa gyabwe.  
\v 29 Salako enviiri zo ggwe Yerusaalemi, ozisuule wala ddala okaabire ku ntikko z’ensozi, kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* alese abantu be era n’asuula ab’omu mulembe guno mw’asunguwalidde ennyo.’ ” 
\s1 Ekiwonvu eky’Okufiiramu 
\p  
\v 30 “Abantu ba Yuda bakoze ekintu eky’ekivve mu maaso gange, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. Batadde bakatonda abalala mu nnyumba yange eyitibwa erinnya lyange ne bagyonoona.  
\v 31 Bazimbye ebifo ebigulumivu ebya Tofesi mu kiwonvu kya mutabani wa Kinomu ne bassaddaakiramu batabani baabwe be bazaala n’abawala, kye saalowoozaako wadde okukibalagira.  
\v 32 Laba, ennaku zijja,” bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, bwe kitariyitibwa Kiwonvu kya Tofesi oba ekya Kinnomu ne kiyitibwa Kiwonvu kya ttambiro: kubanga baliziikamu Tofesi okutuusa we wataliba bbanga lya kuziikamu.  
\v 33 Era emirambo gy’abantu bano gifuuke emmere y’ebinyonyi eby’omu bbanga era n’ensolo ez’omu nsiko, era waleme kubaawo muntu wakuzigoba;  
\v 34 olwo nga nkomezza amaloboozi ag’okusanyuka n’okujaguza, n’eddoboozi ly’omusajja awasa n’ery’omugole we mu bibuga bya Yuda ne mu nguudo za Yerusaalemi, olwo ensi ng’efuuse matongo. 
\c 8  
\p  
\v 1 “Mu kiseera ekyo, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, amagumba ga bakabaka ba Yuda, n’amagumba g’abalangira, n’amagumba ga bakabona, n’amagumba ga bannabbi, n’amagumba g’abatuuze b’omu Yerusaalemi galiggyibwa mu ntaana zaago.  
\v 2 Kale galyanikibwa mu musana, eri omwezi n’emmunyeenye ez’omu ggulu, ze baayagala era ne baaweereza era ze baagoberera ne beebuuzaako ne basinza. Tebalikuŋŋaanyizibwa wadde okuziikibwa naye balibeera ng’ebisasiro wansi ku ttaka.  
\v 3 N’abantu b’ensi eno ennyonoonyi bw’etyo abalisigalawo, be ndiba nsasaanyizza mu mawanga, balyegomba okufa okusinga okuba abalamu,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye. 
\s1 Ekibi n’Okubonerezebwa 
\p  
\v 4 “Bategeeze nti, Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Omuntu bw’agwa, tayimuka? 
\q2 Oba omuntu bw’ava mu kkubo ettuufu, takyusa n’adda? 
\q1  
\v 5 Kale lwaki abantu bange bano 
\q2 banvaako ne bagendera ddala? 
\q1  
\v 6 Nawuliriza n’obwegendereza 
\q2 naye tebayogera mazima; 
\q1 tewali muntu yenna yeenenya bibi byakoze n’okwebuuza nti, 
\q2 ‘Kiki kino kye nkoze?’ 
\q1 Buli muntu akwata kkubo lye 
\q2 ng’embalaasi efubutuka ng’etwalibwa mu lutalo. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ebinyonyi ebibuukira mu bbanga 
\q2 bimanyi ebiseera mwe bitambulira; 
\q1 ne kaamukuukulu n’akataayi ne ssekanyolya 
\q2 bimanyi ebiseera mwe bikomerawo, 
\q1 naye abantu bange 
\q2 tebamanyi biragiro bya \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Muyinza mutya okwogera nti, 
\q2 “Tuli bagezi nnyo, n’amateeka ga \nd Mukama\nd* tugalina, 
\q1 ate nga ekkalaamu y’abawandiisi ey’obulimba 
\q2 yeebikyusizza. 
\q1  
\v 9 Abagezigezi baliswala ne bakeŋŋentererwa 
\q2 era balitwalibwa. 
\q1 Bagaanyi ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 magezi ki ge balina? 
\q1  
\v 10 Noolwekyo bakazi baabwe 
\q2 ndibagabira abasajja abalala 
\q1 n’ennimiro zaabwe 
\q2 zitwalibwe abantu abalala. 
\q1 Bonna ba mululu okuva ku asembayo wansi okutuuka ku akomererayo waggulu, 
\q2 nnabbi ne kabona bonna balimba ne babba abantu. 
\q1  
\v 11 Ebiwundu by’abantu bange babijjanjaba nga tebafaayo, 
\q2 babikomya kungulu nga boogera nti, 
\q2 Mirembe, Mirembe, ate nga teri mirembe. 
\q1  
\v 12 Baakwatibwa ensonyi bwe baakola ebivve? 
\q2 Nedda tebakwatibwa nsonyi wadde, 
\q2 so tebamanyi wadde okulimbalimba. 
\q1 Noolwekyo baligwira mu bagudde, 
\q2 balikka lwe balibonerezebwa,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 “Ndimalirawo ddala amakungula gaabwe,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q2 Tewaliba zabbibu, 
\q1 na mutiini, 
\q2 n’ebikoola byabwe biriwotoka. 
\q1 Bye mbawadde 
\q2 biribaggyibwako. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Kiki ekitutuuzizza wano obutuuza? 
\q2 Mukuŋŋaane. 
\q1 Tuddukire mu bibuga ebiriko bbugwe 
\q2 tuzikiririre eyo. 
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda atuwaddeyo tuzikirire 
\q2 era atuwadde amazzi agalimu obutwa tuganywe, 
\q2 kubanga twonoonye mu maaso ge. 
\q1  
\v 15 Twasuubira mirembe 
\q2 naye tewali bulungi bwajja; 
\q1 twasuubira ekiseera eky’okuwonyezebwa 
\q2 naye waaliwo ntiisa. 
\q1  
\v 16 Okukaaba kw’embalaasi z’omulabe kuwulirwa mu Ddaani; 
\q2 ensi yonna yakankana olw’okukaaba kw’embalaasi. 
\q1 Bajja okuzikiriza 
\q2 ensi ne byonna ebigirimu, 
\q2 ekibuga ne bonna abakibeeramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 “Laba, ndikusindikira emisota egy’obusagwa, 
\q2 amasalambwa g’otasobola kufuga, 
\q2 emisota egyo girikuluma,” 
\q2 bwayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Nnina ennaku etewonyezeka, 
\q2 omutima gwange gwennyise. 
\q1  
\v 19 Wuliriza okukaaba kw’abantu bange 
\q2 okuva mu nsi ey’ewala. 
\q1 “\nd Mukama\nd* taliimu mu Sayuuni? 
\q2 Kabaka we takyalimu?” 
\b  
\q1 “Lwaki bansunguwaza n’ebifaananyi byabwe, 
\q2 bakatonda abalala abatagasa?” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 “Amakungula gayise, 
\q2 n’ekyeya kiyise, 
\q2 tetulokolebbwa.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 Nnumiziddwa olw’okulumizibwa kwa muwala wange. 
\q2 Nkaaba ne nzijula ennaku. 
\q1  
\v 22 Teri ddagala mu Gireyaadi? 
\q2 Teriiyo musawo? 
\q1 Lwaki ekiwundu ky’abantu bange 
\q2 tekiwonyezebwa? 
\c 9  
\q1  
\v 1 Woowe, singa omutwe gwange gubadde mugga 
\q2 n’amaaso gange luzzi lwa maziga, 
\q1 nnandikaabye emisana n’ekiro 
\q2 olw’abantu bange be batta! 
\q1  
\v 2 Woowe singa mbadde n’ekisulo 
\q2 ky’abatambuze mu ddungu, 
\q1 nnandivudde ku bantu bange 
\q2 ne mbaleka 
\q1 kubanga bonna benzi, 
\q2 bibiina by’abasajja ab’enkwe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 “Bategeka olulimi lwabwe 
\q2 ng’omutego ogunasula obulimba; 
\q1 bakulaakulanye mu ggwanga 
\q2 naye nga tebayimiridde ku mazima, 
\q1 kubanga bakola ekibi kino ate ne bongera ekirala; 
\q2 era tebammanyi,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 4 “Mwegendereze mikwano gyammwe 
\q2 era temwesiganga baganda bammwe: 
\q1 kubanga buli wa luganda mulimba 
\q2 na buli wamukwano agenda awaayiriza buwaayiriza. 
\q1  
\v 5 Buli muntu alimba muliraanwa we 
\q2 era tewali n’omu ayogera mazima. 
\q1 Bayigirizza ennimi zaabwe okulimba 
\q2 ne beemalamu amaanyi nga bakola ebitali bya butuukirivu. 
\q1  
\v 6 Mubeera wakati mu bulimba; 
\q2 mu bulimba bwabwe bagaana okummanya,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\p  
\v 7 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Laba, ndibalongoosa ne mbagezesa, 
\q2 kiki ate kye nnaakolera abantu bange 
\q2 kubanga boonoonye? 
\q1  
\v 8 Olulimi lwabwe kasaale akatta, 
\q2 lwogera bya bulimba, 
\q1 buli muntu ayogeza mirembe n’akamwa ke, 
\q2 naye mu mutima gwe ategeka kumutega. 
\q1  
\v 9 Nneme okubabonereza olw’ebintu bino?” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 “Seesasuze ku ggwanga 
\q2 eriri nga lino?” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Ndikaaba ne nkungubagira ensozi 
\q2 era ne nkungubagira amalundiro ag’omu ddungu. 
\q1 Galekeddwa awo era tegayitwamu, 
\q2 n’okukaaba kw’ente tekuwulirwa. 
\q1 Ebinyonyi eby’omu bbanga tebikyawulirwa 
\q2 n’ensolo ez’omu nsiko zidduse. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 “Ndifuula Yerusaalemi entuumu y’ebifunfugu, 
\q2 ekisulo ky’ebibe. 
\q1 Era ndyonoona ebibuga bya Yuda 
\q2 waleme kubaawo muntu yenna abeeramu.” 
\p  
\v 12 Mugezigezi ki anaayinza okutegeera kino? Ani oyo \nd Mukama\nd* gw’abuulidde alyoke akinnyonnyole? Lwaki ensi eyonoonese ng’eddungu ne wataba agiyitamu? 
\p  
\v 13 \nd Mukama\nd* n’agamba nti, “Kubanga balese amateeka gange, ge nabateekerawo. Tebaŋŋondedde wadde okugoberera amateeka gange.  
\v 14 Naye, bagoberedde obukakanyavu bw’emitima gyabwe ne basinza ebifaananyi bya Babaali nga bajjajjaabwe bwe baabayigiriza.”  
\v 15 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, “Laba ndiriisa abantu bano emmere ekaawa ne mbanyweesa n’amazzi ag’obutwa.  
\v 16 Ndibasaasaanya mu mawanga bakitaabwe ge bataamanya; era ndibasindiikiriza n’ekitala, okutuusa nga mbazikirizza.” 
\p  
\v 17 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Mulowooze kaakano, muyite abakazi abakungubazi, bajje; 
\q2 era mutumye abasingayo obumanyirivu. 
\q1  
\v 18 Leka bajje mangu 
\q2 batukaabireko 
\q1 okutuusa amaaso gaffe lwe ganaakulukuta amaziga, 
\q2 n’obukoowekoowe bwaffe ne butiiriika amazzi. 
\q1  
\v 19 Kubanga amaloboozi ag’okukungubaga gawuliddwa mu Sayuuni; 
\q2 ‘Nga tunyagiddwa! 
\q2 Nga tuswadde nnyo! 
\q1 Tuteekwa okuva mu nsi yaffe 
\q2 kubanga amayumba gaffe gazikiriziddwa.’ ” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Kaakano mmwe abakazi, muwulirize ekigambo kya Katonda, 
\q2 era mutege okutu kwammwe kuwulire ekigambo ky’akamwa ke. 
\q1 Muyigirize bawala bammwe okukaaba, 
\q2 era buli muntu ayigirize munne okukungubaga. 
\q1  
\v 21 Kubanga okufa kutuyingiridde mu madirisa, 
\q2 kuyingidde mu mbiri zaffe, 
\q1 okugoba abaana okubaggya ku nguudo, 
\q2 n’abavubuka okubaggya mu bifo ebisanyukirwamu. 
\p  
\v 22 “Yogera,” bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Emirambo gy’abasajja abafudde 
\q2 gijja kugwa ng’obusa ku ttale 
\q1 ng’ebinywa by’eŋŋaano ensale bwe bigwa 
\q2 emabega w’omukunguzi nga tebiriiko alonda.’ ” 
\p  
\v 23 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Omusajja omugezi aleme kwenyumiririza mu magezi ge, 
\q2 oba omusajja ow’amaanyi okwenyumiririza mu maanyi ge 
\q2 oba omugagga mu bugagga bwe. 
\q1  
\v 24 Naye leka oyo eyeenyumiriza yeenyumirizenga mu kino: 
\q2 nti antegeera era ammanyi, 
\q1 nti nze \nd Mukama\nd* akola ebyekisa 
\q2 n’eby’ensonga n’eby’obutuukirivu mu nsi, 
\q2 kubanga mu byo mwe nsanyukira,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 25 “Ennaku zijja,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, “lwe ndibonereza abo bonna abakomole obukomozi mu mubiri:  
\v 26 Misiri, ne Yuda, ne Edomu, n’abaana ba Amoni, ne Mowaabu, era n’abo bonna ababeera mu ddungu mu bifo eby’ewala. Kubanga amawanga gano gonna ddala si makomole, ate era n’ennyumba ya Isirayiri yonna si nkomole mu mutima.” 
\c 10  
\s1 Katonda ne Bakatonda Abalala 
\p  
\v 1 Muwulire ekigambo Katonda ky’abagamba, mmwe ennyumba ya Isirayiri.  
\v 2 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Temugobereranga makubo g’amawanga 
\q2 oba okweraliikirira obubonero obw’oku ku ggulu, 
\q2 kubanga amawanga ge byeraliikirira. 
\q1  
\v 3 Kubanga empisa ez’amawanga tezigasa; 
\q2 batema omuti mu kibira, 
\q2 omubazzi n’aguyooyoota n’ebyuma bye. 
\q1  
\v 4 Bagunyiriza ne ffeeza ne zaabu, 
\q2 bagukomerera n’enninga n’ennyondo 
\q2 guleme okunyeenyanyeenya. 
\q1  
\v 5 Bakatonda bafaanana nga ssemufu 
\q2 mu nnimiro y’ebibala, 
\q1 era tebasobola kwogera 
\q2 kubanga basitulwa busitulwa tebasobola kutambula. 
\q1 Tobatya, 
\q2 tebayinza kukukola kabi konna, 
\q2 wadde okukola akalungi n’akamu.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 Tewali ali nga ggwe, Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q2 Oli mukulu, 
\q2 era erinnya lyo ly’amaanyi nnyo. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ani ataakutye, 
\q2 Ayi Kabaka w’amawanga? 
\q2 Kubanga kino kye kikugwanira. 
\q1 Kubanga mu bagezigezi bonna bannaggwanga 
\q2 ne mu bwakabaka bwabwe bwonna 
\q2 tewali ali nga ggwe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Bonna tebalina magezi basirusiru, 
\q2 abo abayigira ku bakatonda ababajje mu miti. 
\q1  
\v 9 Ffeeza eyaweesebwa ey’empewere eggyibwa e Talusiisi, 
\q2 ne zaabu eva e Yufazi, 
\q1 ffundi n’omuweesi wa zaabu bye bakoze 
\q2 byambazibwa engoye eza kaniki ne z’effulungu. 
\q2 Gino gyonna mirimu gy’abasajja abakalabakalaba. 
\q1  
\v 10 Naye \nd Mukama\nd* ye Katonda ddala, ye Katonda omulamu, 
\q2 era Kabaka ow’emirembe gyonna. 
\q1 Bw’asunguwala, ensi ekankana, 
\q2 amawanga tegasobola kugumira busungu bwe. 
\s1 Katonda Omulamu ne Bakatonda Abataliimu 
\p  
\v 11 “Bw’oti bw’oba obagamba nti, ‘Bakatonda abataakola ggulu na nsi ba kuzikirira bave ku nsi ne wansi w’eggulu.’ ” 
\q1  
\v 12 \nd Mukama\nd* yakola ensi n’amaanyi ge, 
\q2 n’atonda ebitonde byonna n’amagezi ge, 
\q2 era okutegeera kwe, kwe kwayanjuluza eggulu. 
\q1  
\v 13 Bw’afulumya eddoboozi lye, amazzi agali mu bire gawuluguma, 
\q2 asobozesa ebire okusituka nga biva ku nkomerero y’ensi. 
\q1 Amyansisa eggulu mu nkuba, 
\q2 era n’aggya empewo mu mawanika ge. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Buli muntu talina magezi era taliimu kutegeera; 
\q2 buli muweesi wa zaabu aswala olw’ekifaananyi ky’akoze. 
\q1 Kubanga ebifaananyi bye ebisaanuuse bulimba, 
\q2 era tebiriimu bulamu. 
\q1  
\v 15 Tebiriiko kye bigasa, ebisaanye okunyoomebwa 
\q2 ebirizikirizibwa nga \nd Mukama\nd* azze okusala omusango. 
\q1  
\v 16 Oyo Katonda Omugabo gwa Yakobo tali ng’ebyo, 
\q2 ye Mutonzi w’ebintu byonna, 
\q1 era owa Isirayiri, eggwanga ery’omugabo gwe, 
\q2 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye lye linnya lye. 
\s1 Okuzikirira Okujja 
\q1  
\v 17 Mukuŋŋaanye ebyammwe muve mu nsi, 
\q2 mmwe abazingiziddwa. 
\q1  
\v 18 Kubanga bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, 
\q2 “Laba nfuumuula abantu 
\q2 mbaggye mu nsi eno, 
\q1 era ndibaleetako ennaku 
\q2 balyoke bawambibwe.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Zinsanze nze olw’ekiwundu kyange 
\q2 ekinnuma ennyo. 
\q1 Naye ate ne ŋŋamba nti, 
\q2 “Eno ndwadde yange, nteekwa okugigumira.” 
\q1  
\v 20 Eweema yange eyonooneddwa, 
\q2 era emiguwa gyonna gikutuse, abaana bange bandese, tewakyali. 
\q1 Tewali n’omu asigaddewo kaakano 
\q2 kuzimba weema yange 
\q2 wadde okuzimba ekigango kyange. 
\q1  
\v 21 Kubanga abasumba bafuuse ng’ensolo 
\q2 tebakyebuuza ku \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 Noolwekyo tebakulaakulana 
\q2 era endiga zaabwe zonna zisaasaanye. 
\q1  
\v 22 Wuliriza! 
\q2 Amawulire gatuuse, 
\q1 waliwo akeegugungo ak’amaanyi okuva mu nsi ey’omu bukiikakkono, 
\q2 kajja kufuula ebibuga bya Yuda amatongo, ebisulo by’ebibe. 
\s1 Okusaba kwa Yeremiya 
\q1  
\v 23 Mmanyi Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ng’obulamu bw’omuntu si bubwe, 
\q2 omuntu si y’aluŋŋamya amakubo ge. 
\q1  
\v 24 Nnuŋŋamya, \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda naye mu kigera ekisaanidde, 
\q2 si mu busungu bwo, 
\q2 si kulwa ng’onfuula ekitaliimu. 
\q1  
\v 25 Yiwa obusungu bwo ku mawanga agatakumanyi, 
\q2 agatakutwala ng’ekikulu, 
\q2 ku bantu abatakoowoola linnya lyo. 
\q1 Kubanga bamazeewo Yakobo, 
\q2 bamuliiridde ddala 
\q2 era ne boonoona ensi ye. 
\c 11  
\s1 Yuda Amenye Endagaano 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ekyajjira Yeremiya.  
\v 2 Wuliriza ebigambo by’endagaano eno era yogera n’abantu ba Yuda era n’abo ababeera mu Yerusaalemi.  
\v 3 Bagambe nti, “Bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wa Isirayiri bw’ayogera nti, ‘Akolimiddwa omuntu atagondera bigambo by’endagaano eno  
\v 4 bye nalagira bakitammwe bwe nabaggya mu nsi y’e Misiri, okuva mu kikoomi ky’omuliro.’ Nabagamba nti, ‘Muŋŋondere era mukole ebintu byonna nga bwe mbalagira, munaabeeranga bantu bange, nange nnaabeeranga Katonda wammwe,  
\v 5 ndyoke ntuukirize ekirayiro kye nalayirira bajjajjammwe, okubawa ensi ekulukuta amata n’omubisi gw’enjuki, ensi gye mulimu leero.’ ” Awo ne nziramu nti, “Kibeere bwe kityo \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\p  
\v 6 \nd Mukama\nd* n’aŋŋamba nti, “Langirira ebigambo bino byonna mu bibuga bya Yuda ne mu nguudo za Yerusaalemi. ‘Muwulire ebigambo by’endagaano era mubikole.  
\v 7 Okuva lwe naggya bajjajjammwe mu Misiri okutuusa leero, mbakuutidde emirundi mingi nga mbagamba nti, “Muŋŋondere.”  
\v 8 Naye tebampuliriza wadde okussaayo omwoyo, wabula buli muntu yeeyongera okutambulira mu bukakanyavu bw’omutima gwe omubi. Ne ndyoka mbaleetako ebikolimo byonna ebiri mu ndagaano gye nabalagira okukwata ne batagikwata.’ ” 
\p  
\v 9 Ate \nd Mukama\nd* n’aŋŋamba nti, “Waliwo olukwe mu basajja ba Yuda ne mu batuuze b’omu Yerusaalemi.  
\v 10 Bazzeeyo mu butali butuukirivu bwa bajjajjaabwe abaagaana okugoberera ebigambo byange. Bagoberedde bakatonda abalala ne babaweereza. Ennyumba zombi eya Isirayiri n’eya Yuda zimenye endagaano gye nakola ne bajjajjaabwe.  
\v 11 Noolwekyo, bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Laba, ndibaleetako akabi ke batayinza kuwona; wadde banaankaabirira, sijja kubawuliriza.  
\v 12 Ebibuga bya Yuda n’abantu ba Yerusaalemi bajja kugenda bakaabirire bakatonda baabwe be bootereza obubaane, naye tebaabayambe n’akamu nga bali mu nnaku.  
\v 13 Mulina bakatonda abenkana ebibuga byammwe obungi, ggwe Yuda; n’ebyoto bye mukoze okwoterezaako obubaane eri Baali byenkana enguudo za Yerusaalemi obungi.’  
\p  
\v 14 “Noolwekyo tosabira bantu bano, tobakaabiririra wadde okubegayiririra kubanga siribawulira mu biro lwe baligwako akabi. 
\q1  
\v 15 “Omwagalwa akola ki mu yeekaalu yange ng’ate akoze eby’ekivve? 
\q2 Okuwaayo ssaddaaka kuyinza okukuggyako ekibonerezo ekijja? 
\q2 Okola ebibi n’olyoka ojaguza!” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 \nd Mukama\nd* yakutuuma Omuzeyituuni ogubala ennyo, 
\q2 oguliko ebibala ebirungi. 
\q1 Naye ajja kugukumako omuliro 
\q2 n’okuwuuma okw’omuyaga ogw’amaanyi, 
\q2 amatabi gaagwo gakutuke. 
\m  
\v 17 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, eyakusimba akulangiriddeko akabi kubanga ennyumba ya Isirayiri n’ennyumba ya Yuda zikoze eby’ekivve ne zinkwasa obusungu bwe zooterezza Baali obubaane. 
\p  
\v 18 \nd Mukama\nd* yambikkulira nnamanyisa mu bbanga eryo olukwe lwe baali bansalira.  
\v 19 Nnali ng’omwana gw’endiga gwe batwala okuttibwa. Nnali simanyi nga nze gwe baali balyamu olukwe, nga bagamba nti, 
\q1 “Ka tuzikirize omuti n’ekibala kyagwo, 
\q2 ka tumutemere ddala ave ku nsi y’abalamu, 
\q2 erinnya lye lireme okuddayo okujjukirwa n’akatono.” 
\q1  
\v 20 Naye ggwe \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, 
\q2 alamula mu bwenkanya, agezesa omutima n’ebirowoozo, 
\q1 ka ndabe bw’obawoolera eggwanga, 
\q2 kubanga ggwe gwenkwasizza ensonga yange. 
\p  
\v 21 Noolwekyo bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ku basajja b’e Anasosi abanoonya obulamu bwo nga bagamba nti, “Totubuulira bunnabbi mu linnya lya \nd Mukama\nd*, tuleme okukutta.”  
\v 22 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, “Laba, nzija kutta abavubuka n’ekitala; ne batabani baabwe n’abawala bafe enjala.  
\v 23 So tewaliba n’omu alisigalawo, kubanga ndireeta akabi ku basajja b’e Anasosi, mu mwaka gwe ndibabonererezaamu.” 
\c 12  
\s1 Okwemulugunya kwa Yeremiya 
\q1  
\v 1 Bulijjo oba mutuukirivu, Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q2 bwe nkuleetera ensonga yange. 
\q1 Noolwekyo nnaaleeta ensonga yange gy’oli. 
\q2 Lwaki abakozi b’ebibi baba mu kwesiima? 
\q2 Lwaki abalimbalimba bonna baba mu bulamu obw’emirembe? 
\q1  
\v 2 Wabasimba, emirandira ne ginywera, 
\q2 bakula ne baleeta ebibala. 
\q1 Tova ku mimwa gyabwe bulijjo 
\q2 wadde ng’oliwala n’emitima gyabwe. 
\q1  
\v 3 Ate ng’ommanyi Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q2 ondaba era otegeera bye nkulowoozaako. 
\q1 Sika otwale abasajja bano ababi ng’endiga ezigenda okuttibwa. 
\q2 Bategekere olunaku lwe balisanjagirwako. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ensi erikoma ddi okwonooneka, 
\q2 n’omuddo mu buli nnimiro okukala? 
\q1 Kubanga abo abali mu nsi bakozi ba bibi, 
\q2 ensolo n’ebinyonyi bizikiridde, 
\q1 kubanga abantu bagamba nti, 
\q2 “Katonda taalabe binaatutuukako.” 
\s1 Katonda Addamu 
\q1  
\v 5 “Bw’oba owakana n’abaddusi b’embiro 
\q2 n’oggwaamu amaanyi 
\q2 oyinza otya okudduka n’embalaasi? 
\q1 Obanga mu nsi entereevu weesitadde n’ogwa bugwi, 
\q2 onoosobolayo otya mu nsiko y’oku Yoludaani? 
\q1  
\v 6 Ne baganda bo n’ab’omu nnyumba ya kitaawo 
\q2 nabo bennyini bakwefuukidde, 
\q2 beegasse ku abo abawowoggana nga bakulangiriza. 
\q1 Tobeesiga 
\q2 wadde nga bakwogerako bulungi.” 
\s1 Ennaku ya \nd Mukama\nd* olw’Abantu be 
\q1  
\v 7 “Njabulidde ennyumba yange, 
\q2 ne ndeka omugabo gwange; 
\q1 mpaddeyo abo emmeeme yange b’eyagala, 
\q2 mu mikono gy’abalabe baabwe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Abantu bange be nalonda 
\q2 banfuukidde ng’empologoma eri mu kibira; 
\q1 empulugumira, 
\q2 noolwekyo mbakyaye. 
\q1  
\v 9 Abantu bange be nalonda 
\q2 tebanfuukidde ng’ennyonyi erya ginnaazo ey’amabala, 
\q2 ebinyonyi ebirala ebirya binaabyo gye bizingiza ne bigirumba? 
\q1 Mugende mukuŋŋaanye ensolo zonna ez’omu nsiko 
\q2 muzireete zirye. 
\q1  
\v 10 Abasumba bangi 
\q2 boonoonye ennimiro yange ey’emizabbibu, 
\q1 balinnyiridde ennimiro yange, 
\q2 ensi yange ennungi bagirese njereere. 
\q1  
\v 11 Eyonooneddwa efuuse ddungu 
\q2 esigadde awo ng’enkaabirira. 
\q1 Ensi yonna efuuse matongo 
\q2 kubanga tewali muntu n’omu agifaako. 
\q1  
\v 12 Abanyazi bazze 
\q2 batuuse ku nsozi zonna ez’omu ddungu, 
\q1 kubanga ekitala kya \nd Mukama\nd* kijja kulya 
\q2 okuva ku nsonda emu ey’ensi okutuuka ku ndala, 
\q2 awataliiwo n’omu kuwona. 
\q1  
\v 13 Basize eŋŋaano, ne bakungula amaggwa. 
\q2 Bakooyedde bwereere ne bataba na kebaggyamu. 
\q1 Bakwatiddwa ensonyi olw’ebibala bye bakunguddeyo, 
\q2 kubanga ebyo \nd Mukama\nd* y’abikoze olw’obusungu bwe obungi.” 
\p  
\v 14 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Ebikwata ku baliraanwa bange ababi nga bifa ku mugabo gwe nawa abantu bange Isirayiri okuba ogwabwe, laba ndibasiguukulula okuva mu nsi yaabwe, era ndiggya ennyumba ya Yuda mu bo.  
\v 15 Naye nga mmaze okubasiguukululamu, ndibakwatirwa ekisa ne mbakomyawo buli omu eri omugabo gwe mu nsi ye.  
\v 16 Era nga bwe bayigiriza abantu bange okulayirira mu linnya lya Baali bwe batyo balikwatira ddala empisa z’abantu bange, okulayirira mu linnya lyange nga boogera nti, ‘Nga \nd Mukama\nd* bw’ali omulamu,’ olwo balizimbibwa wakati mu bantu bange.  
\v 17 Naye eggwanga bwe litalissaayo mwoyo, ndirisiguukulula ne ndisaanyizaawo ddala,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\c 13  
\p  
\v 1 Bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* bwe yaŋŋamba nti, “Genda ogule olukoba olwa linena olwesibe mu kiwato kyo, naye tolunnyikanga mu mazzi.”  
\v 2 Bwe ntyo ne neegulira olukoba, nga \nd Mukama\nd* bwe yandagira, ne ndwesiba mu kiwato kyange. 
\p  
\v 3 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kinzijira omulundi ogwokubiri  
\v 4 nti, “Ddira olukoba lwe wagula lwe weesibye mu kiwato kyo ogende ku mabbali g’omugga Fulaati olukweke eyo mu lwatika lw’olwazi.”  
\v 5 Bwe ntyo ne ŋŋenda ne ndukweka ku mabbali g’omugga Fulaati nga \nd Mukama\nd* bwe yandagira. 
\p  
\v 6 Ennaku nnyingi nga ziyiseewo, ate \nd Mukama\nd* nandagira nti, “Genda kaakano ku Fulaati oleete olukoba lwe nakulagira okukwekayo.”  
\v 7 Awo ne ndyoka ŋŋenda ku mugga Fulaati, ne nsimulayo olukoba ne nduggya mu kifo we nnali ndukwese. Naye laba, olukoba lwali lwonoonese, nga terukyalina kye lugasa. 
\p  
\v 8 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kinzijira nga kyogera nti,  
\v 9 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Bwe ntyo bwe ndikkakkanya okwegulumiza kwa Yuda ne Yerusaalemi.  
\v 10 Abantu bano aboonoonyi abagaana okukwata ebigambo byange, abagoberera obujeemu bw’emitima gyabwe ne bagoberera bakatonda abalala okubaweereza n’okubasinza, bajja kuba ng’olukoba olwo olutaliiko kye lugasa.  
\v 11 Ng’olukoba bwe lunywerera mu kiwato ky’omuntu, bwe ntyo bwe nzija okwagala ennyumba ya Isirayiri yonna n’eya Yuda zinneesibeko,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘balyoke babeere abantu bange, bagulumize erinnya lyange n’ettendo; naye bo ne batawulira.’ ” 
\s1 Olugero lw’Ekita 
\p  
\v 12 “Bagambe bw’oti nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wa Isirayiri, buli kita kiba kya kujjuza nvinnyo.’ Nabo balikuddamu nti, ‘Tetumanyi nga buli kita kiba kya kujjuza nvinnyo?’  
\v 13 Olwo olyoke obagambe nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Laba nditamiiza abantu bonna abatuula mu nsi eno, ne bakabaka abatuula ku ntebe ya Dawudi ey’obwakabaka, ne bakabona, ne bannabbi n’abantu bonna ab’omu Yerusaalemi.  
\v 14 Era buli omu alikoonagana ne munne, abalenzi ne bakitaabwe, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. Siribalumirwa, wadde okubaleka oba okubakwatirwa ekisa, ndibazikiriza.’ ” 
\s1 Amalala n’Okuswazibwa kwa Yerusaalemi 
\q1  
\v 15 Wuliriza ontegere okutu; 
\q2 toba na malala, 
\q2 \nd Mukama\nd* y’akyogedde. 
\q1  
\v 16 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo 
\q2 mugulumize nga tannaleeta kizikiza, 
\q1 nga ebigere byo tebinneesittala ku nsozi 
\q2 ezikutte ekizikiza. 
\q1 Musuubira ekitangaala, 
\q2 naye ajja okukifuulamu ekisiikirize eky’okufa 
\q2 akikyuse kibe ekizikiza ekikutte ennyo. 
\q1  
\v 17 Naye bwe mutaafeeyo, 
\q2 emmeeme yange eneekaabira mu kyama 
\q2 olw’amalala gammwe; 
\q1 amaaso gange gajja kukaaba nnyo nnyini 
\q2 gakulukuse amaziga 
\q2 era ekisibo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kijja kuwambibwa. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Gamba kabaka era ne namasole nti, 
\q2 “Mukke muve ku ntebe zammwe ez’obwakabaka, 
\q1 kubanga engule zammwe ez’ebitiibwa 
\q2 zijja kugwa okuva ku mitwe gyammwe.” 
\q1  
\v 19 Ebibuga by’e Negebu biggaddwawo, 
\q2 tewali n’omu anaabiggulawo; 
\q1 Yuda yonna yaakutwalibwa mu buwaŋŋanguse, 
\q2 yonna yaakutwalibwa. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 Muyimuse amaaso gammwe 
\q2 mulabe abo abava mu bukiikakkono. 
\q1 Kiruwa ekisibo ekyabaweebwa, 
\q2 endiga ezaabeeyinuzanga? 
\q1  
\v 21 Muligamba mutya \nd Mukama\nd* 
\q2 bw’alibawaayo okufugibwa abo be mwali mutwala nga ab’omukago? 
\q1 Temulirumwa 
\q2 ng’omukazi alumwa okuzaala? 
\q1  
\v 22 Era bwe weebuuza nti, 
\q2 “Lwaki kino kintuseeko?” 
\q1 Olw’ebibi byo ebingi 
\q2 engoye zo kyezivudde ziyuzibwa, 
\q2 era omubiri gwo ne gubonerezebwa. 
\q1  
\v 23 Omuwesiyopya ayinza okukyusa olususu lw’omubiri gwe 
\q2 oba engo okukyusa amabala gaayo? 
\q1 Bwe mutyo bwe mutasobola kukola birungi, 
\q2 mmwe abaamanyiira okukola ebibi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 24 “Ndibasaasaanya ng’ebisusunku 
\q2 ebifuuyibwa empewo eva mu ddungu. 
\q1  
\v 25 Guno gwe mugabo gwo 
\q2 gwe nakupimira,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q1 “kubanga wanneerabira 
\q2 ne weesiga bakatonda ab’obulimba. 
\q1  
\v 26 Nze kennyini ndibikkula engoye zammwe ne nzibikka ku mitwe gyammwe, 
\q2 obwereere bwammwe ne bulabika. 
\q1  
\v 27 Ndabye obwenzi bwammwe 
\q2 n’obwamalaaya bwe mukoze. 
\q1 Ndabye ebikolwa byo eby’ekivve ku busozi 
\q2 era ne mu nnimiro. 
\q1 Zikusanze ggwe, ayi Yerusaalemi! 
\q2 Olituusa ddi obutaba mulongoofu?” 
\c 14  
\s1 Ekyeya, Enjala, n’Ekitala 
\p  
\v 1 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ekyajjira Yerusaalemi ekikwata ku kyeya. 
\q1  
\v 2 “Yuda ekungubaga n’ebibuga byayo bifaafaaganye, 
\q2 bakaabira ensi, 
\q1 era omulanga 
\q2 gusimbuse mu Yerusaalemi. 
\q1  
\v 3 Abakungu batuma abaddu baabwe okuleeta amazzi; 
\q2 bagenda mu ttanka ez’omu ttaka nga temuli kantu, 
\q2 bakomawo n’ebintu ebikalu; 
\q1 ensonyi nga zibakutte 
\q2 n’essuubi nga libaweddemu; 
\q2 babikka amaaso gaabwe. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ettaka lyatise 
\q2 kubanga enkuba tekyatonnya, 
\q1 abalimi baweddemu amaanyi, 
\q2 babikka ku mitwe gyabwe. 
\q1  
\v 5 N’empeewo ku ttale ezaala 
\q2 n’ereka awo omwana gwayo 
\q2 kubanga tewali muddo. 
\q1  
\v 6 N’ennyumbu ez’omu nsiko ziyimirira ku busozi obukalu 
\q2 nga ziwejjawejja ng’ebibe, 
\q1 amaaso gaazo nga tegalaba bulungi 
\q2 kubanga tezirina kye zirya.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Wadde obutali butuukirivu bwaffe butulumiriza, Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 baako ky’okola olw’erinnya lyo. 
\q1 Kubanga tuzze ennyuma emirundi mingi, 
\q2 tukwonoonye nnyo. 
\q1  
\v 8 Ayi ggwe essuubi lya Isirayiri, 
\q2 Omulokozi waalyo mu biseera eby’okulabiramu ennaku, 
\q1 lwaki oli ng’omuyise mu nsi, 
\q2 ng’omutambuze asula ekiro ekimu? 
\q1  
\v 9 Lwaki oli ng’omuntu gwe baguddeko obugwi, 
\q2 ng’omulwanyi ataliimu maanyi ganunula? 
\q1 Ggwe, Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, oli wakati mu ffe, 
\q2 era tuyitibwa linnya lyo. 
\q2 Totuleka. 
\p  
\v 10 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ku bantu be nti, 
\q1 “Baagala nnyo okubula, 
\q2 tebaziyiza bigere byabwe. 
\q1 Noolwekyo \nd Mukama\nd* tabakkiriza 
\q2 era kaakano wakujjukira obutali butuukirivu bwabwe 
\q2 era ababonereze olw’ebibi byabwe.” 
\p  
\v 11 Awo \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda n’aŋŋamba nti, “Tosabira bantu bano kubeera bulungi.  
\v 12 Newaakubadde nga basiiba, sijja kuwulira kukaaba kwabwe, era wadde bawaayo ebiweebwayo ebyokebwa n’ebiweebwayo eby’empeke, sijja kubikkiriza. Naye nnaabazikiriza n’ekitala, n’enjala ne kawumpuli.” 
\p  
\v 13 Naye ne njogera nti, “Woowe, \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, bannabbi abalala babagamba nti, ‘Tewajja kubaawo lutalo wadde okulumwa enjala. Naye nzija kuleeta mirembe egitakoma mu kifo kino.’ ” 
\p  
\v 14 Awo \nd Mukama\nd* n’alyoka aŋŋamba nti, “Bannabbi bawa obunnabbi obw’obulimba mu linnya lyange, sibatumanga wadde okubalagira okwogera nabo. Babategeeza okwolesebwa okw’obulimba n’obunnabbi obutaliimu, n’obutaliimu bw’emitima gyabwe.  
\v 15 Noolwekyo, bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ebikwata ku bannabbi abategeeza ebyobunnabbi mu linnya lyange wadde nga sibatumanga, era abagamba nti, ‘Ekitala n’enjala tebijja kujja mu nsi eno.’ Bannabbi abo bennyini bajja kuzikirizibwa ekitala n’enjala.  
\v 16 N’abantu be bategeezezza obunnabbi balifa enjala n’ekitala ne bakasukibwa mu nguudo babulweko abaziika, bo ne bakazi baabwe, ne batabani baabwe, n’abawala. Kubanga ndibayiwako obusungu obubasaanira. 
\p  
\v 17 “Kino ky’oba obagamba nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Leka amaaso gange gakulukute amaziga 
\q2 emisana n’ekiro awatali kukoma; 
\q1 kubanga muwala wange embeerera, abantu bange, 
\q2 bafunye ekiwundu ekinene, 
\q2 ekintu eky’amaanyi. 
\q1  
\v 18 Bwe ŋŋenda mu byalo 
\q2 ndaba abafumitiddwa n’ekitala! 
\q1 Bwe ŋŋenda mu kibuga 
\q2 ndaba okutaagulwataagulwa okw’enjala. 
\q1 Naye nnabbi ne kabona beeyongera okukola emirimu gyabwe mu ggwanga 
\q2 kyokka nga bye boogera bya bulimba.’ ” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Yuda ogigaanidde ddala? 
\q2 Sayuuni ogyetamiriddwa ddala? 
\q1 Otufumitidde ddala awatali kuwonyezebwa? 
\q2 Twasuubira emirembe naye tewali kalungi ke tufunye, 
\q1 ekiseera eky’okuwonyezebwa 
\q2 naye laba tufunye bulabe bwereere. 
\q1  
\v 20 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* tukkiriza ebibi byaffe 
\q2 era n’obutali butuukirivu bwa bajjajjaffe, 
\q2 kubanga ddala twayonoona gy’oli. 
\q1  
\v 21 Olw’erinnya lyo totugoba, 
\q2 tovumaganyisa ntebe yo ey’obwakabaka ey’ekitiibwa. 
\q1 Jjukira endagaano gye wakola naffe, 
\q2 togimenya, gituukirize. 
\q1  
\v 22 Waliwo ku bakatonda ababajje bannaggwanga asobola okutonnyesa enkuba? 
\q2 Eggulu ku bw’alyo lisobola okuleeta enkuba? 
\q1 Nedda, wabula ggwe, Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe. 
\q2 Noolwekyo essuubi lyaffe liri mu ggwe, 
\q2 kubanga ggwe okola bino byonna. 
\c 15  
\s1 Yuda Wakuzikirira 
\p  
\v 1 Awo \nd Mukama\nd* n’alyoka aŋŋamba nti, “Musa ne Samwiri ne bwe bandiyimiridde okunneegayirira, sandisonyiye bantu bano. Bagobe okuva mu maaso gange, banviire.  
\v 2 Era bwe bakubuuza nti, ‘Tunaagenda wa?’ 
\q1 “Bagambe nti, ‘Kino \nd Mukama\nd* kyagamba nti, 
\q1 Ab’okuttibwa bagenda kuttibwa, 
\q1 n’ab’ekitala bafe ekitala, n’ab’enjala bafe enjala, 
\q1 n’ab’okuwambibwa bawambibwe.’ 
\p  
\v 3 “Ndiweereza engeri nnya ez’okubazikiriza,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. “Ekitala kya kufumita, embwa zikulule, ebinyonyi eby’omu bbanga n’ensolo ez’omu nsiko zirye n’okuzikiriza.  
\v 4 Era ndibawaayo babeetamwe eruuyi n’eruuyi mu bwakabaka bwonna obw’omu nsi olw’ekyo Manase mutabani wa Keezeekiya kabaka wa Yuda kye yakola mu Yerusaalemi. 
\q1  
\v 5 “Ani alikukwatirwa ekisa ggwe Yerusaalemi? 
\q2 Oba ani alikukungubagira? 
\q2 Oba ani alikyama okubuuza ebikufaako? 
\q1  
\v 6 Mwanneegaana,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q2 “Temutya kudda nnyuma. 
\q1 Noolwekyo mbagololeddeko omukono gwange 
\q2 ne mbazikiriza. 
\q1 Sikyasobola 
\q2 kukukwatirwa kisa. 
\q1  
\v 7 Era ndibakuŋŋunta n’ekitiiyo eky’amannyo 
\q2 mu miryango gy’ebibuga eby’omu nsi. 
\q1 Ndizikiriza abantu bange ne mbamalawo 
\q2 kubanga tebaaleka makubo gaabwe. 
\q1  
\v 8 Bannamwandu beeyongedde obungi 
\q2 okusinga n’omusenyu gw’ennyanja. 
\q1 Mu ttuntu mbaleetedde omuzikiriza 
\q2 amalewo ababazaalira abalenzi abato. 
\q1 Mbakubiddewo 
\q2 obubalagaze n’entiisa. 
\q1  
\v 9 Eyazaala omusanvu ayongobedde, 
\q2 awejjawejja. 
\q1 Enjuba ye egudde nga bukyali misana, 
\q2 amaanyi gamuwedde, ensonyi zimukutte, awuunze, awuubadde. 
\q1 N’abo abawonyeewo ndi wa kubasogga ekitala, 
\q2 mu maaso ga balabe baabwe,” 
\q2 bwayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 Zinsanze, mmange lwaki wanzaala 
\q2 omuntu eggwanga lyonna gwe lirwanyisa ne likuluusanya? 
\q1 Siwolanga wadde okweyazika, 
\q2 kyokka buli muntu ankolimira. 
\p  
\v 11 \nd Mukama\nd* agamba nti, 
\q1 “Ddala ndikununula olw’ekigendererwa ekirungi, 
\q2 ddala ndireetera abalabe bo okukwegayirira, 
\q2 mu biseera eby’okuluma obujiji, mu biseera eby’akabi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 “Omusajja ayinza okumenya ekikomo 
\q2 oba ekyuma eky’omu bukiikakkono? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 “Ndiwaayo eby’obugagga byo n’ebintu byo eby’omuwendo ennyo 
\q2 binyagibwe awatali kusasulwa, 
\q1 olw’ebibi byo byonna 
\q2 ebikoleddwa mu ggwanga lyonna. 
\q1  
\v 14 Ndibafuula abasibe b’abalabe bammwe 
\q2 mu ggwanga lye mutamanyi, 
\q1 kubanga obusungu bwange bwakukoleeza omuliro 
\q2 ogunaabookya gubamalewo.” 
\s1 Yeremiya Yeekaabirako 
\q1  
\v 15 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* ggwe omanyi byonna. 
\q2 Nzijukira ondabirire. 
\q2 Ompalanire eggwanga ku abo abanjigganya. 
\q1 Mu kugumiikiriza kwo okunene tontwala. 
\q2 Lowooza ku ngeri gye mbonyeebonye ku lulwo. 
\q1  
\v 16 Ebigambo byo bwe byanzijira, ne mbirya, 
\q2 byali ssanyu era okujaguza kw’omutima gwange. 
\q1 Kubanga mpitibwa linnya lyo, 
\q2 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye. 
\q1  
\v 17 Situulangako mu kuŋŋaaniro ly’abo ab’ebinyumu 
\q2 era sibeerangako mu biduula nabo. 
\q1 Natuulanga nzekka kubanga naliko omukono gwo, 
\q2 era wandeetera okwekyawa. 
\q1  
\v 18 Lwaki okulumwa kwange tekukoma 
\q2 era n’ekiwundu kyange ne kitawona? 
\q1 Onomberera ng’akagga akalimbalimba 
\q2 ng’ensulo ekalira? 
\p  
\v 19 Noolwekyo kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba nti, 
\q1 “Bwe muneenenya, 
\q2 ndibakomyawo musobole okumpeereza; 
\q1 bwe mulyogera ebigambo ebisaana so si ebitasaanidde, 
\q2 mulibeera boogezi bange. 
\q1 Leka abantu bano be baba bajja gy’oli, 
\q2 so si ggwe okugenda gye bali. 
\q1  
\v 20 Ndikufuula ekisenge eri abantu bano, 
\q2 ekisenge ekinywezebbwa eky’ekikomo. 
\q1 Balikulwanyisa 
\q2 naye tebalikuwangula, 
\q1 kubanga ndi naawe, 
\q2 okukununula, n’okukulokola,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 21 “Ndikununula okuva mu mukono gw’abakozi b’ebibi 
\q2 era n’enkuggya mu mukono gw’abasajja abakambwe,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\c 16  
\s1 Olunaku olw’Akabi 
\p  
\v 1 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kinzijira nga kigamba nti,  
\v 2 “Towasa, kuzaalira balenzi na bawala mu kifo kino.  
\v 3 Kubanga kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba ku balenzi n’abawala abazaalibwa mu nsi eno era ne ku bakazi ba nnyaabwe ne ku basajja ba kitaabwe.  
\v 4 Balifa endwadde ez’akabi. Tebalibakungubagira wadde okuziikibwa naye balibeera ng’ebisaaniko ebisuuliddwa ku ttaka. Balizikirira na kitala era balifa njala; n’emirambo gyabwe girifuuka mmere ya binyonyi eby’omu bbanga n’ebisolo eby’omu nsiko.” 
\p  
\v 5 Kubanga bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Toyingira mu nnyumba we balya emmere y’olumbe, togenda kukungubaga wadde okubasaasira kubanga nziggyewo omukisa gwange n’okwagala kwange era n’okusaasira kwange ku bantu bano,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 6 Bonna ab’ekitiibwa n’abakopi baakufiira mu nsi eno. Tebajja kuziikibwa wadde okukungubagirwa era tewali ajja kwesala misale wadde okumwa omutwe ku lwabwe.  
\v 7 Tewaliba n’omu aliwaayo mmere okuliisa abakungubagira abafiiriddwa, ne bwaliba kitaabwe oba nnyaabwe nga kwe kuli afudde; tewaliba n’omu alibawaayo wadde ekyokunywa okubakubagiza. 
\p  
\v 8 Era toyingiranga mu nnyumba muli kinyumu n’otuula okulya n’okunywa.  
\v 9 Kubanga kino \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri, ky’agamba nti, “Nga weerabirako n’amaaso go, mu nnaku z’obulamu bwo, ndikomya eddoboozi ery’essanyu era n’ery’okwesiima ery’abagole omusajja ne mukyala we mu kifo kino. 
\p  
\v 10 “Bw’oligamba abantu bino byonna ne bakubuuza nti, ‘Lwaki \nd Mukama\nd* atutuusizaako akabi kano konna? Kibi ki kye tukoze? Musango ki gwe tuzizza eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe?’  
\v 11 Kale bagambe nti, ‘Kubanga bakitammwe bandeka ne batakuuma mateeka gange,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘ne bagoberera bakatonda abalala ne babaweereza ne babasinza. Bandeka ne batakuuma mateeka gange.  
\v 12 Era mweyisizza bubi n’okusinga bakitammwe. Laba buli omu nga bwe yeeyisa ng’akakanyaza omutima gwe ogujjudde ebibi mu kifo ky’okuŋŋondera.  
\v 13 Noolwekyo ndibaggya mu nsi eno ne mbateeka mu nsi mmwe gye mutamanyi wadde bakitammwe gye bataamanya, era nga muli eyo muliweereza bakatonda abalala emisana n’ekiro, era siribakwatirwa kisa.’ 
\p  
\v 14 “Naye ennaku zijja,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. “Abantu lwe bataliddayo kwogera nti, ‘Ddala nga Katonda bw’ali omulamu eyaggya Isirayiri mu nsi y’e Misiri,’  
\v 15 naye baligamba nti, ‘Ddala nga \nd Mukama\nd* bw’ali omulamu eyaggya Abayisirayiri mu nsi ey’omu bukiikakkono era n’okuva mu nsi zonna gye yali abasudde.’ Kubanga ndibakomyawo mu nsi gye nawa bajjajjaabwe. 
\p  
\v 16 “Naye kaakano leka ntumye abavubi bange,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, “era bajja kubavuba. Ng’ekyo kiwedde nzija kutumya abayizzi bange, era bajja kubayigga ku buli lusozi era na buli kasozi na buli lwatika lwonna mu njazi.  
\v 17 Amaaso gange galaba buli kye bakola, tebinkwekeddwa wadde obutali butuukirivu bwabwe okuunkwekebwa.  
\v 18 Ndibasasula olw’obutali butuukirivu bwabwe n’olw’ekibi kyabwe emirundi ebiri, kubanga boonoonye ensi yange olw’ebintu ebitaliimu bulamu ne bajjuza omugabo gwange ebifaananyi bya bakatonda baabwe abakolerere, eby’emizizo.” 
\q1  
\v 19 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, amaanyi gange era ekigo kyange, 
\q2 ekiddukiro kyange mu biro eby’okulabiramu ennaku, 
\q1 bannaggwanga balijja gy’oli, 
\q2 okuva ku nkomerero z’ensi bagambe nti, 
\q1 “Bakitaffe tebaalina kantu okuggyako bakatonda ab’obulimba, 
\q2 ebifaananyi ebikolerere ebitagasa ebitaabayamba. 
\q1  
\v 20 Abantu beekolera bakatonda baabwe? 
\q2 Ye, naye si Katonda! 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 “Noolwekyo ndibayigiriza, 
\q2 ku mulundi guno; 
\q2 ŋŋenda kubalaga amaanyi gange n’obuyinza bwange. 
\q1 Olwo balyoke bamanye nti 
\q2 erinnya lyange nze \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\c 17  
\s1 Ekibi n’Ekibonerezo kya Yuda 
\q1  
\v 1 “Ekibi kya Yuda kiwandiikiddwa n’ekkalaamu ey’ekyuma 
\q2 n’ejjinja essongovu; 
\q1 kirambiddwa ku mitima gyabwe 
\q2 ne ku mayembe g’ebyoto byabwe. 
\q1  
\v 2 N’abaana baabwe basinziza 
\q2 ku byoto bya bakatonda ba Asera 
\q1 ebiri ku buli muti oguyimiridde 
\q2 era ne ku busozi obuwanvu. 
\q1  
\v 3 Olusozi lwange oluli mu nsi, 
\q2 obugagga bwammwe n’ebintu byo eby’omuwendo byonna, 
\q1 ndibiwaayo byonna binyagibwe 
\q2 n’ebifo byammwe ebigulumivu kwe musaddaakira 
\q2 olw’ekibi ekibunye mu nsi yonna. 
\q1  
\v 4 Musango gwo ggwe nti olifiirwa ensi gye nakuwa okuba omugabo gwo, 
\q2 ndikufuula muddu wa balabe bo mu nsi gy’otomanyangako, 
\q1 kubanga mu busungu bwange omuliro gukoleezeddwa 
\q2 ogunaayakanga emirembe gyonna.” 
\p  
\v 5 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 Akolimiddwa oyo eyeesiga omuntu 
\q2 era eyeesiga omubiri okuba amaanyi ge, 
\q2 era alina omutima oguva ku Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 6 Aliba ng’ekisaka mu ddungu, 
\q2 ataliraba birungi bwe birijja, 
\q1 naye alibeera mu biwalakate mu ddungu, 
\q2 ensi ey’omunnyo omutali abeeramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 Naye alina omukisa omusajja oyo eyeesiga \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 nga \nd Mukama\nd* ly’essuubi lye. 
\q1  
\v 8 Ali ng’omuti ogusimbiddwa awali amazzi, 
\q2 ne gulandiza emirandira gyagwo ku mabbali g’omugga, 
\q1 nga wadde omusana gujja, tegutya 
\q2 n’amakoola gaagwo tegawotoka, 
\q1 so tegulyeraliikirira mu mwaka ogw’ekyeya 
\q2 era teguliremwa kubala bibala. 
\q1  
\v 9 Omutima mulimba okusinga ebintu byonna, 
\q2 era gulwadde endwadde etawonyezeka. 
\q2 Ani ayinza okugutegeera? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 “Nze \nd Mukama\nd* nkebera omutima, 
\q2 ngezesa emmeeme, 
\q1 okuwa buli muntu ng’amakubo ge bwe gali, 
\q2 ng’ebikolwa bye bwe biri.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Ng’enkwale bw’eyalula amagi geetebiikanga, 
\q2 bw’atyo bw’abeera oyo afuna obugagga mu makubo amakyamu; 
\q1 obulamu bwe nga bwakabeerawo kaseera buseera, 
\q2 bulimuggwaako era oluvannyuma alizuulibwa nga musiru. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 Ekifo kyaffe ekitukuvu, 
\q2 ntebe ey’ekitiibwa eyagulumizibwa okuva ku lubereberye. 
\q1  
\v 13 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* essuubi lya Isirayiri, 
\q2 bonna abakuvaako baliswala. 
\q1 Abo abakuvaako ne bakuleka baliba ng’abawandiikiddwa mu nfuufu, 
\q2 kubanga bavudde ku \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 oluzzi olw’amazzi amalamu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 Mponya, Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, nange nnaawona, 
\q2 ndokola nange nnaalokoka, 
\q2 kubanga ggwe gwe ntendereza. 
\q1  
\v 15 Tobakkiriza kuŋŋamba nti, 
\q2 “Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kiri ludda wa? 
\q2 Ka kituukirire nno kaakano!” 
\q1  
\v 16 Sirekeddaawo kuba musumba wa ndiga zo, 
\q2 omanyi nga sikusabanga kubaleetako nnaku. 
\q2 Byonna ebiva mu kamwa kange tebikukwekeddwa, obimanyi. 
\q1  
\v 17 Toba wa ntiisa gye ndi, 
\q2 ggwe oli buddukiro bwange mu kiseera eky’okulabiramu ennaku. 
\q1  
\v 18 Abo abanjigganya leka baswale, 
\q2 era onkuume nneme kuswala; 
\q1 leka bagwemu ekyekango 
\q2 nze onkuume nneme okwekanga, 
\q1 batuuse ku lunaku olw’ekikangabwa, 
\q2 bazikiririze ddala. 
\s1 Okukuuma Ssabbiiti nga Ntukuvu 
\p  
\v 19 Bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* bwe yaŋŋamba nti, “Genda oyimirire ku mulyango gw’abantu, bakabaka ba Yuda mwe bayingirira n’okufuluma; yimirira ne ku nzigi endala eza Yerusaalemi.  
\v 20 Bagambe nti, ‘Muwulirize ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* mmwe bakabaka ba Yuda n’abantu bonna ababeera mu Yerusaalemi, abayita mu miryango gy’ekibuga.  
\v 21 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Weegendereze oleme kufulumya mugugu gwonna mu nnyumba yo wadde okukola omulimu gwonna ku ssabbiiti, naye mukuume olunaku lwa Ssabbiiti nga lutukuvu nga temulukolerako mulimu gwonna,  
\v 22 era kuuma olunaku lwa Ssabbiiti nga lutukuvu nga bwe nalagira bajjajjammwe.’  
\v 23 Naye tebaawuliriza wadde okukkiriza okunenyezebwa.  
\v 24 Kyokka bwe muneegendereza ne muŋŋondera, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘ne mutayisa kintu kyonna kye mwetisse mu miryango gy’ekibuga ku ssabbiiti, naye ne mukuuma olwa Ssabbiiti nga lutukuvu obutakolerako mulimu gwonna,  
\v 25 olwo bakabaka abatuula ku ntebe ya Dawudi bajja kuyita mu miryango gy’ekibuga n’abakungu baabwe. Bo n’abakungu baabwe baakujja ng’abamu bavuga amagaali abalala nga beebagadde embalaasi, nga bawerekeddwako abasajja ba Yuda n’abo abali mu Yerusaalemi era ekibuga kino kiribeerwamu emirembe gyonna.  
\v 26 Abantu balijja okuva mu bibuga bya Yuda ne mu byalo ebiriraanye Yerusaalemi, okuva mu bitundu bya Benyamini ne mu biwonvu ne mu nsozi z’ebugwanjuba, n’okuva mu nsi ey’ensozi ey’e Negevu, nga baleeta ebiweebwayo ebyokebwa, ne ssaddaaka, ebiweebwayo eby’empeke, n’obubaane era n’ebiweebwayo eby’okwebaza mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 27 Naye bwe mutaŋŋondere kukuuma lunaku lwa Ssabbiiti nga lutukuvu ne mwetikkirako emigugu gyammwe nga mufuluma mu nguudo za Yerusaalemi ku lunaku olwa Ssabbiiti, ndikoleeza omuliro ogutazikira mu miryango gya Yerusaalemi oguliyokya ebigo byakyo.’ ” 
\c 18  
\s1 Olugero lw’Omubumbi n’Ebbumba 
\p  
\v 1 Kino ky’ekigambo ekyajjira Yeremiya ekyava eri \nd Mukama\nd* nti,  
\v 2 “Serengeta mu nnyumba y’omubumbi nkuweere eyo obubaka bwange.”  
\v 3 Awo ne nserengeta eri ennyumba y’omubumbi ne mmulaba ng’akolera emirimu gye ku nnamuziga.  
\v 4 Naye ekintu kye yali abumba kyali kyonoonekedde mu ngalo ze, omubumbi kyeyava akibumbamu ekintu ekirala ng’akibumba nga bwe yasiima. 
\p  
\v 5 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kinzijira nga kigamba nti,  
\v 6 “Gwe ennyumba ya Isirayiri, siyinza nze kubakola ng’omubumbi ono bw’akoze?” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. “Okufaanana ng’ebbumba mu mukono gw’omubumbi, bwe mutyo bwe muli mu ngalo zange, ggwe ennyumba ya Isirayiri.  
\v 7 Ekiseera kyonna bwe nnangirira nti eggwanga oba obwakabaka bwa kusiguukululwa, okumenyebwa era n’okuzikirizibwa,  
\v 8 era singa eggwanga lye nalabula lyenenya ebibi byalyo, olwo ndyejjusa ne sibatuusaako kabi ke nnali ŋŋambye okubakola.  
\v 9 Era ekiseera kyonna nnangirira ebikwata ku ggwanga oba obwakabaka nti ndizimba era ndisimba,  
\v 10 era bwe likola ebibi mu maaso gange, ne litaŋŋondera, ndyejjusa obulungi bwe nagamba okubakolera. 
\p  
\v 11 “Noolwekyo gamba abantu ba Yuda n’abo ababeera mu Yerusaalemi nti, ‘Kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’ayogera nti, Laba ntekateeka okubatuusaako ekikangabwa era nteesezza okubakola akabi. Kale muve mu makubo gammwe amabi, buli omu ku mmwe, mukyuse enneeyisa yammwe n’ebikolwa byammwe.’  
\v 12 Naye ne boogera nti, ‘Tekirina kye kigasa. Tujja kugenda mu maaso n’entegeka yaffe; buli omu ku ffe anaakolanga ng’obukakanyavu bw’omutima gwe bwe buli.’ ” 
\p  
\v 13 Noolwekyo bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* ng’agamba nti, 
\q1 “Mwebuuzeeko mu mawanga. 
\q2 Ani eyali awuliddeko ekintu bwe kiti? 
\q1 Muwala wange Isirayiri 
\q2 akoze ekintu eky’ekivve. 
\q1  
\v 14 Omuzira oguli ku Lebanooni 
\q2 gwali guwedde ku njazi zaakwo? 
\q1 Amazzi gaakwo amannyogovu agava ewala 
\q2 gaali galeseeyoko okukulukuta? 
\q1  
\v 15 Naye ate abantu bange banneerabidde, 
\q2 banyookezza obubaane eri bakatonda abalala, 
\q1 abaleetera okwesittala mu makubo gaabwe 
\q2 era ne mu makubo ag’edda 
\q1 era ne balaga mu bukubokubo. 
\q1  
\v 16 Ensi yaabwe ya kusigala matongo, 
\q2 ekintu eky’okusekererwa emirembe gyonna, 
\q1 abo bonna abayise balyewuunya 
\q2 era ne banyeenya emitwe gyabwe. 
\q1  
\v 17 Ndibasaasaanya mu maaso g’abalabe baabwe 
\q2 ng’empewo eva ebuvanjuba; 
\q1 ndibalaga mabega 
\q2 so si maaso gange ku lunaku olw’okulabirako ennaku.” 
\p  
\v 18 Awo ne balyoka bagamba nti, “Mujje tubeeko kye tukola Yeremiya. Kubanga bakabona weebali banaatutegeezanga amateeka, n’amagezi tunaagafunanga ku bagezi, era n’ebyobunnabbi binaavanga mu bannabbi. Kaakano mujje tumulumbe tumuwakanye era tuleme okussaayo omwoyo ku bigambo bye.” 
\q1  
\v 19 Ompulirize, Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 owulirize abampakanya kye bagamba. 
\q1  
\v 20 Ebikolwa ebirungi binaasasulwanga na bikolwa ebibi? 
\q2 Bansimidde obunnya. 
\q1 Ojjukire nga nayimirira mu maaso go 
\q2 ne nkaaba ku lwabwe, 
\q2 nga nsaba olekeraawo okubasunguwalira. 
\q1  
\v 21 Noolwekyo abaana baabwe baleke bafe enjala, 
\q2 obaweeyo battibwe n’ekitala. 
\q1 Leka bakazi baabwe bafuuke bagumba era babe bannamwandu; 
\q2 abasajja baabwe battibwe; 
\q2 abavubuka baabwe batirimbulwe n’ekitala mu lutalo. 
\q1  
\v 22 Leka okukaaba kuwulirwe nga kuva mu nnyumba zaabwe, 
\q2 bwe banaalumbibwa ne bazindibwa embagirawo, 
\q1 kubanga bansimidde ekinnya bankwate 
\q2 era bateze ebigere byange emitego. 
\q1  
\v 23 Naye Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, gw’omanyi byonna, 
\q2 bye bateesa banzite. 
\q1 Tobasonyiwa byonoono byabwe 
\q2 wadde okusangulawo ebibi byabwe mu maaso go. 
\q1 Obawangulire ddala, 
\q2 era obabonereze mu kiseera ky’obusungu bwo. 
\c 19  
\s1 Olugero lw’Ensumbi Eyayatika 
\p  
\v 1 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Genda ogule ensumbi ey’ebbumba okuva ku mubumbi. Twala abamu ku bakadde ne ku bakabona,  
\v 2 ofulume ogende mu kiwonvu kya mutabani wa Kinomu ekiri awayingirirwa mu mulyango Kalusiisi, olangiririre eyo ebigambo bye nnaakutegeeza.  
\v 3 Ogambe nti, ‘Muwulire ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* mmwe bakabaka ba Yuda nammwe abali mu Yerusaalemi, bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Muwulirize! Ndireeta ekikangabwa mu kifo kino ekiriwaawaaza buli kutu.  
\v 4 Kubanga banvuddeko ekifo kino ne bakifuula ekya bakatonda abalala. Bookerezaamu ebiweebwayo eri bakatonda, bakitaabwe wadde bakabaka ba Yuda be batamanyangako, nga bajjuzza ekifo kino omusaayi gw’abataliiko musango.  
\v 5 Bazimbye ebifo ebigulumivu ebya Baali, bookereyo batabani baabwe mu muliro ng’ekiweebwayo eri Baali, ekintu kye siragiranga, era kye soogerangako, wadde okukirowoozaako.  
\v 6 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Mwegendereze, ennaku zijja, ng’ekifo kino abantu tebakyakiyita Tofesi newaakubadde Kiwonvu kya mutabani wa Kinomu, wabula nga bakiyita ekiwonvu eky’ettambiro. 
\p  
\v 7 “ ‘Mu kifo kino ndizikiriza entegeka za Yuda ne Yerusaalemi. Ne mbawaayo mu mikono gy’abalabe baabwe battibwe n’ekitala, era ndiwaayo emirambo gyabwe okuba emmere y’ebinyonyi eby’omu bbanga n’ebisolo eby’omu nsiko.  
\v 8 Ndidibaga ekibuga kino ne nkifuula eky’okusekererwa, n’abo bonna abayitawo bennyamire era baseke olw’ebiwundu byakyo byonna.  
\v 9 Olw’okuzingizibwa n’okunyigirizibwa abalabe baabwe abanoonya okubatta, ndibaliisa emirambo gya batabani baabwe n’egy’abawala baabwe era buli omu alirya munne.’ 
\p  
\v 10 “Awo n’olyoka omenya ensumbi abo b’ogenze n’abo nga balaba,  
\v 11 obagambe nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, Ndiyasaayasa eggwanga lino n’ekibuga kino ng’ensumbi y’omubumbi eno bw’engiyasaayasa nga tekikyayinzika kugiddaabiriza. Baliziika abafu mu Tofesi okutuusa ekifo awaziikibwa lwe kirijjula.  
\v 12 Kino kye ndikola ekifo kino n’abo abakibeeramu, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. Ekibuga kino ndikifuula nga Tofesi.  
\v 13 Amayumba g’omu Yerusaalemi n’aga bakabaka ba Yuda galiyonoonebwa ng’ago mu Tofesi, ennyumba zonna mwe booterezza obubaane eri eggye lyonna erya bakatonda ab’omu bbanga, ne baweerayo ekiweebwayo ekyokunywa.’ ” 
\p  
\v 14 Awo Yeremiya n’akomawo okuva e Tofesi \nd Mukama\nd* gye yali amutumye okuwa obunnabbi, n’ayimirira mu mbuga ya yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd* n’agamba abantu bonna nti,  
\v 15 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Muwulirize, ndireeta ku kibuga kino ne ku bubuga obukyetoolodde buli kikangabwa kyonna kye nakirangirirako, kubanga baakakanyaza ensingo zaabwe ne batagondera bigambo byange.’ ” 
\c 20  
\s1 Yeremiya Ayigganyizibwa ng’Abuulira 
\p  
\v 1 Awo Pasukuli eyali kabona mutabani wa Immeri, eyali omukulu mu yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*, yawulira nga Yeremiya awa obubaka buno,  
\v 2 n’alagira Yeremiya akubibwe. N’asibibwa mu nvuba eyali mu mulyango ogw’ekyengulu ogwa Benyamini ku yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 3 Olunaku olwaddirira, nga Pasukuli amusumuludde mu nvuba, Yeremiya n’amugamba nti, “\nd Mukama\nd* takyakuyita Pasukuli, naye Magolumissabibu.  
\v 4 Kubanga bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Laba, ndikufuula eky’entiisa, ekikangabwa, eri ggwe n’eri mikwano gyo bonna; era balifa ekitala ky’abalabe baabwe, n’amaaso go galikiraba, era Yuda yonna ndigiwaayo mu mukono gwa kabaka w’e Babulooni, alibatwala e Babulooni oba okubattisa ekitala.  
\v 5 Era ndigabula obugagga bw’ekibuga kino bwonna obulimu, n’eby’omuwendo omungi era n’eby’obugagga byonna ebya bakabaka ba Yuda mu mukono gw’abalabe baabwe. Balibutwala babwetikke ng’omunyago mu Babulooni.  
\v 6 Era ggwe Pasukuli, era n’abo bonna ab’omu nnyumba yo balitwalibwa mu busibe, e Babulooni. Eyo gy’olifiira era oziikibwe, ggwe ne mikwano gyo bonna b’otegeezezza obunnabbi obw’obulimba.’ ” 
\s1 Okwemulugunya kwa Yeremiya 
\q1  
\v 7 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, wannimba era n’ennimbibwa, 
\q2 wansinza amaanyi n’ompangula. 
\q1 Nvumibwa okuva ku makya okuzibya obudde, 
\q2 buli muntu ankudaalira. 
\q1  
\v 8 Buli lwe njogera, 
\q2 ndeekaana ne nnangirira akatabanguko n’okuzikirira. 
\q1 Kale ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kindeetera 
\q2 kuvumwa na kusekererwa buli lunaku. 
\q1  
\v 9 Naye bwe ŋŋamba nti, 
\q2 “Sijja kumwogerako oba okweyongera okwogera mu linnya lye,” 
\q1 ekigambo kye mu mutima gwange kiri ng’omuliro ogwaka, 
\q2 ogukwekeddwa mu magumba gange. 
\q1 Nkooye okukizibiikiriza 
\q2 era ddala sisobola. 
\q1  
\v 10 Mpulira bangi nga beegeya nti, “Akabi kali enjuuyi zonna. 
\q2 Mumuloope. 
\q2 Leka naffe tumuloope.” 
\q1 Mikwano gyange bonna 
\q2 banninda ngwe, 
\q1 nga bagamba nti, “Oboolyawo anaasobya, 
\q2 tumugweko 
\q2 tuwoolere eggwanga.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 Naye \nd Mukama\nd* ali nange ng’omulwanyi ow’amaanyi ow’entiisa, 
\q2 kale abanjigganya kyebaliva bagwa ne bataddayo kuyimirira. 
\q1 Baakulemererwa era baswalire ddala 
\q2 n’okuswala kwabwe tekulyerabirwa emirembe gyonna. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye oyo agezesa abatuukirivu, 
\q2 alaba ebiri munda mu mitima era n’ebirowoozo, 
\q1 kale leka ndabe bw’obawoolererako eggwanga, 
\q2 kubanga ensonga zange nzitadde mu mikono gyo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 Muyimbire \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q2 Mumuwe ettendo. 
\q1 Kubanga awonyezza obulamu bw’omunaku 
\q2 mu mikono gy’abo abakozi b’ebibi. 
\q1  
\v 14 Lukolimirwe 
\q2 olunaku kwe nazaalirwa! 
\q1 Olunaku mmange kwe yanzaalira 
\q2 luleme kuweebwa mukisa! 
\q1  
\v 15 Akolimirwe eyaleetera kitange amawulire, 
\q2 agaamusanyusa ennyo, 
\q2 ng’agamba nti, “Omwana omulenzi akuzaaliddwa.” 
\q1  
\v 16 Omusajja oyo abeere ng’ebibuga \nd Mukama\nd* bye yamenyaamenya 
\q2 awatali kusaasira kwonna. 
\q1 Okukaaba kuwulirwe ku makya, 
\q2 ne nduulu z’abalwanyi mu ttuntu. 
\q1  
\v 17 Yandinzitidde mu lubuto lwa mmange. 
\q2 Mmange yandibadde entaana yange, 
\q2 olubuto lwe ne luba lunene emirembe gyonna. 
\q1  
\v 18 Lwaki nava mu lubuto 
\q2 okulaba emitawaana n’obuyinike 
\q2 era ennaku zange ne nzimala mu buswavu? 
\c 21  
\s1 Katonda Agaana Okusaba kwa Zeddekiya 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo ekyajja eri Yeremiya okuva eri \nd Mukama\nd*, kabaka Zeddekiya bwe yamutumira Pasukuli mutabani wa Malukiya ne Zeffaniya kabona mutabani wa Maaseya okumugamba nti,  
\v 2 “Tubuulize kaakano ku \nd Mukama\nd* kubanga Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni atulumbye. Oboolyawo \nd Mukama\nd* anatukolera ekyamagero ng’edda, Nebukadduneeza n’atuleka.” 
\p  
\v 3 Naye Yeremiya n’abaddamu nti, “Mugambe Zeddekiya nti,  
\v 4 ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Nnaatera okuboolekeza ebyokulwanyisa byammwe ebiri mu mikono gyammwe bye mukozesa okulwanyisa kabaka w’e Babulooni n’Abakaludaaya ababazinze ne beetooloola ebweru wa bbugwe w’ekibuga kyammwe. Nzija kubakuŋŋaanyiza munda mu kibuga kino.  
\v 5 Nze kennyini nzija kubalwanyisa n’omukono gwange ogw’amaanyi, ogugoloddwa mu busungu, n’ekiruyi n’obukambwe obungi.  
\v 6 Era ndittisa kawumpuli omubi, abantu awamu n’ensolo enkambwe, mu kibuga kino.  
\v 7 Oluvannyuma lw’ekyo, nnaawaayo Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda, n’abakungu be n’abantu bonna mu kibuga kino abanaaba bawonye kawumpuli, ekitala n’enjala ebya Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni n’abalabe baabwe ababanoonya okubatta. Nebukadduneeza anaabatta n’ekitala, taabalage kisa n’akatono wadde okubasaasira oba okubasonyiwa.’ 
\p  
\v 8 “Era abantu bagambe nti, ‘Bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* bw’ayogera nti: Laba mbateereddewo ekkubo ery’obulamu era n’ekkubo ery’okufa.  
\v 9 Buli anaasigala mu kibuga kino ajja kufa ekitala, oba enjala oba kawumpuli. Naye buli afuluma ne yeewaayo eri Abakaludaaya ababazingizza, ajja kuba mulamu, era anaawonya obulamu bwe.  
\v 10 Mmaliridde okuleetera ekibuga kino akabi so si mirembe, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. Kijja kuweebwayo mu mikono gya kabaka w’e Babulooni, era ajja kukizikiriza n’omuliro.’ 
\p  
\v 11 “N’ekirala gamba ennyumba ya Yuda ey’obwakabaka nti, ‘Wulira ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*;  
\v 12 ggwe ennyumba ya Dawudi, 
\q1 “ ‘kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba: 
\q2 Musale emisango mu bwenkanya, 
\q2 mununule ababa banyagiddwa ababanyigiriza, 
\q1 obusungu bwange buleme kuvaayo 
\q2 bubookye ng’omuliro olw’ekibi kye mukoze, 
\q2 nga tewakyali n’omu abuziyiza. 
\q1  
\v 13 Laba nkugguddeko olutalo, 
\q2 ggwe Yerusaalemi abeera waggulu w’ekiwonvu, 
\q2 ku lusozi olwagaagavu olw’ekyaziyazi, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q1 mmwe abagamba nti, “Ani ayinza okutulumba? 
\q2 Ani ayinza okuyingira mu nnyumba zaffe?” 
\q1  
\v 14 Nzija kubabonereza ng’ebikolwa byammwe bwe biri, 
\q2 era ndikoleeza omuliro mu kibira kyammwe, 
\q1 gwokye byonna ebikyetoolodde,’ ” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\c 22  
\s1 Omusango eri Bakabaka Ababi 
\p  
\v 1 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Serengeta ogende mu lubiri lwa kabaka wa Yuda  
\v 2 olangirire obubaka buno nti, Wulira ekigambo kya Katonda ggwe kabaka wa Yuda, ggw’atuula ku ntebe ya Dawudi, mmwe abakungu n’abantu bammwe abayita mu miryango gino.  
\v 3 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Musale emisango egy’ensonga, mukole ebituufu. Anyagiddwako ebibye mumuggye mu mukono gw’oyo amujooga. Temukola kibi oba eby’obukambwe eri omugwira, newaakubadde atalina kitaawe, newaakubadde nnamwandu so temuyiwa musaayi gw’abantu abataliiko musango mu kifo kino.  
\v 4 Kubanga bwe muneegendereza ne mukuuma ebiragiro bino, olwo bakabaka abatuula ku ntebe ya Dawudi baliyita mu miryango gy’olubiri luno nga batudde mu magaali gaabwe n’abo abeebagadde embalaasi nga bawerekerwako n’abakungu baabwe, n’abantu baabwe.  
\v 5 ‘Naye bwe mutaagondere biragiro bino, nneelayirira ku lwange nti olubiri luno lulifuuka matongo,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\p  
\v 6 Kubanga kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba ku lubiri lwa kabaka wa Yuda nti, 
\q1 “Newaakubadde ng’oli nga Gireyaadi gye ndi, 
\q2 ng’entikko y’olusozi Lebanooni, 
\q1 ddala ddala nzija kukufuula ddungu, 
\q2 ng’ebibuga ebitaliimu bantu. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ndikusindikira abakuzikiriza, 
\q2 buli musajja n’ebyokulwanyisa bye, 
\q1 era balitema emivule gyo egisinga obulungi 
\q2 ne bagisuula mu muliro. 
\p  
\v 8 “Abantu abava mu mawanga amangi baliyita ku kibuga kino nga beebuuzaganya bokka ne bokka nti, ‘Lwaki \nd Mukama\nd* yakola ekintu ekifaanana bwe kiti ku kibuga kino ekikulu bwe kiti?’  
\v 9 Era eky’okuddamu kibeere nti, ‘Kubanga beerabira endagaano ya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe ne basinza era ne baweereza bakatonda abalala.’ ” 
\q1  
\v 10 Temukaabira kabaka afudde 
\q2 oba okumukungubagira, 
\q1 wabula mukaabire nnyo oyo omuwaŋŋanguse, 
\q2 kubanga taliddayo kulaba nsi ye nate. 
\m  
\v 11 Kubanga kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba ku Sallumu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda eyasikira Yosiya n’afuuka kabaka wa Yuda naye n’atwalibwa. “Talidda.  
\v 12 Alifiira eyo gye baamutwala nga musibe, taliraba nsi eno nate.” 
\q1  
\v 13 “Zimusanze oyo azimba olubiri ku butali butuukirivu, 
\q2 ebisenge bye ebya waggulu ku butali bwenkanya 
\q1 abantu b’ensi ye n’abakozeseza bwereere 
\q2 n’atabasasula mpeera yaabwe. 
\q1  
\v 14 Agamba nti, ‘Nzija kwezimbira olubiri olunene 
\q2 n’ebisenge ebya waggulu ebigazi ennyo.’ 
\q1 Kale nnaakola amadirisa amanene 
\q2 nnaateekamu emivule 
\q2 era nnaasiigako langi emyufu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 “Okweyongerayongera emivule emingi kikufuula kabaka? 
\q2 Kitaawo teyalina byakulya na byakunywa? 
\q1 Yakola ebituufu eby’obwenkanya. 
\q2 Noolwekyo byonna 
\q2 byamugendera bulungi. 
\q1  
\v 16 Yalwanirira abaavu n’abali mu bwetaavu 
\q2 kale byonna ne bimugendera bulungi. 
\q1 Ekyo si kye kitegeeza okummanya?” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 17 “Naye amaaso gammwe n’emitima gyammwe 
\q2 biri ku magoba ag’obukuusa, 
\q1 ne ku kuyiwa omusaayi ogutaliiko musango 
\q2 ne ku kunyigiriza ne ku kunyaga.” 
\m  
\v 18 Noolwekyo kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’ayogera ku Yekoyakimu omwana wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda nti, 
\q1 “Tebalimukungubagira; 
\q2 ‘Kikafuuwe, mukama wange!’ 
\q1 Kikafuuwe, 
\q2 obugagga bwe! 
\q1  
\v 19 Aliziikibwa 
\q2 nga bwe baziika endogoyi, 
\q2 akululwe asuulibwe ebweru w’enzigi za Yerusaalemi.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 “Genda mu Lebanooni okaabe, 
\q2 leka eddoboozi lyo liwulirwe mu Basani. 
\q1 Kaabira ku Abalimu, 
\q2 kubanga bonna ababadde ku ludda lwo bazikiridde. 
\q1  
\v 21 Nayogera gy’oli ng’okyali mu biseera byo eby’obugagga 
\q2 naye n’ogamba nti, ‘Sijja kuwuliriza!’ 
\q1 Bw’oti bw’obadde okuva mu buto bwo, 
\q2 togonderanga ku ddoboozi lyange. 
\q1  
\v 22 Empewo erikunguzza abalunzi b’ebisibo byo bonna, 
\q2 n’abawagizi bo batwalibwe mu buwaŋŋanguse. 
\q1 Olwo okwatibwe ensonyi 
\q2 oggweemu amaanyi olw’ebibi byo byonna. 
\q1  
\v 23 Mmwe abali mu Lebanooni,\f + \fr 22:23 \ft lwe lubiri oluli mu Yerusaalemi\f* 
\q2 abesulira mu bizimbe eby’emivule, 
\q1 nga mulikaaba, ng’obulumi bubajjidde! 
\q2 Okulumwa ng’okw’omukazi alumwa okuzaala. 
\p  
\v 24 “Ddala ddala nga bwe ndi omulamu, wadde ggwe Koniya omwana wa Yekoyakimu, singa wali mpeta ey’obuyinza ku mukono gwange ogwa ddyo, nandikusiseeko,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 25 “Ndikuwaayo eri abo abanoonya obulamu bwo, abo bootya, Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni era n’eri Abakaludaaya.  
\v 26 Ndikusuula mu nsi endala gye mutaazaalibwa, ggwe ne maama wo eyakuzaala, era eyo mwembi gye mulifiira.  
\v 27 Temulidda mu nsi gye mwegomba okuddamu.” 
\q1  
\v 28 Omusajja ono Koniya kintu ekinyoomebwa, 
\q2 ekimenyese, ekitaliiko ayagala? 
\q1 Lwaki ye n’abaana be balikanyugibwa ebweru, 
\q2 basuulibwe mu nsi gye batamanyi? 
\q1  
\v 29 Ayi ggwe ensi, ensi, 
\q2 wulira ekigambo kya Katonda! 
\q1  
\v 30 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Omusajja ono mumubale ng’atazaalangako 
\q2 kubanga tewali ku baana be alikulaakulana, 
\q1 alituula ku ntebe ya Dawudi 
\q2 oba aliddayo okufuga mu Yuda.” 
\c 23  
\s1 Ettabi Ettukuvu 
\p  
\v 1 “Zibasanze abasumba abazikiriza era abasaasaanya endiga z’ekisibo kyange!” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 2 Noolwekyo, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri ebikwata ku basumba abalabirira abantu bange nti, “Kubanga musaasaanyizza abantu bange ne mubagoba ne mutabalabirira, nzija kubaleetako ebibonerezo olw’ebibi bye mukoze,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 3 “Nze kennyini nzija kukuŋŋaanya abaasigalawo ku kisibo kyange okuva mu mawanga gonna gye nabagobera, mbakomyewo mu kisibo kyabwe, gye banaabalira ebibala beeyongere obungi.  
\v 4 Ndibawa abasumba abanaabalabirira, era tebaliddayo kutya oba kuggwaamu maanyi, era tewaabe n’omu abula,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 5 “Ennaku zijja, 
\q2 lwe ndiyimusiza Dawudi Ettabi ettukuvu, 
\q1 Kabaka alikulembera n’amagezi 
\q2 akole ebituufu eby’obwenkanya mu nsi,” bwayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 6 Mu mirembe gye, Yuda alirokolebwa 
\q2 ne Isirayiri alibeera mu mirembe. 
\q1 Lino lye linnya lye balimuyita: 
\q2 \nd Mukama\nd* Obutukuvu Bwaffe. 
\m  
\v 7 “Noolwekyo ennaku zijja, abantu lwe batalyogera nate nti, ‘Ddala nga \nd Mukama\nd* bwali omulamu eyaggya Abayisirayiri mu Misiri,’ bwayogera \nd Mukama\nd*,  
\v 8 naye bagambe nti, ‘Ddala nga \nd Mukama\nd* bw’ali omulamu, eyaggya abaana ba Isirayiri mu nsi ey’omu bukiikakkono era ne mu nsi zonna gye yali abagobedde.’ Olwo balibeera mu nsi yaabwe ku bwabwe,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\s1 Bannabbi Abalimba 
\p  
\v 9 Ebikwata ku bannabbi: 
\q1 omutima gwange gwennyise mu nda yange 
\q2 amagumba gange gonna gakankana, 
\q1 nninga omusajja omutamiivu, 
\q2 ng’omusajja afugiddwa omwenge, 
\q1 ku lwa \nd Mukama\nd* 
\q2 n’ebigambo bye ebitukuvu. 
\q1  
\v 10 Ensi ejjudde abenzi; 
\q2 olw’ekikolimo ensi esigadde nkalu 
\q2 era n’amalundiro g’omu ddungu meereere. 
\q1 Bannabbi bagoberera amakubo amabi 
\q2 era bakozesa obuyinza bwabwe mu butali bwenkanya. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 “Nnabbi ne kabona bombi tebalina Katonda, 
\q2 ne mu yeekaalu yange mbasanze nga bakoleramu ebibi,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 12 “Noolwekyo amakubo gaabwe gajja kuseerera 
\q2 era bajja kusuulibwa mu kizikiza 
\q2 era eyo gye baligwira. 
\q1 Ndibaleetako okuzikirira 
\q2 mu mwaka gwe balibonerezebwamu,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 13 “Mu bannabbi b’e Samaliya 
\q2 nalaba ekintu kino ekyenyinyalwa. 
\q1 Balagulira wansi wa Baali 
\q2 ne babuza abantu bange Isirayiri. 
\q1  
\v 14 Era ne mu bannabbi ba Yerusaalemi 
\q2 ndabye ekintu ekibi ennyo. 
\q2 Bakola eby’obwenzi ne batambulira mu bulimba. 
\q1 Bagumya abo abakozi b’ebibi 
\q2 ne wataba n’omu ava mu kwonoona kwe. 
\q1 Bonna bali nga Sodomu gye ndi; 
\q2 abantu ba Yerusaalemi bali nga Ggomola.” 
\p  
\v 15 Noolwekyo, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye ebikwata ku bannabbi nti, 
\q1 “Nzija kubaliisa emmere ekaawa 
\q2 banywe amazzi ag’obutwa, 
\q1 kubanga okuva mu bannabbi ba Yerusaalemi, 
\q2 obutatya Katonda bubunye mu nsi yonna.” 
\p  
\v 16 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’eggye nti, 
\q1 “Temuwuliriza bannabbi bye babategeeza: 
\q2 babajjuza essuubi ekyamu. 
\q1 Boogera ebirooto ebiva mu mitima gyabwe, 
\q2 so si ebiva mu kamwa ka \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 17 Bagamba abo abannyooma nti, 
\q2 ‘\nd Mukama\nd* Katonda agamba onoobeera n’emirembe.’ 
\q1 Abo abagoberera obukakanyavu bw’emitima gyabwe 
\q2 babagamba nti, ‘Tewali kabi kanaakujjira.’ 
\q1  
\v 18 Naye ani ku bo 
\q2 eyali abadde mu lukiiko lwa \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda okulaba 
\q2 oba okuwulira ekigambo kye? 
\q1  
\v 19 Laba, omuyaga gwa \nd Mukama\nd* 
\q2 gujja kubwatuka n’ekiruyi, 
\q1 empewo ey’akazimu 
\q2 eyetooloolera ku mitwe gy’abakozi b’ebibi. 
\q1  
\v 20 Obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* tebujja kukoma 
\q2 okutuusa ng’amaze okutuukiriza 
\q2 ekigendererwa ky’omutima gwe. 
\q1 Mu nnaku ezijja, mujja kukitegeera bulungi.  
\v 21 Situmanga bannabbi bano, 
\q2 songa bagenda 
\q2 badduka n’obubaka buno, 
\q1 era sogeranga nabo, 
\q2 songa bategeeza obunnabbi. 
\q1  
\v 22 Naye singa bayimirira mu maaso gange, 
\q2 bandibuulidde abantu bange ebigambo byange, 
\q1 era bandibaggye mu makubo gaabwe amabi 
\q2 era ne mu bikolwa byabwe ebibi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 “Ndi Katonda abeera okumpi wokka, 
\q2 so si abeera ewala?” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 24 “Omuntu ayinza okwekweka mu bifo eby’ekyama 
\q2 ne sisobola kumulaba?” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q2 “Sijjuza eggulu n’ensi?” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 25 “Mpulidde bannabbi aboogera eby’obulimba mu linnya lyange. Bagamba nti, ‘Naloose! Naloose!’  
\v 26 Kino kinaakoma ddi mu mitima gy’abo bannabbi b’obulimba, abategeeza eby’obulimba ebiva ku mitima gyabwe?  
\v 27 Balowooza nti ebirooto bye balootolola bannaabwe bijja kuleetera abantu bange okwerabira erinnya lyange, nga bakitaabwe bwe beerabira erinnya lyange nga basinza Baali.  
\v 28 Nnabbi alina ekirooto ayogere ekirooto kye, n’oyo alina ekigambo kyange akyogere mu bwesigwa. Kubanga ebisusunku birina nkolagana ki n’eŋŋaano?” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 29 “Ekigambo kyange tekiri nga muliro, ng’ennyondo eyasaayasa olwazi?” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 30 “Noolwekyo, ndi mulabe wa bannabbi ababbiŋŋanako ebigambo ebiva gye ndi,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 31 “Weewaawo,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, “saagalira ddala bannabbi abayogerayogera nga bagamba nti, ‘Bw’atyo \nd Mukama\nd* bw’agamba.’  
\v 32 Ddala ddala ndi mulabe w’abo abawa obunnabbi bw’ebirooto ebikyamu. Babyogera ne babuza abantu bange n’obulimba bwabwe obutaliimu, ate nga saabatuma wadde okubateekawo. Tebalina kye bayamba bantu bano n’akatono,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\s1 Obubaka Obukyamu ne Bannabbi Aboobulimba 
\p  
\v 33 “Abantu bano, oba nnabbi oba kabona bw’abuuza nti, ‘Bubaka ki \nd Mukama\nd* bw’atutumye?’ Bagambe nti, ‘Bubaka ki? Nzija kubabuulira, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.’  
\v 34 Nnabbi, oba kabona oba omuntu yenna bw’agamba nti, ‘Buno bwe bubaka bwa \nd Mukama\nd*,’ Nzija kubonereza omusajja oyo n’ab’omu maka ge.  
\v 35 Kino buli omu ky’anagamba mikwano gye oba ab’eŋŋanda ze. ‘\nd Mukama\nd*, azeemu ki? Oba kiki \nd Mukama\nd* ky’ayogedde?’  
\v 36 Naye temuddayo kugamba nti, ‘Buno bwe bubaka bwa \nd Mukama\nd*,’ kubanga buli kigambo kya muntu kifuuka bubaka bwe era mukyusa ebigambo bya Katonda omulamu, \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda waffe.  
\v 37 Kino kye munaabuuza nnabbi nti, ‘Kiki \nd Mukama\nd* kyakuzzeemu?’ Oba nti, ‘\nd Mukama\nd*, agambye ki?’  
\v 38 Naye era mujja kugamba nti, ‘Buno bwe bubaka \nd Mukama\nd* bwatutumye,’ wadde nga nabagamba nti, Temusaanye kwogera nti, ‘Buno bwe bubaka bwa \nd Mukama\nd*,’  
\v 39 kyenaava mbagobera ddala mu maaso gange ne mu kibuga ekyo kye nabawa, mmwe ne bakitammwe.  
\v 40 Ndibaleetako ekivume ekitaliggwaawo, n’ensonyi ez’olubeerera ebitagenda kwerabirwa.” 
\c 24  
\s1 Ebibbo by’Emitiini 
\p  
\v 1 Yekoyakini mutabani wa Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda n’abakungu, n’abaweesi n’abafundi ba Yuda bwe baatwalibwa kabaka Nebukadduneeza mu buwaŋŋanguse mu Babulooni okuva mu Yerusaalemi, \nd Mukama\nd* yandaga ebibbo bibiri eby’emitiini nga biteekeddwa mu maaso ga yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 2 Ekibbo ekimu kyalimu ettiini nga nnungi nnyo ng’eyo esooka okwengera, n’ekibbo ekirala kyalimu ettiini nga mbi nnyo, ezitayinza kuliika. 
\p  
\v 3 \nd Mukama\nd* n’ambuuza nti, “Olaba ki Yeremiya?” Ne muddamu nti, “Ndaba ettiini. Ennungi nga nnungi nnyo naye embi nga mbi nnyo ezitayinza kuliika.” 
\p  
\v 4 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kinzijira nti,  
\v 5 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Ng’ettiini zino ennungi, ndaba nti abawaŋŋanguse b’omu Yuda balungi, be natwala okuva mu kifo kino eri mu nsi ey’Abakaludaaya.  
\v 6 Amaaso gange gajja kubalabirira olw’obulungi bwabwe, era nzija kubakomyawo mu nsi eno. Nzija kubazimba era nneme kubamenyaamenya: nzija kubasimba nneme kubakuula.  
\v 7 Ndibawa omutima bammanye, nti nze \nd Mukama\nd*. Balibeera bantu bange, nange ndibeera Katonda waabwe, kubanga balidda gye ndi n’omutima gwabwe gwonna. 
\p  
\v 8 “ ‘Naye ng’ettiini embi, embi ennyo ezitayinzika kuliika, bwe ntyo bwe nnaakola Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda, n’abakungu be n’abo abaasigalawo mu Yerusaalemi, oba abaasigalawo mu nsi eno oba abo ababeera mu Misiri,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 9 ‘Ndibafuula kyennyinnyalwa era eky’omuzizo eri amawanga g’ensi, eky’okusekererwa era olugero obugero, ekintu eky’okusekererwa era eky’okukolimirwanga yonna gye nnaabagoberanga.  
\v 10 Ndireeta ekitala, n’ekyeya, ne kawumpuli okubalumba okutuusa lwe balizikirira babule ku nsi gye nabawa ne bakitaabwe.’ ” 
\c 25  
\s1 Emyaka Nsanvu egy’Obusibe 
\p  
\v 1 Ekigambo ekikwata ku bantu bonna aba Yuda ne kijjira Yeremiya mu mwaka ogwokuna ogw’obufuzi bwa Yekoyakimu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda, ogwali omwaka ogusooka ogw’obufuzi bwa kabaka Nebukadduneeza mu bwakabaka bwa Babulooni.  
\v 2 Awo Yeremiya nnabbi n’agamba abantu bonna aba Yuda n’abantu bonna abaali mu Yerusaalemi nti,  
\v 3 Okuva mu mwaka ogw’ekkumi n’esatu ogw’obufuzi bwa Yosiya mutabani wa Amoni kabaka wa Yuda, gy’emyaka amakumi abiri mu esatu okutuusa leero, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kizze gye ndi era njogedde gye muli emirundi mingi, naye temufuddeeyo. 
\p  
\v 4 Newaakubadde nga \nd Mukama\nd* abaweerezza bannabbi be emirundi mingi, temuwulirizza wadde okufaayo.  
\v 5 Babagamba nti, “Mukyuke kaakano, buli omu ku mmwe okuva mu bikolwa bye ebibi, mulyoke musigale mu nsi \nd Mukama\nd* gye yabawa mmwe ne bakitammwe emirembe gyonna.  
\v 6 Temugoberera bakatonda balala, temubaweereza wadde okubasinza; temunsunguwaza olw’ekyo emikono gyammwe kye gyakola, nneme okubakolako obulabe.” 
\p  
\v 7 “Naye temwampuliriza, mwansunguwaza n’ekyo kye mwakola n’emikono gyammwe, era ne mwereetera akabi,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\p  
\v 8 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, “Kubanga temuwulirizza bigambo byange,  
\v 9 nzija kukoowoola abantu bonna ab’omu bukiikakkono n’omuddu wange Nebukadduneeza, balumbe ensi eno n’abantu baamu era n’ensi zonna ezibeetoolodde. Nzija kuzizikiririza ddala nzifuule ekintu eky’entiisa era eky’okusekererwa, era zoonoonekere ddala.  
\v 10 Ndibagobako eddoboozi ery’essanyu era n’okujaguza, eddoboozi ery’awasa omugole n’ery’omugole, eddoboozi ly’olubengo n’okwaka kw’ettaala.  
\v 11 Ensi eno yonna ejja kufuuka matongo, n’amawanga gano gajja kuweereza kabaka w’e Babulooni emyaka nsanvu. 
\p  
\v 12 “Naye emyaka ensanvu bwe giriggwako, ndibonereza kabaka w’e Babulooni n’eggwanga lye, ensi ya Babulooni olw’ekibi kyabwe, ngifuule matongo emirembe gyonna,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 13 “Ndireeta ku nsi eno ebintu byonna bye njogeddeko, ebyo byonna ebiwandiikiddwa ku muzingo guno era ne Yeremiya byategeezezza amawanga gano gonna.  
\v 14 Bo bennyini balifuulibwa baddu ba mawanga mangi era baddu ba bakabaka ab’ekitiibwa; ndibasasula ng’ebikolwa byabwe bwe biri n’emirimu gy’emikono gyabwe bwe giri.” 
\s1 Ekikopo ky’Obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* 
\p  
\v 15 Bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri bwe yaŋŋamba nti, “Twala ekikopo kino, okuva mu mukono gwange, ekijjudde wayini ow’obusungu bwange, okinywese amawanga gonna gye nnaakutuma okukibanywesa.  
\v 16 Bwe banaakinywa, bajja kugwa eddalu batagale olw’ekitala kye nnaabasindikamu.” 
\p  
\v 17 Awo ne ntwala ekikopo okuva mu Mukono gwa \nd Mukama\nd* ne nkitwala eri amawanga gonna gye yantuma okukibanywesa; 
\b  
\li1  
\v 18 Yerusaalemi n’ebibuga bya Yuda, ne bakabaka baabyo n’abakungu basaanewo era bafuuke ekintu eky’entiisa n’okuzikirira, n’okusekererwa n’ekikolimo nga bwe bali kaakano. 
\li1  
\v 19 Falaawo, ye kabaka w’e Misiri, ne bakalabaalaba be, n’abakungu be n’abantu be bonna,  
\v 20 n’abagwira bonna abaaliyo; 
\li1 bakabaka ba Uzi bonna, 
\li1 ne bakabaka b’Abafirisuuti bonna, abo ab’e Asukulooni, n’e Gaza, n’e Ekuloni, n’abantu abaalekebwa e Asudodi, 
\li1  
\v 21 n’e Edomu, n’e Mowaabu n’e Ammoni, 
\li1  
\v 22 bakabaka bonna ab’e Tuulo ne Sidoni, bakabaka ab’oku lubalama ng’osomose ennyanja; 
\li1  
\v 23 Dedani, n’e Teema, n’e Buuzi n’abo bonna abali mu bifo eby’ewala, 
\li1  
\v 24 ne bakabaka bonna ab’e Buwalabu, ne bakabaka b’abannamawanga ababeera mu ddungu; 
\li1  
\v 25 ne bakabaka bonna ab’e Zimuli, n’e Eramu n’e Meedi; 
\li1  
\v 26 n’abo bonna bakabaka ab’omu bukiikakkono, abeewala, n’ab’okumpi, omu ku omu, obwakabaka bwonna obuli ku nsi. 
\li1 Oluvannyuma lwabo kabaka w’e Sesaki naye balikinywa. 
\b  
\p  
\v 27 “Era onoobagamba nti, ‘Bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Munywe mutamiire, museseme, mugwe muleme kuddayo kusituka olw’ekitala ekyo kye ŋŋenda okusindika mu mmwe.’  
\v 28 Naye bwe bagaana okuggya ekikopo mu mukono gwo okukinywa, bagambe nti, ‘Kino \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye ky’agamba nti, Muteekwa okukinywa!  
\v 29 Laba, ntandika okuzikiriza ekibuga ekiyitibwa Erinnya lyange, ddala munaagenda nga temubonerezeddwa? Mujja kubonerezebwa kubanga nkoowoola ekitala kikke ku abo bonna abali ku nsi, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye.’ 
\p  
\v 30 “Kaakano bategeeze ebigambo bino byonna obagambe nti, 
\q1 “ ‘\nd Mukama\nd* Katonda anaayogerera waggulu, 
\q2 era anaayimusa eddoboozi lye okuva mu kifo kye ekitukuvu 
\q2 awulugume n’amaanyi mangi nnyo ng’awakanya bonna abali mu nsi. 
\q1 Ajja kuleekaana ng’abasogozi abasamba emizabbibu, 
\q2 ng’aleekaanira abo abali ku nsi. 
\q1  
\v 31 Eddoboozi lye liriwulirwa n’ensi gy’ekoma. 
\q2 Kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* alisalira amawanga emisango gy’abavunaana, 
\q2 alisalira abantu bonna omusango, atte ababi n’ekitala,’ ” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 32 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Laba okuzikirira kugenda kusaasaana kuva nsi ku nsi; 
\q2 enkuba ey’amaanyi ejja kuva ku nkomerero y’ensi.” 
\m  
\v 33 Mu kiseera ekyo abo abattiddwa \nd Mukama\nd* bajja kubeera buli wamu okuva ku nsonda emu ey’ensi okutuuka ku ndala. Tebajja kukungubagirwa wadde okukuŋŋaanyizibwa oba okuziikibwa, naye banaaba ng’obusa obulekeddwa ku ttaka. 
\q1  
\v 34 Mukaabe mulaajane mmwe abasumba, 
\q2 mwevulunge mu ttaka, mmwe abakulu b’ebisibo. 
\q1 Kubanga obudde bwammwe obw’okuttibwa butuuse 
\q2 mujja kugwa mubetentebwe ng’ebibya eby’ebbumba. 
\q1  
\v 35 Abasumba tebaabeeko na buddukiro, 
\q2 n’abakulu b’ebisibo tebaabeeko na wa kwekweka. 
\q1  
\v 36 Muwulire okukaaba kw’abasumba, 
\q2 okwaziirana kw’abanannyini b’ebisibo, 
\q2 kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* alizikiriza amalundiro gaabwe. 
\q1  
\v 37 Amalundiro amalungi galifuuka matongo 
\q2 olw’obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* obubuubuuka. 
\q1  
\v 38 Ajja kuleka ekisulo kye 
\q2 ng’empologoma bw’eva w’esula, 
\q1 n’ensi yaabwe ejja kusigala njereere olw’ekitala ky’omulumbaganyi 
\q2 era n’olw’obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* obw’entiisa. 
\c 26  
\s1 Yeremiya Atiisibwatiisibwa Okuttibwa 
\p  
\v 1 Awo Yekoyakimu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda nga yakalya obwakabaka, ekigambo kino kyajja okuva eri \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Yimirira mu luggya lw’ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* oyogere eri abantu bonna ab’ebibuga bya Yuda abazze okusinza mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*. Bagambe byonna bye nkulagira; tobaako na ky’olekayo.  
\v 3 Oboolyawo banaawulira, buli muntu n’akyuka okuva mu makubo ge amabi. Olwo nnejjuse nneme kubaleetako kikangabwa kyembadde ntegeka olw’okwonoona kwabwe.  
\v 4 Bagambe, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Bwe mutampulirize ne mugoberera amateeka gange ge mbawadde,  
\v 5 era bwe mutaawulirize bigambo bya baddu bange bannabbi, be mbatumidde emirundi emingi wadde nga temubafuddeeko,  
\v 6 ndifuula enju eno nga Siiro era n’ekibuga kino ng’ekintu eky’okukolimirwa mu mawanga ag’ensi.’ ” 
\p  
\v 7 Bakabona ne bannabbi n’abantu bonna ne bawulira Yeremiya ng’ayogera ebigambo bino mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 8 Naye nga Yeremiya ya kamaliriza okubuulira abantu bonna ebintu byonna \nd Mukama\nd* bye yali amulagidde okwogera, bakabona ne bannabbi, n’abantu bonna ne bamukwata ne bagamba nti, “Oteekwa okufa!  
\v 9 Lwaki oyogera ebyobunnabbi mu linnya lya \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Ennyumba eno eneebeera nga Siiro, n’ekibuga kino kinaakubwa kisigale matongo?” Awo abantu bonna ne beetooloola Yeremiya mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 10 Awo abakungu ba Yuda bwe baawulira ebigambo bino, ne bava mu lubiri ne bambuka mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ne batuula mu bifo byabwe awayingirirwa ku Mulyango Omuggya ogw’ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 11 Awo bakabona ne bannabbi ne bagamba abakungu n’abantu bonna nti, “Omusajja ono asaana kusalirwa musango gwa kufa kubanga ayogedde ebyobunnabbi ebibi ku kibuga kino. Mukiwulidde n’amatu gammwe gennyini.” 
\p  
\v 12 Awo Yeremiya n’agamba abakungu bonna n’abantu bonna nti, “\nd Mukama\nd* yantuma njogere ebyobunnabbi bwe bityo ku nnyumba eno n’ekibuga kino ebintu byonna bye muwulidde.  
\v 13 Kaakano mukyuse amakubo gammwe n’ebikolwa byammwe mugondere \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wammwe. Olwo \nd Mukama\nd* anaakyusa n’ataleeta bikangabwa by’aboogeddeko.  
\v 14 Nze, ndi mu mikono gyammwe; munkole kyonna kye mulowooza nga kye kirungi era kye kituufu.  
\v 15 Mumanyire ddala nno nti bwe munzita, mujja kwereetako omusango gw’okuyiwa omusaayi ogutalina musango, mmwe n’ekibuga kino n’abo abakibeeramu, kubanga eky’amazima \nd Mukama\nd* ye yantumye okwogera gye muli ebigambo bino byonna mubiwulire.” 
\p  
\v 16 Awo abakungu n’abantu bonna ne bagamba bakabona ne bannabbi nti, “Omusajja ono tasaana kusalirwa musango gwa kufa! Ayogedde naffe mu linnya lya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe.” 
\p  
\v 17 Abamu ku bakadde ne bavaayo ne bajja mu maaso ne boogera eri ekibiina kyonna eky’abantu nti,  
\v 18 “Mikka ow’e Moreseesi yawa obunnabbi mu nnaku za Keezeekiya kabaka wa Yuda. Yagamba abantu bonna aba Yuda nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Sayuuni ajja kulimibwa ng’ennimiro, 
\q2 Yerusaalemi ajja kufuuka ntuumu ya mafunfugu, 
\q2 olusozi lwa yeekaalu, lufuuke akasozi akamezeeko ebisaka.’  
\m  
\v 19 Keezeekiya oba omuntu omulala yenna mu Yuda, yamutta? Keezeekiya teyatya \nd Mukama\nd* n’anoonya ekisa kye? Era \nd Mukama\nd* teyakyusa n’ataleeta kuzikirira kwe yali agambye okubaleetako? Naye tunaatera okwereetera obulabe obw’amaanyi!” 
\p  
\v 20 Waaliwo omusajja omulala Uliya omwana wa Semaaya ow’e Kiriyasuyalimu, eyawa obunnabbi mu linnya lya \nd Mukama\nd*. Yawa obunnabbi bwe bumu ng’obwa Yeremiya obugugumbula ekibuga kino era n’ensi eno.  
\v 21 Wabula kabaka Yekoyakimu n’abakungu be bonna n’abasajja be n’ab’obuyinza, bwe baawulira ebigambo bye, kabaka n’amunoonya okumutta, naye Uliya bwe yakiwulira n’atya n’addukira e Misiri.  
\v 22 Awo kabaka Yekoyakimu n’atuma Erunasani mutabani wa Akubooli n’abasajja abawerako,  
\v 23 ne baggya Uliya e Misiri ne bamutwala eri kabaka Yekoyakimu, eyalagira attibwe n’ekitala omulambo gwe ne gusuulibwa mu kifo ekiziikibwamu ekya lukale. 
\p  
\v 24 Akikamu mutabani wa Safani n’awolereza Yeremiya n’amuwagira n’ataweebwayo eri bantu kuttibwa. 
\c 27  
\s1 Yuda Alibeera Muddu wa Nebukadduneeza 
\p  
\v 1 Ku ntandikwa y’obufuuzi bwa Zeddekiya mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda, ekigambo kino kyajjira Yeremiya okuva eri \nd Mukama\nd*:  
\v 2 Bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* bwe yaŋŋamba nti: “Weekolere ekikoligo okiteeke ku nsingo yo,  
\v 3 oweereze ekigambo eri bakabaka ba Edomu, ne Mowaabu, ne Ammoni, ne Tuulo ne Sidoni, ng’otuma ababaka abazze mu Yerusaalemi eri Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda.  
\v 4 Tumira bakama baabwe obagambe nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, “Kino mukitegeeze bakama bammwe.  
\v 5 N’amaanyi gange amangi n’omukono ogugoloddwa natonda ensi n’abantu baamu n’ensolo ezigiriko, era ngiwa omuntu yenna gwe njagala.  
\v 6 Kaakano ŋŋenda kuwaayo amawanga gammwe eri omuddu wange Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni, n’ensolo ez’omu nsiko nzija kuziteeka wansi we.  
\v 7 Amawanga gonna galimuweereza ne mutabani we ne muzzukulu we okutuusa ekiseera eky’ensi ye okusalirwa omusango lwe kirituuka; olwo amawanga mangi ne bakabaka bangi ab’amaanyi balimuwangula. 
\p  
\v 8 “ ‘ “Naye singa eggwanga lyonna oba obwakabaka bwonna tebuliweereza Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni oba okuteeka ensingo wansi w’ekikoligo ky’abwo, nzija kubonereza ensi eyo n’ekitala, n’ekyeya, ne kawumpuli, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, okutuusa lwe ndigizikiriza n’omukono gwange.  
\v 9 Noolwekyo bannabbi bammwe, n’abalaguzi, n’abavvuunuzi b’ebirooto, temubawuliriza wadde abalogo wadde abafumu ababagamba nti, ‘Temulibeera baddu ba kabaka w’e Babulooni.’  
\v 10 Baabawa bunnabbi bwa bulimba obunaabaleetera okutwalibwa ewala okuva mu mawanga gammwe. Ndibagobera wala era mulizikirira.  
\v 11 Naye singa eggwanga lirikutamya ensingo yaalyo wansi w’ekikoligo kya kabaka w’e Babulooni limuweereze, nzija kuleka eggwanga eryo lisigale mu nsi yaalyo, okugirima, n’okugibeeramu, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.” ’ ” 
\p  
\v 12 Nategeeza obubaka bwe bumu eri Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda nga ŋŋamba nti, “Kutamya ensingo yo wansi w’ekikoligo kya kabaka w’e Babulooni, beera omuddu we n’abantu be, onoobeera mulamu.  
\v 13 Lwaki ggwe n’abantu bo mufa ekitala, n’ekyeya ne kawumpuli \nd Mukama\nd* by’agambye okutuuka ku nsi yonna eteefuuke muddu wa kabaka w’e Babulooni?  
\v 14 Towuliriza bigambo bya bannabbi abakugamba nti, ‘Tolibeera muddu wa kabaka w’e Babulooni,’ kubanga bakutegeeza bya bulimba.  
\v 15 ‘Sibatumanga,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. ‘Bawa obunnabbi bwa bulimba mu linnya lyange. Noolwekyo, nzija kubagobera wala muzikirire, mmwe ne bannabbi ababategeeza obunnabbi.’ ” 
\p  
\v 16 Olwo ne ŋŋamba bakabona n’abantu bano bonna nti, “Kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba nti, Temuwuliriza bannabbi abagamba nti, ‘Amangu ddala ebintu by’omu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* bijja kukomezebwawo okuva mu Babulooni.’ Bababuulira bunnabbi bwa bulimba.  
\v 17 Temubawuliriza. Muweereze kabaka w’e Babulooni, mubeere balamu. Lwaki ekibuga kino kifuuka amatongo?  
\v 18 Bwe baba bannabbi nga balina ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*, leka bakaabirire \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti ebintu eby’omuwendo ebikyasigadde mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ne mu lubiri lwa kabaka wa Yuda ne mu Yerusaalemi bireme kutwalibwa Babulooni.  
\v 19 Kubanga bw’ati \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye bw’ayogera ku mpagi, n’Ennyanja, okuteekebwa ebintu, n’ebintu ebirala ebisigadde mu kibuga kino,  
\v 20 kabaka Nebukadduneeza ow’e Babulooni by’ataatwala lwe yatwala Yekoyakini mutabani wa Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda n’abakungu bonna aba Yuda ne Yerusaalemi.  
\v 21 Bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri ku bikwata ku bibya ebyasigala mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ne mu lubiri olwa kabaka wa Yuda ne mu Yerusaalemi nti,  
\v 22 ‘Biritwalibwa mu Babulooni eyo gye birisigala okutuusa ku lunaku lwe ndibikima, olwo ndibikomyawo mbizze mu kifo kino,’ ” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\c 28  
\s1 Kananiya Nnabbi ow’Obulimba 
\p  
\v 1 Mu mwezi ogwokutaano ogw’omwaka gwe gumu, gwe mwaka ogwokuna, obufuzi bwa Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda nga bw’akatandika, nnabbi Kananiya omwana wa Azuri eyali abeera e Gibyoni n’aŋŋambira mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* nga bakabona n’abantu bonna we bali nti,  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Nzija kumenya ekikoligo kya kabaka w’e Babulooni.  
\v 3 Emyaka ebiri nga teginnaggwaako, ndikomyawo ebintu by’omu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* mu kifo kino, Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni bye yaggya wano n’abitwala e Babulooni.  
\v 4 Era ndikomyawo wano Yekoyakini mutabani wa Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda n’abantu abalala bonna abaava mu Yuda abaatwalibwa e Babulooni,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘kubanga ndimenya ekikoligo kya kabaka w’e Babulooni.’ ” 
\p  
\v 5 Awo nnabbi Yeremiya n’addamu mu bunnabbi bwa Kananiya nga ne bakabona n’abantu bonna we bali bayimiridde mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*, n’agamba nti,  
\v 6 “Amiina! Bw’atyo \nd Mukama\nd* bw’aba akola! \nd Mukama\nd* atuukirize ebigambo by’oyogedde ng’akomyawo ebintu eby’omu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* era n’abawambe bonna abakomyewo mu kifo kino okuva mu Babulooni.  
\v 7 Wabula, wuliriza kye ŋŋenda okwogera ng’owuliriza n’abantu bano bonna nga bawulira.  
\v 8 Okuva edda n’edda bannabbi abaatusooka, ggwe nange baategeezanga kubaawo kwa ntalo, na bikangabwa na kawumpuli okugwa ku mawanga n’obwakabaka obw’amaanyi.  
\v 9 Naye nnabbi eyategeeza obunnabbi obw’emirembe ajja kulabibwa nga ddala atumiddwa \nd Mukama\nd* era ng’obubaka bw’ategeeza butuukiridde.” 
\p  
\v 10 Awo nnabbi Kananiya n’alyoka akwata ekikoligo ekyali ku nsingo ya Yeremiya n’akimenya,  
\v 11 n’alyoka ayogera eri abantu bonna nti, “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Mu ngeri y’emu bw’eti, bwe ndimenya ekikoligo ekya Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni okuva ku mawanga gonna mu myaka ebiri.’ ” Naye ye nnabbi Yeremiya n’avaawo ne yeetambulira. 
\p  
\v 12 Bwe waayitawo ebbanga ttono nga nnabbi Kananiya amenye ekikoligo ku nsingo ya Yeremiya, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 13 “Genda ogambe Kananiya nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Omenye ekikoligo kya muti naye mu kifo kyakyo ojja kufunamu kikoligo kya kyuma.  
\v 14 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Nditeeka ekikoligo eky’ekyuma mu nsingo z’amawanga gano gonna baweereze Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni era balimuweereza. Ndimuwa obuyinza n’ensolo azifuge.’ ” 
\p  
\v 15 Awo nnabbi Yeremiya n’agamba nnabbi Kananiya nti, “Wuliriza, Kananiya! \nd Mukama\nd* tannakutuma naye ggwe owalirizza eggwanga lino okwesiga obulimba.  
\v 16 Noolwekyo kino \nd Mukama\nd* kyagamba nti, ‘Ndikumpi okukuggya ku nsi. Omwaka guno gwennyini ogenda kufa, kubanga oyigirizza abantu okujeemera \nd Mukama\nd*.’ ” 
\p  
\v 17 Mu mwezi ogw’omusanvu ogw’omwaka gwe gumu, Kananiya n’afa. 
\c 29  
\s1 Ebbaluwa eri Abawaŋŋanguse 
\p  
\v 1 Bino bye byali mu bbaluwa nnabbi Yeremiya gye yaweereza okuva mu Yerusaalemi eri abakadde abaali bakyasigaddewo mu bawaŋŋanguse n’eri bakabona, ne bannabbi n’abantu bonna Nebukadduneeza be yali atutte mu buwaŋŋanguse mu Babulooni okuva mu Yerusaalemi.  
\v 2 Kino kyaliwo nga kabaka Yekoyakini n’abakungu be ne Namasole we n’abakulembeze ba Yuda ne Yerusaalemi, n’abafundi n’abaweesi bonna baggyiddwa mu Yerusaalemi.  
\v 3 Ebbaluwa yagiwa Erasa mutabani wa Safani ne Bemaliya mutabani wa Kirukiya, ne Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda be yatuma eri kabaka Nebukadduneeza mu Babulooni. Yali egamba bw’eti nti, 
\pm  
\v 4 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri, ng’agamba abo bonna be natwala mu buwaŋŋanguse okuva mu Yerusaalemi okugenda mu Babulooni nti,  
\v 5 “Mwezimbire amayumba mutuule omwo; mulime ennimiro mulye ebibala byamu.  
\v 6 Muwase muzaale abaana aboobulenzi n’aboobuwala; muwasize batabani bammwe abakazi, ne bawala bammwe mubafumbize, nabo bazaale abaana abalenzi n’abawala. Mweyongere obungi eyo, temukendeera.  
\v 7 Era munoonye emirembe n’okukulaakulana kw’ekibuga gye mbatutte mu buwaŋŋanguse. Musabenga \nd Mukama\nd*, ekibuga mukisabire kubanga bwe kikulaakulana nammwe mujja kukulaakulana.”  
\v 8 Ddala kino \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri ky’agamba nti, “Temukkiriza bannabbi n’abalaguzi abali mu mmwe kubalimbalimba. Temussaayo mwoyo ku birooto byabwe bye babalootolola.  
\v 9 Babategeeza obunnabbi bwa bulimba mu linnya lyange. Sibatumanga,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\pm  
\v 10 Ddala ddala bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Emyaka nsanvu nga giweddeko e Babulooni, ndijja gye muli ntuukirize ekisuubizo kyange eky’ekisa mbakomyewo mu kifo kino.  
\v 11 Kubanga mmanyi enteekateeka ze nnina gye muli, enteekateeka ez’okubakulaakulanya so si okubakolako akabi, enteekateeka ez’okubawa essuubi era n’obulamu obw’omu maaso,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 12 “Awo mulimpita ne mujja ne munsaba, nange ne mbawulira,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 13 “Mulinnoonya ne mundaba bwe mulinnoonya n’omutima gwammwe gwonna.  
\v 14 Mulinzuula era ndibakomyawo okubaggya mu buwaŋŋanguse. Ndibakuŋŋaanya mu mawanga gonna n’ebifo byonna, gye nabagobera, era ndibakomyawo mu kifo mwe nabaggya okubatwala mu buwaŋŋanguse,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\pm  
\v 15 Muyinza okugamba nti, “\nd Mukama\nd* atuyimusirizza bannabbi mu Babulooni.”  
\v 16 Naye kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba ku kabaka atuula ku ntebe ya Dawudi n’abantu bonna abaasigala mu kibuga kino, n’abantu ab’ensi yammwe abataagenda nammwe mu buwaŋŋanguse.  
\v 17 Bw’ati bwayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, “Ndisindika ekitala, n’enjala ne kawumpuli okubalumba era mbafuule ng’emitiini emibi ennyo egitayinza kuliika olw’obubi bwagyo.  
\v 18 Ndibagoberera n’ekitala, n’enjala ne kawumpuli ne mbafuula ekyenyinyalwa eri obwakabaka bwonna obw’ensi era ekikolimo n’ekikangabwa, n’eky’okusekererwa n’okuvumwa eri amawanga gonna gye ndibagobera.  
\v 19 Kubanga tebaawuliriza bigambo byange,” bwayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, “ebigambo bye nabatumira emirundi emingi mu baweereza bange bannabbi. Era nammwe abawaŋŋanguse temuwulirizza,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\pm  
\v 20 Noolwekyo, muwulirize ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*, mmwe mwenna abali mu buwaŋŋanguse be nagoba mu Yerusaalemi okugenda mu Babulooni.  
\v 21 Kino \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri, ky’ayogera ku Akabu mutabani wa Kolaya ne Zeddekiya mutabani wa Maaseya, abaawa obunnabbi mu linnya lyange nti, “Ndibawaayo eri Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni, abatte nga mulaba.  
\v 22 Olw’abasajja abo, abali mu buwaŋŋanguse bonna abaava mu Yuda abali mu Babulooni balikozesa ekikolimo kino nti, ‘\nd Mukama\nd* akukole nga bwe yakola Zeddekiya ne Akabu, kabaka w’e Babulooni be yayokya mu muliro.’  
\v 23 Kubanga bakoze eby’ekivve mu Isirayiri; bakoze obwenzi ne baka baliraanwa baabwe era ne boogera eby’obulimba mu linnya lyange, bye sibagambanga kwogera. Nkimanyi era ndi mujulirwa ku ekyo,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\s1 Obubaka eri Semaaya 
\p  
\v 24 Semaaya Omunekeramu mugambe nti,  
\v 25 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Waweereza ebbaluwa mu mannya go eri abantu bonna mu Yerusaalemi, eri Zeffaniya mutabani wa Maaseya kabona ne bakabona bonna. Wagamba Zeffaniya nti,  
\v 26 ‘\nd Mukama\nd* yakuteekawo okuba kabona mu kifo kya Yekoyaada okutwala obuvunaanyizibwa ku nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*; oteekwa okuteeka omulalu yenna eyefuula nga nnabbi mu nvuba ne mu masamba.  
\v 27 Noolwekyo lwaki tokangavudde Yeremiya ow’e Yanasosi, eyefuula nnabbi wakati mu mmwe?  
\v 28 Atuweerezza obubaka buno mu Babulooni ng’agamba nti, Obuwaŋŋanguse bwammwe bujja kubeera bwa bbanga ddene. Noolwekyo mwezimbire amayumba mutereere mu nsi, mulime ennimiro mulye ebibala byamu.’ ” 
\p  
\v 29 Wabula Zeffaniya kabona nasomera nnabbi Yeremiya ebbaluwa eno.  
\v 30 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 31 “Muweereze obubaka buno eri abawaŋŋanguse nti, ‘Kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba ku Semaaya Omunekeramu. Kubanga Semaaya yakuwa obunnabbi, wadde nga ssamutuma, era akutuusizza ku kwesiga eby’obulimba,  
\v 32 kino \nd Mukama\nd* ky’agamba nti, Ddala ddala ndibonereza Semaaya Omunekeramu n’abantu b’omu nju ye. Tewaliba n’omu alisigalawo ku bantu be, wadde aliraba ebirungi bye ndikolera abantu bange, kubanga ayigirizza abantu okunjeemera, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.’ ” 
\c 30  
\s1 Isirayiri Azzibwawo 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ekyajjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Wandiika ku muzingo ebigambo byonna bye njogedde naawe.  
\v 3 Ennaku zijja, lwe ndikomyawo abantu bange Isirayiri ne Yuda okuva mu busibe, mbazzeeyo mu nsi gye nawa bajjajjaabwe babeere omwo,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\p  
\v 4 Bino bye bigambo \nd Mukama\nd* bye yayogera ebikwata ku Isirayiri ne Yuda nti,  
\v 5 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Emiranga egy’okutya giwulirwa, 
\q2 bulabe teri mirembe. 
\q1  
\v 6 Mubuuze mulabe. 
\q2 Omusajja alumwa okuzaala? 
\q1 Kale lwaki ndaba buli musajja ow’amaanyi 
\q2 ng’atadde emikono gye ku lubuto ng’omukazi alumwa okuzaala, 
\q2 buli muntu mu maaso yenna asiiwuuse ng’agenda okufa? 
\q1  
\v 7 Nga luliba lwa nnaku olunaku olwo! 
\q2 Tewali lulirufaanana. 
\q1 Kiriba kiseera kya kabi eri Yakobo, 
\q2 naye aliwona n’akiyitamu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 “ ‘Olulituuka ku lunaku olwo, 
\q2 ndimenya ekikoligo okuva mu nsingo zaabwe 
\q1 era ne mbasaleko amasamba, 
\q2 ab’amawanga nga tebakyaddayo kubafuula baddu,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye. 
\q1  
\v 9 Wabula, bajja kuweerezanga \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe 
\q2 ne Dawudi kabaka waabwe 
\q2 gwe ndibayimusiza. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 “ ‘Noolwekyo totya, ggwe Yakobo omuweereza wange, 
\q2 toggwaamu maanyi ggwe Isirayiri,’ 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 ‘Ddala ddala ndibalokola okubaggya mu kifo eky’ewala, 
\q2 nziggye ezzadde lyammwe okuva mu nsi ey’obuwaŋŋanguse. 
\q1 Yakobo aliddamu okuba n’emirembe n’obutebenkevu, 
\q2 era tewali n’omu alimutiisatiisa. 
\q1  
\v 11 Ndi wamu nammwe 
\q2 era ndibalokola, 
\q1 wadde nga ndizikiririza ddala amawanga gye mbagobedde, 
\q2 siribazikiririza ddala mmwe,’ 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 Ndibakangavvula n’obwenkanya, 
\q2 siribaleka nga temubonerezebbwa n’akatono. 
\p  
\v 12 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Ekiwundu kyo tekiwonyezeka, 
\q2 Ebisago byo si byakuwona. 
\q1  
\v 13 Tewali n’omu wa kukuwolereza, 
\q2 tewali ddagala lya kiwundu kyo, toowonyezebwe. 
\q1  
\v 14 Abakuyamba bonna bakwerabidde 
\q2 tebakufaako. 
\q1 Nkukubye ng’omulabe bwe yandikoze 
\q2 ne nkubonereza ng’owettima bwe yandikoze, 
\q1 kubanga omusango gw’ozzizza munene nnyo 
\q2 n’ebibi byo bingi ddala. 
\q1  
\v 15 Lwaki okaaba olw’ekiwundu kyo, 
\q2 obulumi bwo obutaliiko ddagala? 
\q1 Olw’okwonoona kwo okunene n’ebibi byo ebingi ennyo 
\q2 nkuleeseeko ebintu bino. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 16 “ ‘Naye bonna abakumira nabo baliriibwa, 
\q2 abalabe bo bonna baligenda mu buwaŋŋanguse. 
\q1 Abo abaakunyaga balinyagibwa, 
\q2 abo abaakwelula balyelulwa. 
\q1  
\v 17 Naye ndikuzzaawo owone, 
\q2 ndiwonya ebiwundu byo,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q1 ‘kubanga oyitibwa eyasuulibwa, 
\q2 Sayuuni atalina n’omu amufaako.’ 
\p  
\v 18 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Ndizzaawo eby’obugagga by’eweema za Yakobo 
\q2 era mbeere n’ekisa ku kifo kyammwe kye mwabeerangamu. 
\q1 Ekibuga kirizimbibwa awaali amatongo gaakyo, 
\q2 n’olubiri luzzibwe mu kifo kyalwo ekituufu. 
\q1  
\v 19 Mu bo mulivaamu ennyimba ez’okwebaza 
\q2 era n’eddoboozi ery’okujaguza, 
\q1 ndibaaza, era tebaliba batono, 
\q2 ndibawa ekitiibwa, tebalinyoomebwa. 
\q1  
\v 20 Abaana baabwe baliba nga bwe baali mu nnaku ez’edda, 
\q2 era n’ebitundu byabwe mwe baabeeranga bizimbibwe nga ndaba. 
\q2 Ndibonereza bonna ababanyigiriza. 
\q1  
\v 21 Omukulembeze waabwe aliba omu ku bo; 
\q2 omukulembeze waabwe aliyimuka okuva mu bo. 
\q1 Ndimuleeta wendi era musembeze kumpi nange, 
\q2 kubanga ani oyo alyewaayo 
\q2 okunyiikira okubeera okumpi nange?’ 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 22 ‘Noolwekyo munaabeeranga bantu bange, 
\q2 nange n’abeeranga Katonda wammwe.’ ” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Laba, omuyaga gwa \nd Mukama\nd* 
\q2 gulikuntira mu kiruyi, 
\q1 empewo ey’amaanyi 
\q2 eyeetooloolera ku mitwe gy’abakozi b’ebibi. 
\q1  
\v 24 Obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* obubuubuuka 
\q2 tebujja kukoma okutuusa ng’atuukirizza 
\q2 ekigendererwa ky’omutima gwe. 
\q1 Mu nnaku ezirijja, 
\q2 kino mulikitegeera. 
\c 31  
\p  
\v 1 “Mu kiseera ekijja, ndiba Katonda w’ebika byonna ebya Isirayiri, era balibeera bantu bange,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 2 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Abantu abawona ekitala 
\q2 baliraba ekisa mu ddungu. 
\q2 Ndijja n’empa Isirayiri ekiwummulo.” 
\p  
\v 3 \nd Mukama\nd* yatulabikira edda ng’agamba nti, 
\q1 “Nkwagadde n’okwagala okutaliggwaawo, 
\q2 kyenvudde nkusembeza gye ndi n’ekisa ekijjudde okwagala. 
\q1  
\v 4 Ndikuzimba nate, era olizimbibwa, 
\q2 ggwe Omuwala Isirayiri. 
\q1 Era oliddamu okuyonjebwa okwate ebitaasa byo 
\q2 ofulume ozine n’abo abasanyuka. 
\q1  
\v 5 Oliddamu okusimba emizabbibu ku lusozi Samaliya, 
\q2 abalimi baligisimba balye ebibala byakwo. 
\q1  
\v 6 Walibeerawo olunaku 
\q2 abakuumi lwe balikoowoola ku busozi bwa Efulayimu nti, 
\q1 ‘Mujje, tugende ku Sayuuni, 
\q2 eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe.’ ” 
\p  
\v 7 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Muyimbe n’essanyu olwa Yakobo 
\q2 Muleekaanire waggulu olw’ensi esinga zonna.” 
\q1 Ettendo lyammwe liwulikike, era mugambe nti, 
\q2 “Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, lokola abantu bo, 
\q2 abaasigalawo ku Isirayiri.” 
\q1  
\v 8 Laba, ndibakomyawo okuva mu nsi ey’obukiikakkono, 
\q2 ne mbakuŋŋaanya okuva ku nkomerero y’ensi. 
\q1 Mu bo mulibaamu abazibe b’amaaso, n’abalema, 
\q2 n’abakyala ab’embuto, n’abalumwa okuzaala, 
\q2 era abantu bangi balikomawo. 
\q1  
\v 9 Balikomawo nga bakaaba, 
\q2 balisaba nga mbakomyawo. 
\q1 Ndibakulembera ku mabbali g’emigga, 
\q2 mu kkubo eggolokofu mwe batalyesittalira 
\q1 kubanga nze Kitaawe wa Isirayiri, 
\q2 era Efulayimu ye mutabani wange omubereberye. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 “Muwulire ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* mmwe amawanga, 
\q2 mukyogere mu nsi ezeewala. 
\q1 ‘Oyo eyasaasaanya Isirayiri alibakuŋŋaanya 
\q2 era alirabirira ekisibo kye ng’omusumba w’endiga.’ 
\q1  
\v 11 Kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* aligula Yakobo 
\q2 era abanunule okuva mu mukono gw’oyo abasinga amaanyi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Balijja baleekaana olw’essanyu ku nsozi za Sayuuni; 
\q2 balisanyukira okugabula kwa \nd Mukama\nd*: 
\q1 emmere ey’empeke, ne wayini omusu, n’omuzigo, 
\q2 n’abaana b’endiga era n’ebisibo. 
\q1 Balibeera ng’ennimiro efukiririddwa obulungi, 
\q2 era tebalyongera kulaba nnaku. 
\q1  
\v 13 Abawala balizina beesiime, 
\q2 n’abavubuka, n’abakadde. 
\q1 Okukaaba kwabwe ndikufuula essanyu; 
\q2 ndibawa emirembe n’essanyu okusinga ennaku. 
\q1  
\v 14 Ndikkusa bakabona ebintu ebingi, 
\q2 n’abantu bange mbajjuze ebintu,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 15 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Eddoboozi liwulirwa mu Laama, 
\q2 nga likungubaga n’okukaaba okungi. 
\q1 Laakeeri akaabira abaana be 
\q2 era agaanye okusirisibwa, 
\q2 kubanga abaana be baweddewo.” 
\p  
\v 16 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Ziyiza eddoboozi lyo lireme okuwulikika ng’okaaba 
\q2 n’amaaso go galeme okujja amaziga, 
\q1 kubanga omulimu gwo gulisasulibwa,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q2 Balikomawo okuva mu nsi y’omulabe. 
\q1  
\v 17 Waliwo essuubi, 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q2 Abaana bo baliddayo mu nsi yaabwe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 “Ddala mpulidde Efulayimu ng’akungubaga nti, 
\q2 ‘Wankangavvula ng’ennyana endalu 
\q2 era kaakano nkangavvuddwa. 
\q1 Nziza, n’akomawo gy’oli 
\q2 kubanga ggwe \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wange. 
\q1  
\v 19 Nga mmaze okubula, 
\q2 neenenya, 
\q1 nga nzizeemu amagezi agategeera 
\q2 ne neekuba mu kifuba. 
\q1 Nakwatibwa ensonyi era ne nswala, 
\q2 kubanga naliko ekivume ky’obuvubuka bwange.’ 
\q1  
\v 20 Efulayimu si mwana wange omwagalwa, 
\q2 omwana gwe nsanyukira? 
\q1 Wadde nga ntera okumunenya 
\q2 naye nkyamujjukira. 
\q1 Noolwekyo omutima gwange gumuyaayaanira; 
\q2 nnina ekisa kingi gy’ali,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 “Muteeke ebipande ku nguudo; 
\q2 muteekeeko ebipande. 
\q1 Mwetegereze ekkubo eddene, 
\q2 ekkubo mwe muyita. 
\q1 Komawo ggwe Omuwala Isirayiri, 
\q2 komawo mu bibuga byo. 
\q1  
\v 22 Olituusa ddi okudda eno n’eri, 
\q2 ggwe omuwala atali mwesigwa? 
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* alikola ekintu ekiggya ku nsi, 
\q2 omukazi aliwa omusajja obukuumi.” 
\p  
\v 23 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, “Bwe ndibakomyawo okubaggya mu busibe, abantu b’omu nsi ye Yuda ne mu bibuga byamu bajja kuddamu okukozesa ebigambo bino nti, ‘\nd Mukama\nd* akuwe omukisa, ggwe ekifo ekitukuvu, ggwe olusozi olutukuvu.’  
\v 24 Abantu balibeera wamu mu Yuda ne mu bibuga byakyo byonna, abalimi n’abo abatambula n’amagana gaabwe.  
\v 25 Abalumwa ennyonta ndibanywesa, nzizeemu amaanyi abazirika.” 
\p  
\v 26 Awo we nazuukukira ne ntunulatunula. Otulo twange twali tunnyumidde. 
\p  
\v 27 “Ennaku zijja,” bwayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, “lwe ndisimba ennyumba ya Isirayiri ne nnyumba ya Yuda n’ezzadde ly’abantu n’ery’ensolo.  
\v 28 Nga bwe nabalabirira nga bakuulibwa era nga bayuzibwayuzibwa, nga babetentebwa, era nga bazikirizibwa ne beeleetako ekikangabwa, bwe ntyo bwe ndibalabirira nga bazimbibwa era nga basimbibwa,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 29 “Mu nnaku ezo abantu banaaba tebakyagamba nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Bakitaabwe balidde emizabbibu egikaawa\f + \fr 31:29 \ft emizabbibu gitera okuba nga giwoomerera noolwekyo tukisome nti giwoomerera\f*, 
\q2 n’amannyo g’abaana ne ganyenyeera.’ ” 
\m  
\v 30 Wabula buli muntu alifa olw’obutali butuukirivu bwe ye, buli muntu alya ezabbibu erinyenyeeza amannyo, amannyo ge galinyenyeera. 
\q1  
\v 31 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Ekiseera kijja, 
\q2 lwe ndikola endagaano empya 
\q1 n’ennyumba ya Isirayiri 
\q2 era n’ennyumba ya Yuda. 
\q1  
\v 32 Teribeera ng’endagaano eri 
\q2 gye nakola ne bajjajjaabwe 
\q1 bwe nabakwata ku mukono 
\q2 okubakulembera okubaggya mu nsi y’e Misiri, 
\q1 kubanga baamenya endagaano yange nabo 
\q2 wadde nga nze nnali nga omwami waabwe,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 33 “Eno y’endagaano gye nnaakola 
\q2 n’ennyumba ya Isirayiri mu kiseera ekyo,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 “Nditeeka amateeka gange mu birowoozo byabwe, 
\q2 ne ngawandiika ku mitima gyabwe. 
\q1 Ndibeera Katonda waabwe, 
\q2 nabo balibeera bantu bange. 
\q1  
\v 34 Omuntu taliddayo kuyigiriza muliraanwa we, 
\q2 oba omusajja muganda we ng’agamba nti, ‘Manya \nd Mukama\nd*,’ 
\q1 Kubanga bonna balimmanya, 
\q2 okuva ku asokerwako wansi okutuuka ku akomererayo waggulu,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 “Kubanga ndisonyiwa obutali butuukirivu bwabwe, 
\q2 n’ekibi kyabwe ne siddamu kukijjukira.” 
\p  
\v 35 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 Oyo ateekawo enjuba 
\q2 okwaka emisana, 
\q1 n’alagira omwezi n’emmunyeenye okwaka ekiro, asiikuula ennyanja 
\q2 amayengo gaayo ne gawuluguma; 
\q2 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye lye linnya lye. 
\q1  
\v 36 “Amateeka gano 
\q2 nga bwe gavudde mu maaso gange, 
\q1 n’ezzadde lya Isirayiri we linaakoma okubeera eggwanga 
\q2 olw’ebyo byonna bye bakoze,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\p  
\v 37 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, 
\q1 “Okuggyako ng’eggulu lisobola okupimibwa 
\q2 n’emisingi gy’ensi wansi okunoonyezebwa, 
\q1 olwo lw’endigoba ezzadde lya Isirayiri 
\q2 olw’ebyo bye bakoze,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 38 “Ennaku zijja,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, “ekibuga lwe kinaazimbibwa okuva ku Munaala gwe Kananeri okutuuka ku Mulyango gw’oku Nsonda.  
\v 39 Omuguwa ogupima gujja kupima okuva eyo okutuuka ku lusozi lw’e Galebu n’oluvannyuma gupime okuva eyo okutuuka e Gowa.  
\v 40 Ekiwonvu kyonna emirambo n’evvu gye bisuuliddwa, era n’ennimiro zonna okutuuka ku kagga Kidulooni ku bukiikakkono n’okutuuka ku nsonda eyitibwa Omulyango gw’Embalaasi, kinaaba kitukuvu eri Katonda. Ekibuga tekigenda kuddayo kusimbulwa wadde okusaanyizibwawo.” 
\c 32  
\s1 Yeremiya Agula Ennimiro 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ekyajjira Yeremiya mu mwaka ogw’ekkumi ogw’obufuzi bwa Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda, ogwali omwaka ogw’ekkumi n’omunaana ogw’obufuzi bwa Nebukadduneeza.  
\v 2 Amaggye ga kabaka w’e Babulooni gaali gazingizza Yerusaalemi, era ne Yeremiya nnabbi baali bamusibidde mu luggya lw’omukuumi mu lubiri lwa kabaka wa Yuda. 
\p  
\v 3 Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda yali amusibidde eyo ng’agamba nti, “Lwaki otegeeza obunnabbi mu ngeri eyo? Ogamba nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. Nnaatera okuwaayo ekibuga kino eri kabaka w’e Babulooni, era agenda kukiwamba.  
\v 4 Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda tajja kuwona mikono gy’Abakaludaaya naye ddala wa kuweebwayo eri kabaka w’e Babulooni era ajja kwogera naye, balabagane amaaso n’amaaso.  
\v 5 Alitwala Zeddekiya mu Babulooni, gy’alisigala okutuusa lwe ndimujjira. Bwe munaalwanyisa Abakaludaaya, temujja kuwangula,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\p  
\v 6 Yeremiya n’agamba nti, “Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kyanzijira:  
\v 7 Laba Kanameri mutabani wa Sallumu kojjaawo agenda kujja gy’oli akugambe nti, ‘Gula ennimiro yange eri mu Anasosi kubanga ng’owooluganda asinga okuba okumpi guba mukisa gwo era buvunaanyizibwa bwo okugigula.’  
\p  
\v 8 “Awo nga \nd Mukama\nd* bwe yali agambye, omwana wa kojja wange Kanameri yajja mu luggya lw’omukuumi gye nnali n’aŋŋamba nti, ‘Gula ennimiro yange eri mu Anasosi mu kitundu kya Benyamini, kubanga okirinako obuyinza n’obuvunaanyizibwa okukinunulayo n’okyefunira, kyegulire.’ 
\p “Olwo ne mmanya nti kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 9 Ne ndyoka ngula ennimiro ey’e Anasosi ku Kanameri omwana wa kojjange, ne mubalira ensimbi, ebitundu kkumi na musanvu ebya ffeeza.  
\v 10 Ne nteeka omukono ku kiwandiiko ky’endagaano okugulirwa ettaka ne nkissaako n’akabonero, ne nfuna abajulirwa, ne mpima ffeeza ku minzaani.  
\v 11 Ne ntwala ekiwandiiko ekimpa obwannannyini ekirimu enkola era n’ebisuubirwa okugobererwa, era ne kkopi ey’olwatu.  
\v 12 Ne mpa Baluki mutabani wa Neriya mutabani wa Maseya ekiwandiiko ky’obwannannyini, Kanameri omwana wa kojjange nga waali n’abajulirwa nga weebali abaateeka emikono ku kiwandiiko eky’obwannannyini n’Abayudaaya bonna abaali batudde mu luggya lw’omukuumi. 
\p  
\v 13 “Ne nkuutirira Baluki mu maaso gaabwe nti,  
\v 14 ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Twala ebiwandiiko bino byombi, ekisibeko envumbo n’ekitali kisibeko obiteeke mu nsumbi ey’ebbumba bisobole okulwawo ebbanga gwanvu.  
\v 15 Kubanga bw’atyo bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Ennyumba, n’ebibanja n’ennimiro ez’emizabbibu biriddamu okugulibwa mu nsi eno.’  
\p  
\v 16 “Nga mmaze okuwaayo ekiwandiiko kino eri Baluki mutabani wa Neriya, nasaba \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\pm  
\v 17 “Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, ggwe wakola eggulu n’ensi n’amaanyi go amangi ennyo, n’omukono gwo ogugoloddwa. Tewali kintu na kimu kikulema.  
\v 18 Olaga okwagala kwo eri enkumi n’enkumi ate oleeta ekibonerezo ky’ebibi bya bakitaabwe ku baana baabwe. Ayi Katonda ow’ekitalo era ow’amaanyi, ayitibwa \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye,  
\v 19 ebigendererwa byo nga binene era n’ebikolwa byo nga bikulu. Amaaso go gatunuulidde amakubo gonna ag’abantu, osasula buli muntu ng’enneeyisa ye bweri era ng’ebikolwa bye bwe biri.  
\v 20 Wakola obubonero n’ebikolwa ebyamagero mu Misiri era weeyongedde okubikola leero, wonna mu Isirayiri ne mu bantu bonna era erinnya lyo lyeyongedde okwatiikirira.  
\v 21 Waggya abantu bo Isirayiri mu Misiri n’obubonero n’eby’amagero, n’omukono gwo ogw’amaanyi gwe wagolola n’entiisa ey’amaanyi.  
\v 22 Wabawa ensi eno gye wali olayidde okuwa bajjajjaabwe, ensi ekulukuta amata n’omubisi gw’enjuki.  
\v 23 Baagituukamu ne bagitwala, naye tebaakugondera wadde okugoberera amateeka go, byonna bye wabalagira tebaliiko wadde na kimu kye baakola. Kyewava obaleetako akabi kano konna. 
\pm  
\v 24 “Laba entuumo z’omulabe z’atuumye okuzinda ekibuga okukiwamba n’ekitala, n’enjala ne kawumpuli, ekibuga kigenda kuweebwayo eri Abakaludaaya abakirumba. Ekyo kye wagamba kituukiridde nga kaakano bw’olaba.  
\v 25 Era wadde ng’ekibuga kigenda kuweebwayo eri Abakaludaaya, ggwe Ayi \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda oŋŋambye nti, ‘Toola ffeeza weegulire ennimiro era wabeerewo n’abajulirwa.’ ” 
\p  
\v 26 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 27 “Nze \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda w’abantu bonna. Eriyo ekinnema?  
\v 28 Noolwekyo, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Nnaatera okuwaayo ekibuga kino eri Abakaludaaya ne Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni, abanaakiwamba.  
\v 29 Abakaludaaya abanaalumba ekibuga kino bajja kukikumako omuliro, bakyokye kiggye, n’amayumba gonna abantu mwe bankwasiza obusungu nga bootereza Baali obubaane waggulu ku mayumba era n’okuwaayo ebiweebwayo eby’okunywa eri bakatonda abalala.’  
\p  
\v 30 “Abantu ba Isirayiri ne Yuda bye bakoze bibi byereere mu maaso gange okuva mu buvubuka bwabwe; era ddala abantu ba Isirayiri tebalina kirala kye bakoze wabula okunnyiiza n’ebyo emikono gyabwe gye gikoze, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 31 Okuva ku lunaku lwe kyazimbibwa ne leero, ekibuga kino kindeetedde obusungu bungi n’ekiruyi, noolwekyo nteekwa okukiggya mu maaso gange.  
\v 32 Abantu ba Isirayiri ne Yuda bannyiizizza olw’ebibi byonna bye bakoze, bo ne bakabaka baabwe n’abakungu baabwe, ne bakabona baabwe ne bannabbi, abasajja ba Yuda n’abantu ba Yerusaalemi.  
\v 33 Banvaako ne bankuba amabega mu kifo ky’okuntunuulira; wadde nga nabayigiriza ne nkiddiŋŋana emirundi mingi naye tebaawuliriza wadde okufaayo eri okukangavvulwa.  
\v 34 Baateekawo ebifaananyi bya bakatonda baabwe abakole n’emikono, eby’omuzizo mu nnyumba eyitibwa Erinnya lyange ne bagyonoona.  
\v 35 Baazimba ebifo ebigulumivu ebya Baali mu kiwonvu kya mutabani wa Kinomu, basaddaake batabani baabwe ne bawala baabwe mu muliro eri Moleki, newaakubadde nga sibalagiranga, wadde okukirowooza mu magezi gange, nti balikola ekintu ekibi ennyo bwe kityo kiviireko Yuda okwonoona. 
\p  
\v 36 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Ekibuga kino okyogerako nti, Kijja kuweebwayo eri kabaka w’e Babulooni lwa kitala, n’enjala, ne kawumpuli.’  
\v 37 Naye laba, ndibakuŋŋaanya mu mawanga gye mbagobedde n’obusungu bwange n’ekiruyi eky’amaanyi; ndibakomyawo mu kifo kino, mubeere n’emirembe.  
\v 38 Era balibeera bantu bange, nange mbeere Katonda waabwe.  
\v 39 Ndibawa omutima gumu n’ekkubo limu, bantyenga emirembe gyonna, olw’obulungi bwabwe, n’obulungi bw’abaana abaliddawo.  
\v 40 Ndikola nabo endagaano eteriggwaawo: siribaleka era sirirekeraawo kubakolera birungi, era ndibassaamu omwoyo oguntya, baleme kuddayo kunvaako.  
\v 41 Ndisanyuka olw’okubakolera ebirungi era awatali kubuusabuusa ndibasimba mu nsi eno n’omutima gwange gwonna n’emmeeme yange yonna. 
\p  
\v 42 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Nga bwe naleeta akabi kano konna ku bantu bano, era nze ndibawa okukulaakulana kwonna kwe mbasuubizza.  
\v 43 Era nate ennimiro zirigulwa mu ggwanga lino lye mugamba nti, ‘Lifuuse matongo agatagambika, omutali bantu wadde ensolo kubanga kiweereddwayo eri Abakaludaaya.’  
\v 44 Ennimiro zirigulibwa ffeeza, era n’ebiwandiiko eby’obwannannyini biteekebweko omukono, bisabikibwe era bifune n’ababijulira mu Benyamini, ne mu byalo ebyetoolodde Yerusaalemi, ne mu bibuga bya Yuda ne mu bibuga ebyetoolodde Yerusaalemi, ne mu byalo bya Yuda ne mu bibuga eby’omu nsi ey’ensozi, ne mu bibuga eby’omu nsenyi ne mu bibuga eby’omu bukiikaddyo, kubanga ndikomyawo okukulaakulana kwabwe, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\c 33  
\s1 Ebisuubizo by’Okuddawo 
\p  
\v 1 Yeremiya bwe yali ng’akyali mu kkomera mu luggya lw’omukuumi, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kimujjira omulundi ogwokubiri nti,  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, oyo eyakola ensi, \nd Mukama\nd* eyagikola era n’agiteekawo, \nd Mukama\nd* lye linnya lye:  
\v 3 ‘Mumpite n’abayitaba ne mbalaga ebikulu ebitanoonyezeka bye mutamanyi.’  
\v 4 Kubanga bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri ku mayumba agali mu kibuga kino era ne ku mbiri z’obwakabaka bwa Yuda ebyamenyebwamenyebwa okukozesebwa ng’entuumo eziziyiza obulumbaganyi n’ekitala  
\v 5 mu lutalo n’Abakaludaaya. ‘Birijjula emirambo gy’abasajja be nditta olw’obusungu bwange n’ekiruyi. Ndikweka amaaso gange okuva ku kibuga kino olw’obutali butuukirivu bwabwe bwonna. 
\p  
\v 6 “ ‘Naye ndikiwa obulamu n’okuwonyezebwa; ndiwonya abantu bange, mbaleetere okweyagalira mu mirembe emigazi era eminywevu.  
\v 7 Ndikomyawo Yuda ne Isirayiri okubaggya mu buwambe era mbazimbe nga bwe baasooka okubeera.  
\v 8 Ndibalongoosa okubaggyako ebibi byonna bye bannyonoona era mbasonyiwe n’ekibi eky’okunjeemera.  
\v 9 Olwo ekibuga kino kirindetera okwongera okumanyika, n’essanyu, n’ettendo era n’ekitiibwa eri amawanga gonna ku nsi agaliwulira ebintu byonna ebirungi bye mbakolera; era balyewuunya bakankane olw’okukulaakulana n’emirembe gye nkiwa.’ 
\p  
\v 10 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Mwogera ku kifo kino nti, “Matongo agaalekebwa awo, omutali bantu wadde ensolo.” Ate nga mu bibuga bya Yuda n’enguudo za Yerusaalemi ezalekebwawo omutali bantu wadde ensolo, muliddamu okuwulirwa nate  
\v 11 amaloboozi ag’essanyu n’okujaguza, n’amaloboozi g’omugole ne bba, n’amaloboozi gaabo abaleeta ekiweebwayo eky’okwebaza eri ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*, nga bagamba nti, 
\q1 “ ‘ “Mumwebaze \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, 
\q2 kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* mulungi; 
\q2 okwagala kwe kubeerera emirembe gyonna.” 
\m Kubanga ndizzaawo omukisa gw’eggwanga lino nga bwe gwali mu kusooka,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\p  
\v 12 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, ‘Mu kifo kino ekirekeddwa awo omutali bantu wadde ensolo, mu bibuga byakyo byonna nate muliddamu amalundiro ag’abasumba mwe banaawummulizanga ebisibo byabwe.  
\v 13 Mu bibuga eby’ensi ey’obusozi, eby’eri wansi w’ensozi ez’omu bugwanjuba era ne Negebu, mu kitundu kya Benyamini, mu byalo ebyetoolodde Yerusaalemi n’ebibuga ebyetoolodde Yuda mwonna ebisibo biriddamu okuyita wansi w’omukono gw’oyo abibala,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\p  
\v 14 “ ‘Ennaku zijja,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘lwe ndituukiriza ekisuubizo eky’ekisa kye nakolera ennyumba ya Isirayiri n’ennyumba ya Yuda. 
\q1  
\v 15 “ ‘Mu nnaku ezo era mu kiseera ekyo 
\q2 ndireeta Ettabi ettukuvu mu lunyiriri lwa Dawudi 
\q2 era alikola eby’amazima era ebituufu mu nsi. 
\q1  
\v 16 Mu nnaku ezo Yuda alirokolebwa 
\q2 ne Yerusaalemi alibeera mirembe. 
\q1 Lino lye linnya ly’aliyitibwa nti, 
\q2 \nd Mukama\nd* Obutuukirivu bwaffe.’ ” 
\m  
\v 17 Kubanga bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, “Dawudi talirema kubeera na muntu kutuula ku ntebe ey’obwakabaka bw’ennyumba ya Isirayiri,  
\v 18 wadde bakabona, n’Abaleevi, okulemwa okubeera n’omusajja ow’okuyimirira mu maaso gange ebbanga lyonna okuwaayo ssaddaaka ezokebwa, okwokya ekiweebwayo eky’empeke era n’okuwaayo ssaddaaka.” 
\p  
\v 19 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* kyajjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 20 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Bw’oba osobola okumenya endagaano yange n’emisana era n’endagaano yange n’ekiro, ne kiba nti emisana n’ekiro tebijja mu biseera byabyo ebyateekebwawo,  
\v 21 olwo endagaano yange ne Dawudi omuddu wange, n’endagaano yange n’Abaleevi, ne bakabona, n’abaweereza bange eyinza okumenyebwa, Dawudi aleme kuddayo kuba na muntu wa mu nju ye okufuga ku ntebe ye ey’obwakabaka.  
\v 22 Ndifuula ab’enju ya Dawudi omuddu wange n’Abaleevi abaweereza mu maaso gange okwala ng’emmunyeenye ez’oku ggulu ezitabalika era abatabalika ng’omusenyu gw’okulubalama lw’ennyanja ogutapimika.’ ” 
\p  
\v 23 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 24 Tonategeera nti abantu bano bagamba nti, “\nd Mukama\nd* agaanye obwakabaka obubiri bwe yalonda? Kale banyooma abantu bange era tebakyababala ng’eggwanga.  
\v 25 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Bwe mba nga sassaawo ndagaano yange n’emisana n’ekiro n’amateeka ag’enkalakkalira ag’eggulu n’ensi,  
\v 26 olwo nzija kwegaana ezzadde lya Yakobo ne Dawudi omuddu wange era sirironda n’omu ku batabani be okufuga ezzadde lya Ibulayimu, ne Isaaka ne Yakobo. Kubanga ndizzaawo nate emikisa gyabwe, era ne mbakwatirwa ekisa.’ ” 
\c 34  
\s1 Okulabula Zeddekiya 
\p  
\v 1 Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni n’amaggye ge gonna, n’abantu bonna ab’ensi ze yali afuga bwe baali balwanyisa Yerusaalemi n’ebibuga ebikyetoolodde, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nga kigamba nti,  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Genda eri Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda omugambe nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera nti, Nnaatera okuwaayo ekibuga kino eri kabaka w’e Babulooni, era agenda kukyokya.  
\v 3 Tolisumattuka mukono gwe era oliwambibwa otwalibwe gy’ali. Oliraba kabaka w’e Babulooni n’amaaso go, olyogera naye nga mutunuuliraganye, era olitwalibwa e Babulooni. 
\p  
\v 4 “ ‘Wabula wulira ekisuubizo kya \nd Mukama\nd*, ggwe Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda. Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ku bikukwatako nti, Tolifa kitala;  
\v 5 olifa mu mirembe. Ng’abantu bwe bakuma ebyoto mu nnyimbe za bakitaawo, bakabaka abasooka, bwe batyo bwe balikuwa ekitiibwa nga bakujjukira nga bakukungubagira nga bagamba nti, “Woowe mukama waffe!” Nze kennyini mpa ekisuubizo kino, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.’ ” 
\p  
\v 6 Awo Yeremiya nnabbi bino byonna n’abibuulira Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda, mu Yerusaalemi,  
\v 7 nga amaggye ga kabaka w’e Babulooni bwe galwanyisa Yerusaalemi n’ebibuga ebirala ebya Yuda, Lakisi ne Azeka, ebyali bikyanywereddewo. Bino bye bibuga byokka ebyaliko eminaala egyali gisigadde mu Yuda. 
\s1 Eddembe ly’Abaddu 
\p  
\v 8 Kino kye kigambo ekyajjira Yeremiya okuva eri \nd Mukama\nd* nga kabaka Zeddekiya amaze okukola endagaano n’abantu bonna mu Yerusaalemi okulangirira nti abaddu baweereddwa eddembe.  
\v 9 Buli muntu yenna yali ateekwa okuta omuddu we Omwebbulaniya, abasajja n’abakazi; nga tewali n’omu alina kukuumira Muyudaaya munne mu busibe.  
\v 10 Abakungu bonna n’abantu abaayingira mu ndagaano eno bakkiriziganya nti baali bakusumulula abaddu baabwe abasajja n’abakazi baleme kubakuumira mu buddu nate. Era ne babasumulula.  
\v 11 Naye oluvannyuma ne bakyuka ne bazzaayo abaddu be baali bawadde eddembe. 
\p  
\v 12 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 13 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Nakola endagaano ne bajjajjammwe bwe nabaggya mu nsi y’e Misiri, mu nsi ey’obuddu. Nagamba nti,  
\v 14 ‘Buli mwaka ogw’omusanvu buli omu ku mmwe ateekwa okuta Mwebbulaniya munne eyeetunda gy’ali. Bwakuweererezanga emyaka omukaaga, oteekwa okumuta agende.’ Naye bakitammwe tebampuliriza wadde okunfaako.  
\v 15 Emabegako mmwe mwennyini mwenenya ne mukola ekisaanidde mu maaso gange. Buli omu ku mmwe yalangirira eddembe eri abantu b’ensi ye, era ne mukola n’endagaano mu nnyumba yange eyitibwa Erinnya lyange.  
\v 16 Naye kaakano mwekyusizza ne mwonoona erinnya lyange; buli omu ku mmwe yeddiza abaddu abasajja n’abakazi be mwali mutadde bagende gye baali beeyagalidde. Mubawalirizza babeere abaddu bammwe nate. 
\p  
\v 17 “Noolwekyo, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Temuŋŋondedde; temutadde bantu ba nsi yammwe. Kale kaakano nangirira ‘eddembe’ gye muli, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘eddembe’, okuttibwa n’ekitala, ne kawumpuli n’enjala. Ndibafuula ekyenyinyalwa eri obwakabaka bwonna obw’oku nsi.  
\v 18 Abasajja abamenye endagaano yange ne batatuukiriza bweyamo buli mu ndagaano gye baakola mu maaso gange, nzija kubakolako ng’ennyana gye basalamu ebitundu ebibiri ne bayita wakati w’ebitundu byayo.  
\v 19 Abakulembeze b’omu Yuda ne Yerusaalemi, n’abakungu b’embuga ya kabaka, ne bakabona n’abantu bonna ab’omu nsi abaatambulira wakati w’ebitundu by’ennyana,  
\v 20 ndibawaayo eri abalabe baabwe abanoonya obulamu bwabwe. Emirambo gyabwe gya kufuuka mmere eri ebinyonyi eby’omu bbanga era n’eri ensolo ez’omu nsiko. 
\p  
\v 21 “Ndiwaayo Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda n’abakungu be bonna eri abalabe baabwe ababanoonya okubatta, n’eri eggye lya kabaka w’e Babulooni, eribadde lizzeeyo emabega.  
\v 22 Ŋŋenda kuwa ekiragiro, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, era ndibakomyawo mu kibuga kino. Balikirwanyisa bakitwale, bakyokye. Era ndizikiriza ebibuga bya Yuda waleme kubaawo abibeeramu.” 
\c 35  
\s1 Abalekabu 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ekyajjira Yeremiya mu bufuzi bwa Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda, mutabani wa Yosiya nga kigamba nti,  
\v 2 “Genda eri ekika eky’Abalekabu obayite bajje mu kimu ku bisenge mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* obawe envinnyo banywe.” 
\p  
\v 3 Awo ne ntwala Yaazaniya mutabani wa Yeremiya, mutabani wa Kabazziniya ne baganda be ne batabani be bonna, ekika kyonna eky’Abalekabu.  
\v 4 Ne mbayingiza mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*, mu kisenge kya batabani ba Kanani mutabani wa Igudaliya omusajja wa Katonda. Kyali kiriraanye ekisenge kya bakungu, ekyali waggulu w’ekisenge kya Maaseya mutabani wa Sallumu omukuumi w’oluggi.  
\v 5 Ne nteeka ebibya ebijjudde envinnyo n’ebikopo ebimu mu maaso g’abasajja ab’ennyumba y’Abalekabu ne mbagamba nti, “Munywe ku nvinnyo.” 
\p  
\v 6 Naye ne baddamu nti, “Tetujja kunywa nvinnyo kubanga jjajjaffe Yonadabu mutabani wa Lekabu yatulagira nti, ‘Tewabanga n’omu ku mmwe wadde abaana bammwe anywanga envinnyo.  
\v 7 Era temuzimbanga ennyumba, wadde okusiganga ensigo wadde okusimba emizabbibu; temubanga na bintu bino byonna, naye mubeeranga mu weema zokka. Olwo munaawangaliranga mu nsi gye munaaberangamu.’  
\v 8 Twagondera ekiragiro kya jjajjaffe Yonadabu mutabani wa Lekabu kye yatulagira. Ffe wadde bakazi baffe wadde batabani baffe wadde bawala baffe tetunywangako ku nvinnyo,  
\v 9 oba okuzimba ennyumba okusulamu oba okuba n’ennimiro ez’emizabbibu, oba ebibanja oba ebirime.  
\v 10 Tusula mu weema era tugondedde bulambalamba byonna jjajjaffe Yonadabu bye yatulagira.  
\v 11 Naye Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni bwe yazinda ensi eno ne tugamba nti, ‘Tugende e Yerusaalemi tuwone eggye ery’Abakaludaaya n’ery’Abasuuli,’ kyetuvudde tubeera mu Yerusaalemi.” 
\p  
\v 12 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 13 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Genda ogambe abantu ba Yuda n’ab’omu Yerusaalemi nti, ‘Temuyinza kubaako kye muyiga, ne mugondera ebigambo byange?  
\v 14 Yonadabu mutabani wa Lekabu yalagira batabani be obutanywa nvinnyo n’ekiragiro kino kyakumibwa. Okutuusa ne leero tebanywa nvinnyo, kubanga baagondera etteeka lya jjajjaabwe. Naye njogedde nammwe emirundi mingi, naye temuŋŋondedde.  
\v 15 Emirundi mingi, natuma abaddu bange bonna bannabbi gye muli. Babagamba nti, “Buli omu ku mmwe ateekwa okuva mu makubo ge amabi akyuse ebikolwa bye, muleme kugoberera bakatonda balala okubaweereza, mulyoke mubeere mu nsi gye nabawa ne bajjajjammwe.” Naye temwanfaako wadde okumpuliriza.  
\v 16 Ab’enda ya Yonadabu mutabani wa Lekabu baakuuma ekiragiro jjajjaabwe kye yabalagira, naye abantu bano tebaŋŋondedde.’ 
\p  
\v 17 “Noolwekyo, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Muwulirize, ŋŋenda kuleeta ku Yuda ne ku buli muntu yenna atuula mu Yerusaalemi buli kibonoobono kye naboogerako. Nayogera nabo, naye tebampuliriza; nabayita, naye tebanziramu.’ ” 
\p  
\v 18 Awo Yeremiya n’agamba ennyumba y’Abalekabu nti, “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Mugondedde ekiragiro kya jjajjaammwe Yonadabu ne mukwata byonna bye yabalagira ne mutuukiriza byonna bye yabagamba.’  
\v 19 Noolwekyo, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Yonadabu mutabani wa Lekabu talirema kuba na mwana we alimpeereza.’ ” 
\c 36  
\s1 Yekoyakimu Ayokya Ekiwandiiko kya Yeremiya 
\p  
\v 1 Mu mwaka ogwokuna ogw’obufuzi bwa Yekoyakimu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nga kigamba nti,  
\v 2 “Twala omuzingo gw’empapula oguwandiikeko ebigambo byonna bye njogedde naawe ebikwata ku Isirayiri, ne Yuda n’amawanga gonna okuva mu biseera bye natandika okwogera naawe okuva mu bufuzi bwa Yosiya okutuusa kaakano.  
\v 3 Oboolyawo abantu ba Yuda bwe banaawulira ku bikangabwa bye ntegeka okubateekako, buli omu ku bo anaakyuka okuleka amakubo ge amabi, ndyoke mbasonyiwe ebibi byabwe n’obutali butuukirivu bwabwe.” 
\p  
\v 4 Awo Yeremiya n’ayita Baluki mutabani wa Neriya, era nga Yeremiya ayogera ebigambo byonna \nd Mukama\nd* bye yali ayogedde naye, Baluki n’abiwandiika ku muzingo.  
\v 5 Awo Yeremiya n’agamba Baluki nti, “Nagaanibwa okugenda mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 6 Kale laga mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ku lunaku olw’okusiiba osomere abantu ebigambo bya \nd Mukama\nd* ebiri ku muzingo by’owandiise nga njogera. Bisomere abantu ba Yuda bonna abava mu bibuga byabwe.  
\v 7 Oboolyawo banaaleeta okwegayirira kwabwe eri \nd Mukama\nd*, era buli omu anaava mu makubo ge amabi, kubanga obusungu n’ekiruyi \nd Mukama\nd* by’agambye okutuusa ku bantu bano binene nnyo.” 
\p  
\v 8 Baluki mutabani wa Neriya n’akola byonna nnabbi Yeremiya bye yamugamba okukola; n’asomera, ebigambo bya \nd Mukama\nd* okuva mu muzingo, mu yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 9 Mu mwezi ogwomwenda ogw’omwaka ogwokutaano ogw’obufuzi bwa Yekoyakimu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda, ekiseera eky’okusiibira mu maaso ga \nd Mukama\nd* kyalangirirwa eri abantu bonna mu Yerusaalemi era n’abo abaali bavudde mu bibuga bya Yuda.  
\v 10 Awo ng’abantu bonna bawulira, Baluki n’asoma ebigambo bya Yeremiya okuva mu muzingo, mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ng’ali mu kisenge kya Gemaliya mutabani wa Safani omuwandiisi, ekyali mu luggya olw’ekyengulu, mu mulyango omuggya ogw’ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ng’abantu bonna bawulira. 
\p  
\v 11 Mikaaya mutabani wa Gemaliya mutabani wa Safani bwe yawulira ebigambo bya \nd Mukama\nd* byonna ebyali mu muzingo,  
\v 12 n’agenda eri ennyumba y’omuwandiisi mu lubiri lwa kabaka, abakungu bonna gye baali batudde: Erisaama omuwandiisi, ne Deraya mutabani wa Semaaya, ne Erunasani mutabani wa Akubooli, ne Gemaliya mutabani wa Safani, ne Zeddekiya mutabani wa Kananiya, n’abakungu bonna abalala.  
\v 13 Mikaaya ng’ababuulidde byonna bye yali awulidde Baluki asomera abantu okuva ku muzingo,  
\v 14 abakungu bonna ne batuma Yekudi mutabani wa Nesaniya, mutabani wa Seremiya mutabani wa Kuusi eri Baluki amugambe nti, “Leeta omuzingo gw’osomedde abantu, naawe ojje.” Awo Baluki mutabani wa Neriya n’atwalira omuzingo mu mikono gye n’agubaleetera.  
\v 15 Ne bamugamba nti, “Tuula wansi, ogutusomere.” Awo Baluki n’agubasomera. 
\p  
\v 16 Bwe baawulira ebigambo ebyo byonna, buli omu n’atunula ku munne ng’atidde ne bagamba Baluki nti, “Tuteekwa okubuulira kabaka ebigambo bino byonna.”  
\v 17 Awo ne babuuza Baluki nti, “Tubuulire, wazze otya okuwandiika bino byonna? Yeremiya ye yabikugambye?” 
\p  
\v 18 Baluki n’abaddamu nti, “Weewaawo ye yayogedde ebigambo bino byonna, nze ne mbiwandiika ne bwino ku muzingo.” 
\p  
\v 19 Awo abakungu bonna ne bagamba Baluki nti, “Ggwe ne Yeremiya mugende mwekweke. Temukkiriza muntu yenna kumanya gye muli.” 
\p  
\v 20 Bwe baamala okutereka omuzingo mu kisenge kya Erisaama omuwandiisi, ne bagenda eri kabaka mu luggya ne bamutegeeza byonna.  
\v 21 Kabaka n’atuma Yekudi okuleeta omuzingo, Yekudi n’aguleeta okuva mu kisenge kya Erisaama omuwandiisi agusomere kabaka n’abakungu bonna abaali bamuyimiridde ku lusegere.  
\v 22 Gwali mwezi gwa mwenda ne kabaka yali atudde mu nnyumba etuulwamu mu budde obw’obutiti, ng’omuliro gwakira mu kibya kyagwo mu maaso ge.  
\v 23 Buli Yekudi lwe yasomangako empapula ssatu oba nnya ez’omuzingo, kabaka ng’azisala n’akambe k’omuwandiisi n’azisuula mu muliro okutuusa omuzingo gwonna lwe gwajjiira mu muliro.  
\v 24 Kabaka n’abantu bonna abaawulira ebigambo bino tebaatya, wadde okuyuza engoye zaabwe.  
\v 25 Newaakubadde nga Erunasani, ne Deraaya ne Gemaliya beegayirira kabaka obutayokya muzingo, teyabawuliriza.  
\v 26 Naye kabaka yalagira Yerameeri mutabani wa kabaka ne Seraya mutabani wa Azulyeri ne Seremiya mutabani wa Abudeeri okukwata Baluki omuwandiisi ne nnabbi Yeremiya, wabula \nd Mukama\nd* ng’abakwese. 
\p  
\v 27 Kabaka ng’amaze okwokya omuzingo ogwalimu ebigambo Baluki bye yali awandiise nga Yeremiya abyogera, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 28 “Twala omuzingo omulala oguwandiikeko ebigambo byonna ebyali ku muzingo ogwasooka, Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda gwe yayokya.  
\v 29 Gamba ne Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Wayokya omuzingo ogwo n’ogamba nti, “Lwaki wakiwandiikamu nti kabaka w’e Babulooni alijja azikiririze ddala ensi eno agimalemu abantu n’ensolo?”  
\v 30 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* eri Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda nti, Tajja kubeera na muntu n’omu kutuula ku ntebe ya Dawudi, n’omulambo gwe gulisuulibwa ebweru gwanikibwe mu musana emisana ne mu butiti ekiro.  
\v 31 Ndimubonereza n’abaana be, ne bakalabaalaba be olw’okwonoona kwabwe. Ndimuleetako ne bonna ababeera mu Yerusaalemi ne bonna ababeera mu Yuda buli kibonoobono kye naboogerako, kubanga tebawulirizza.’ ” 
\p  
\v 32 Olwo Yeremiya n’atwala omuzingo omulala n’aguwa omuwandiisi Baluki mutabani wa Neriya; nga Yeremiya ayogera, Baluki yawandiikamu ebigambo byonna ebyali mu muzingo guli Yekoyakimu kabaka wa Yuda gwe yayokya mu muliro. N’ebigambo bingi ebifaanana bwe bityo byayongerwamu. 
\c 37  
\s1 Yeremiya Asibibwa mu Kkomera 
\p  
\v 1 Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni n’afuula Zeddekiya mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda okuba kabaka wa Yuda mu kifo kya Koniya mutabani wa Yekoyakimu.  
\v 2 Wabula ye wadde abakungu be wadde abantu ab’omu nsi tebaafaayo ku bigambo \nd Mukama\nd* bye yali ayogedde ng’ayita mu nnabbi Yeremiya. 
\p  
\v 3 Wabula kabaka Zeddekiya n’atuma Yekukaali mutabani wa Seremiya ne Zeffaniya mutabani wa Maaseya kabona eri nnabbi Yeremiya, bamutegeeze nti, “Tusabire eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe.” 
\p  
\v 4 Awo Yeremiya yali alina eddembe okujja nga bw’ayagala mu bantu, kubanga yali tannaba kuteekebwa mu kkomera.  
\v 5 Eggye lya Falaawo lyali livudde e Misiri era Abakaludaaya abaali balumbye Yerusaalemi bwe baakiwulira, ne bava e Yerusaalemi. 
\p  
\v 6 Awo ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira nnabbi Yeremiya nga kigamba nti,  
\v 7 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Mugambe kabaka wa Yuda eyabatumye okunnebuuzako nti, ‘Eggye lya Falaawo erizze okubayambako, lijja kuddayo mu nsi yaalyo e Misiri.  
\v 8 Abakaludaaya bakomewo balumbe ekibuga kino; bajja kukiwamba bakyokye.’ 
\p  
\v 9 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, Temwerimbarimba nga mulowooza nti, ‘Abakaludaaya ddala baakutuleka.’ Tebajja kubaleka.  
\v 10 Wadde nga mwandiwangudde, eggye lyonna erya Babulooni eribalumbye, abatuusiddwako ebisago bokka nga be basigadde mu weema zaabwe, bandivuddeyo ne bookya ekibuga kino.” 
\p  
\v 11 Awo eggye ly’Abakaludaaya nga livudde mu Yerusaalemi olw’eggye lya Falaawo,  
\v 12 Yeremiya n’ava mu kibuga agende mu bitundu bya Benyamini afune omugabo gwe ogw’ebintu mu bantu eyo.  
\v 13 Naye bwe yatuuka ku mulyango gwa Benyamini, Omukulu w’abaserikale eyali ayitibwa Iriya mutabani wa Seremiya mutabani wa Kananiya n’amukwata n’agamba nti, “Ogenda kwegatta ku Bakaludaaya!” 
\p  
\v 14 Yeremiya n’amuddamu nti, “Ompayiriza! Sigenda kusenga Bakaludaaya.” Naye Iriya n’atamuwuliriza; n’akwata Yeremiya n’amutwala eri abakungu.  
\v 15 Baanyiigira Yeremiya ne bamukuba ne bamusibira mu nnyumba ya Yonasaani omuwandiisi, gye baali bafudde ekkomera. 
\p  
\v 16 Yeremiya yateekebwa mu kasenge akaali mu kkomera mwe yamala ebbanga eddene.  
\v 17 Awo kabaka Zeddekiya n’amutumya n’amuleeta mu lubiri gye yamubuuliza mu kyama nti, “Olinayo ekigambo kyonna okuva eri \nd Mukama\nd*?” Yeremiya n’addamu nti, “Weewaawo, ojja kuweebwayo eri kabaka w’e Babulooni.” 
\p  
\v 18 Awo Yeremiya n’agamba Kabaka Zeddekiya nti, “Musango ki gwe nzizizza gy’oli oba eri abakungu bo oba abantu bano; mulyoke munteeke mu kkomera?  
\v 19 Bannabbi bo baluwa abakulagula nti, ‘Kabaka w’e Babulooni tajja kukulumba ggwe wadde ensi eno?  
\v 20 Naye kaakano mukama wange kabaka nsaba owulirize, nkwegayirira, tonzizaayo mu nnyumba ya Yonasaani omuwandiisi, kuba nandifiira eyo.’ ” 
\p  
\v 21 Kabaka Zeddekiya n’alyoka alagira Yeremiya okuteekebwa mu luggya lw’abakuumi n’aweebwanga omugaati buli lunaku okuva ew’omufumbi waagyo mu Yerusaalemi, okutuusa emigaati lwe gyaggwa mu kibuga. Awo Yeremiya n’asigala mu luggya lw’abaserikale abakuumi. 
\c 38  
\s1 Yeremiya Asuulibwa mu Kinnya 
\p  
\v 1 Awo Sefatiya mutabani wa Mattani ne Gedaliya mutabani wa Pasukuli ne Yukali mutabani wa Malukiya ne bawulira ebigambo Yeremiya bye yali agamba abantu bonna nti,  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Buli muntu anaasigala mu kibuga kino ajja kufa ekitala, enjala oba kawumpuli, naye buli afuluma n’agenda eri Abakaludaaya ajja kuba mulamu.’  
\v 3 Era bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Ekyamazima ekibuga kino kya kuweebwayo eri eggye lya kabaka w’e Babulooni; anaakiwamba.’ ” 
\p  
\v 4 Awo abakungu ne bagamba kabaka nti, “Omusajja ono asaana kuttibwa. Amalamu abaserikale abasigadde mu kibuga amaanyi, era n’abantu bonna, olw’ebintu by’abagamba. Omuntu ono tanoonya bulungi bw’abantu naye kuzikirizibwa kwabwe.” 
\p  
\v 5 Kabaka Zeddekiya n’addamu nti, “Ali mu mikono gyammwe, siyinza kubawakanya.” 
\p  
\v 6 Awo ne batwala Yeremiya ne bamuteeka mu kinnya kya Malukiya mutabani wa kabaka ekyali mu luggya lw’abakuumi. Yeremiya ne baamussaayo n’emiguwa mu kinnya. Tekyalimu mazzi wabula ebitosi, era omwo Yeremiya mwe yabbika. 
\p  
\v 7 Naye Ebedumeleki Omuwesiyopya omu ku balaawe b’omu lubiri lwa kabaka bwe yawulira nga batadde Yeremiya mu kinnya, nga ne kabaka atudde ku mulyango gwa Benyamini,  
\v 8 Ebedumeleki n’ava mu lubiri n’agenda eri kabaka n’amugamba nti,  
\v 9 “Mukama wange kabaka, abantu bano bakoze bubi mu byonna bye bakoze nnabbi Yeremiya okumusuula mu kinnya, gy’anafiira enjala nga tekyali mugaati gwonna mu kibuga.” 
\p  
\v 10 Awo kabaka n’alagira Ebedumeleki Omuwesiyopya nti, “Twala abasajja amakumi asatu okuva wano musitule nnabbi Yeremiya okuva mu kinnya nga tannafa.” 
\p  
\v 11 Awo Ebedumeleki n’atwala abasajja ne bagenda mu kisenge wansi w’etterekero ly’ensimbi mu lubiri. Nakwata ebigoye ebimu ebikadde n’engoye enziinaziina n’abissa awamu n’emiguwa eri Yeremiya mu kinnya.  
\v 12 Ebedumeleki Omuwesiyopya n’agamba Yeremiya nti, “Teeka ebigoye bino ebikadde wansi w’enkwawa zo okunyweza emiguwa wansi w’emikono gyo.” Yeremiya n’akola bw’atyo.  
\v 13 Ne bamusikayo n’emiguwa ne bamuggya mu kinnya. Yeremiya n’asigala mu luggya lw’abakuumi. 
\s1 Zeddekiya Addamu Okubuuza Yeremiya 
\p  
\v 14 Kabaka Zeddekiya n’atumya nnabbi Yeremiya bamuleete ku mulyango ogwokusatu ogwa yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*. Kabaka n’agamba Yeremiya nti, “Nnina kye ŋŋenda okukubuuza. Tobaako ky’onkweka.” 
\p  
\v 15 Yeremiya n’agamba Zeddekiya nti, “Bwe nnaakuddamu tonzite? Ne bwe nnaakuwa amagezi tojja kumpuliriza.” 
\p  
\v 16 Naye kabaka Zeddekiya n’alayira ekirayiro mu kyama eri Yeremiya nti, “Nga Katonda bw’ali omulamu, eyatuwa omukka gwe tussa, sijja kukutta wadde okukuwaayo eri abo abanoonya okukutta.” 
\p  
\v 17 Awo Yeremiya n’agamba Zeddekiya nti, “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Singa weewaayo eri abakungu ba kabaka w’e Babulooni, ojja kukuumibwa bulungi tootuukibweko kabi konna, n’ekibuga kino tekijja kwokebwa; ggwe n’ab’omu maka go munaabeera balamu.  
\v 18 Naye bw’oteweeyo eri abakungu ba kabaka w’e Babulooni, ekibuga kino kijja kuweebwayo eri Abakaludaaya bakyokye; nawe wennyini tojja kubawona.’ ” 
\p  
\v 19 Kabaka Zeddekiya n’agamba Yeremiya nti, “Ntya Abayudaaya abaddukidde mu Babulooni, kubanga Abakaludaaya bayinza okumpaayo gye bali ne bambonyaabonya.” 
\p  
\v 20 Yeremiya n’amuddamu nti, “Tebaakuweeyo. Ggwe gondera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ng’okola kye nkugamba. Olwo binaakugendera bulungi, nawe tojja kuttibwa.  
\v 21 Naye bwonoogaana okwewaayo, kino \nd Mukama\nd* kyandaze:  
\v 22 Abakazi bonna abasigadde mu lubiri lwa kabaka wa Yuda bajja kuleetebwa eri abakungu ba kabaka w’e Babulooni, bakugambe nti, 
\q1 “ ‘Mikwano gyo gye weesiga 
\q2 baakubuzaabuza ne bakuwangula. 
\q1 Kaakano otubidde mu ttosi. 
\q2 Mikwano gyo gikudduseeko.’  
\p  
\v 23 “Bakazi bo n’abaana bo bonna balireetebwa eri Abakaludaaya. Ggwe kennyini tojja kubasumattuka ojja kukwatibwa kabaka w’e Babulooni; n’ekibuga kino kijja kwokebwa.” 
\p  
\v 24 Awo Zeddekiya n’agamba Yeremiya nti, “Tobuulirako muntu n’omu ku bye twogedde, bw’onookikola ojja kufa.  
\v 25 Abakungu bwe banaawulira nti wayogeddeko nange ne bajja ne bakubuuza nti, ‘Tubuulire kye wagambye kabaka ne kabaka kye yakuzeemu, totukweka kintu kyonna sikulwa nga tukutta,’  
\v 26 bagambe nti, ‘Mbadde neegayirira kabaka aleme kunzizaayo eri mu nnyumba ya Yonasaani okufiira eyo.’ ” 
\p  
\v 27 Abakungu bonna ne bajja eri Yeremiya okumubuuza, n’abaddamu byonna nga kabaka bye yamulagira okwogera. Ne bataddayo ku mubuuza kintu kyonna, kubanga tewaali n’omu eyali awulidde bye yali ayogedde ne kabaka. 
\p  
\v 28 Yeremiya n’asigala mu luggya lw’abakuumi okutuusa olunaku Yerusaalemi lwe kyawambibwa. 
\s1 Okugwa kwa Yerusaalemi 
\p Yerusaalemi bwe kiti bwe kyawambibwa: 
\c 39  
\nb  
\v 1 Mu mwaka ogwomwenda ogw’obufuzi kwa Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda, mu mwezi ogw’ekkumi, Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni, n’alumba Yerusaalemi, n’eggye lye lyonna, n’akizingiza.  
\v 2 Ku lunaku olw’omwenda olw’omwezi ogwokuna ogw’omwaka ogw’ekkumi n’ogumu ogw’obufuzi kwa Zeddekiya, ekisenge ky’ekibuga kyabotolwa.  
\v 3 Awo Nerugalusalezeeri, ne Samugaluneebo, ne Salusekimu, ne Labusalisi, ne Nerugalusalezeeri, ne Labumagi, n’abakungu abalala bonna aba kabaka w’e Babulooni ne bajja ne batuula mu mulyango ogwa wakati ogwa Yerusaalemi.  
\v 4 Awo Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda n’abaserikale be bonna bwe babalaba ne bava mu kibuga kiro ne badduka; ne bayita mu nnimiro ya kabaka, nga bayita mu mulyango wakati w’ebisenge ebibiri, ne boolekera Alaba. 
\p  
\v 5 Naye eggye ly’Abakaludaaya ne libagoba ne lisanga Zeddekiya mu nsenyi ez’e Yeriko, ne bamuwamba, ne bamuleeta eri kabaka Nebukadduneeza ow’e Babulooni e Libuna mu nsi y’e Kamasi; n’amusalira eyo omusango.  
\v 6 Kabaka w’e Babulooni n’attira batabani ba Zeddekiya mu maaso ga kitaabwe e Libuna, era kabaka w’e Babulooni n’atta abakungu ba Yuda bonna.  
\v 7 Nebukadduneeza n’aggyamu Zeddekiya amaaso, n’amusiba mu masamba n’amutwala e Babulooni. 
\p  
\v 8 Abakaludaaya ne bookya ennyumba ya kabaka n’ennyumba z’abantu, ne bamenya n’ebisenge bya Yerusaalemi.  
\v 9 Awo Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’eggye n’atwala abantu abaali basigaddewo mu kibuga, n’abo abaali bamwegasseeko, n’abo abaali basigaddewo mu bifo ebirala, e Babulooni.  
\v 10 Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’eggye, n’aleka abamu ku bantu abaavu abaali batalina kantu, mu nsi ya Yuda; n’abawa ebibanja n’ennimiro z’emizabbibu. 
\p  
\v 11 Awo Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni yali awadde Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’eggye lya kabaka w’e Babulooni, ebiragiro bino ebikwata ku Yeremiya ng’amugamba nti,  
\v 12 “Mmutwale omulabirire: tomubonyaabonya wabula mukolere byonna by’ayagala.”  
\v 13 Awo Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’eggye, ne Nebusazibaani omukungu ow’oku ntikko ne Nerugalusalezeeri, ne Labumagi, n’abakungu bonna aba kabaka w’e Babulooni,  
\v 14 ne batumya ne baggya Yeremiya mu luggya lw’abaserikale. Ne bamukwasa Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu, mutabani wa Safani, amuzzeeyo ewaabwe. Olwo n’asigala n’abantu be. 
\p  
\v 15 Yeremiya bwe yali asibiddwa mu luggya lw’abaserikale abakuumi, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kimujjira nga kigamba nti,  
\v 16 “Genda ogambe Ebedumeleki Omuwesiyopya nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Nnaatera okutuukiriza ebigambo byange eri ekibuga kino nga nkozesa ebibonoobono, si kukulaakulana. Mu biseera ebyo birituukirizibwa nga mulaba n’amaaso gammwe.  
\v 17 Naye ndikuwonya ku lunaku olwo,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*; ‘toliweebwayo eri abo b’otya.  
\v 18 Ndikuwonya; tolittibwa, olisigala ng’oli mulamu, kubanga onneesiga, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*.’ ” 
\c 40  
\p  
\v 1 Ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya, nga Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’abambowa amusumuludde e Laama, bwe yamusanga ng’asibiddwa mu masamba n’abasibe abalala bonna ab’e Yerusaalemi ne Yuda abaali batwalibwa e Babulooni mu busibe.  
\v 2 Omuduumizi w’abaserikale yatwala Yeremiya n’amugamba nti, “\nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo, ye yaleeta ekivume kino ku kifo kino.  
\v 3 Kaakano \nd Mukama\nd* akireese era akikoze nga bwe yasuubiza. Bino byonna byabaawo kubanga abantu bo baasobya eri \nd Mukama\nd* ne batamugondera.  
\v 4 Naye leero nkusumulula okuva mu njegere ez’oku mikono gyo. Jjangu tugende ffembi e Babulooni obanga oyagala, nnaakulabirira; naye bw’oba nga toyagala, tojja. Laba, ensi yonna eri mu maaso go, genda yonna gy’oyagala.”  
\v 5 Wabula Yeremiya nga tannaba kukyuka kugenda, Nebuzaladaani n’ayongerako nti, “Ddayo eri Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu mutabani wa Safani, kabaka w’e Babulooni gw’afudde Gavana w’ebibuga bya Yuda, obeere naye mu bantu, oba genda yonna gy’osiima okubeera.” Awo omuduumizi w’abambowa n’amuwa ebyokulya n’ekirabo n’amuleka. 
\p  
\v 6 Awo Yeremiya n’agenda ewa Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu e Mizupa n’abeera naye n’abantu abaaliyo abaali balekeddwa mu nsi eyo. 
\s1 Gedaliya Attibwa 
\p  
\v 7 Awo abakulu b’eggye lya Yuda bonna n’abasajja baabwe abaali bakyali mu byalo ne bawulira nti, Kabaka w’e Babulooni alonze Gedaliya omwana wa Akikamu okuba Gavana w’ensi era ng’amuwadde obuvunaanyizibwa bw’abantu bonna, abasajja, n’abakazi, n’abaana, n’abaali basembayo obwavu mu nsi abataatwalibwa mu buwaŋŋanguse e Babulooni.  
\v 8 Awo Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya, ne Yokanaani ne Yonasaani batabani ba Kaleya, ne Seraya mutabani wa Tanukumesi, ne batabani ba Efayi Omunetofa, ne Yezaniya omwana w’omu Maakasi, ne bagenda n’abasajja baabwe eri Gedaliya e Mizupa.  
\v 9 Awo Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu mutabani wa Safani n’abalayirira bo n’abasajja baabwe ng’ayogera nti, “Temutya kuweereza Bakaludaaya. Mubeere mu nsi, muweereze kabaka w’e Babulooni munaaba bulungi.  
\v 10 Nze kennyini nzija kusigala e Mizupa okubakiikirira eri Abakaludaaya abajja gye tuli, naye mmwe mukungule emizabbibu, n’ebibala eby’omu kyeya, mukuŋŋaanye n’omuzigo mubiteeke mu materekero gammwe, mubeere mu bibuga bye mufuga.” 
\p  
\v 11 Awo Abayudaaya bonna mu Mowaabu, ne Amoni, ne Edomu n’ensi endala zonna bwe baawulira nti, Kabaka w’e Babulooni yali aleseeyo abantu mu Yuda era nga ataddewo Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu, mutabani wa Safani okuba Gavana waabwe,  
\v 12 bonna ne bakomawo mu nsi ya Yuda eri Gedaliya e Mizupa, ne bava mu nsi zonna gye baali basaasaanidde. Ne bakungula ebirime mu bungi, emizabbibu n’ebibala eby’omu kyeya. 
\p  
\v 13 Awo Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’abakulu bonna ab’ebibinja bya magye abaali mu byalo ne bajja eri Gedaliya e Mizupa.  
\v 14 Ne bamugamba nti, “Tomanyi nga Baalisi kabaka w’abaana ba Amoni atumye Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya okukutta?” Naye Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu teyakikkiriza. 
\p  
\v 15 Awo Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’ayogera ne Gedaliya e Mizupa kyama ng’agamba nti, “Ka ŋŋende nkwegayiridde nzite Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya, so tewaliba muntu alikimanya. Lwaki akutta, Abayudaaya bonna abakuŋŋaanidde gy’oli basaasaane, ekitundu kya Yuda ekifisseewo nakyo kizikirire?” 
\p  
\v 16 Naye Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu n’agamba Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya nti, “Tokola kintu bwe kityo! Ky’oyogera ku Isimayiri si kituufu.” 
\c 41  
\p  
\v 1 Mu mwezi ogw’omusanvu Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya, mutabani wa Erisaama, omu ku balangira ate nga ye omu ku bakulu b’eggye lya Yuda n’ajja n’abasajja kkumi eri Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu e Mizupa. Bwe baali nga balya,  
\v 2 Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya n’abasajja ekkumi abaali naye ne bayimuka ne batta Gedaliya, mutabani wa Akikamu, mutabani wa Safani, n’ekitala, gavana, kabaka w’e Babulooni gwe yali ataddewo okufuga mu nsi.  
\v 3 Isimayiri n’atta n’Abayudaaya bonna abaali ne Gedaliya e Mizupa, n’abaserikale Abakaludaaya abaaliyo. 
\p  
\v 4 Olunaku olwaddirira Gedaliya ng’amaze okuttibwa, nga tewannabaawo akimanyiiko,  
\v 5 abasajja kinaana abaali beemwedde ebirevu, nga bayuzizza engoye zaabwe era nga beesazeesaze, bajja okuva e Sekemu, ne Siiro ne Samaliya, nga baleese ekiweebwayo eky’emmere ey’empeke n’obubaane eby’omu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*.  
\v 6 Isimayiri omwana wa Nesaniya n’ava e Mizupa okubasisinkana ng’agenda bw’akaaba. Bwe yabatuukako, n’abagamba nti, “Mujje eri Gedaliya omwana wa Akikamu.”  
\v 7 Bwe baatuuka mu kibuga, Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya n’abasajja be ne batta abamu ku basajja abo, ne babasuula mu kinnya.  
\v 8 Naye kkumi ku bo ne bagamba Isimayiri nti, “Totutta! Tulina eŋŋaano ne sayiri, n’omuzigo, n’omubisi gw’enjuki, tubikwese mu nnimiro.” Awo ne babaleka ne batabattira wamu na bali abalala.  
\v 9 Ekinnya mwe baasuula emirambo gy’abasajja bonna be battira awamu ne Gedaliya, kye kiri kabaka Asa kye yali asimye ng’alwanyisa Baasa kabaka wa Isirayiri. Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya yakijjuza abafu. 
\p  
\v 10 Isimayiri n’awamba abantu bonna abalala abaali e Mizupa, abawala ba kabaka n’abalala bonna abaali basigaddeyo, Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’eggye lya kabaka Nebukadduneeza be yali awadde Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu. Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya n’abatwala nga bawambe ne yeetegeka okubasomosa okubatwala eri Abamoni. 
\p  
\v 11 Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’abaduumizi bonna abaali naye bwe baawulira ebikolobero Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya bye yali akoze,  
\v 12 ne batwala abasajja baabwe bonna ne bagenda okulwanyisa Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya. Ne bamutuukako okumpi n’amazzi amangi e Gibyoni.  
\v 13 Abantu bonna abaali ne Isimayiri bwe baalaba Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’abaduumizi ba magye be yali nabo, ne basanyuka.  
\v 14 Abantu bonna Isimayiri be yali awambye e Mizupa ne bakyuka ne bagenda eri Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya.  
\v 15 Naye Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya ne basajja be munaana ne batoloka okuva ku Yokanaani ne bagenda mu ba Amoni. 
\p  
\v 16 Awo Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’abaduumizi b’eggye bonna abaali naye ne batwala abawambe okuva e Mizupa be baali baggye ku Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya ng’amaze okutta Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu: abaserikale, n’abakazi, n’abaana n’abakungu b’omu lubiri be yali aggye e Gibyoni.  
\v 17 Ne beeyongerayo ne bayimirirako e Gerusukimamu okumpi ne Besirekemu, nga boolekedde e Misiri,  
\v 18 badduke Abakaludaaya. Baali batidde Abakaludaaya kubanga Isimayiri mutabani wa Nesaniya yali asse Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu, oyo kabaka w’e Babulooni gwe yali ataddewo okufuga ensi nga gavana. 
\c 42  
\p  
\v 1 Awo abaduumizi ba magye bonna, ng’ogasseeko Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya ne Yezaniya mutabani wa Kosaaya, n’abantu bonna okuva ku asokerwako wansi okutuuka ku akomererayo waggulu baatuukirira  
\v 2 nnabbi Yeremiya ne bamugamba nti, “Tukwegayiridde, wulira okusaba kwaffe osabe \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo ku lw’abantu bano bonna abafisseewo. Kale naawe nga bw’olaba, abaali abangi kaakano tusigaddewo batono nnyo.  
\v 3 Saba \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo atubuulire gye tusaanye okulaga ne kye tusaanye okukola.” 
\p  
\v 4 Nnabbi Yeremiya n’abagamba nti, “Mbawulidde, ddala nzija kubasabira eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wammwe nga bwe munsabye; nzija kubabuulira byonna \nd Mukama\nd* by’anaŋŋamba, sirina kye nnaabakisa.” 
\p  
\v 5 Awo ne bagamba Yeremiya nti, “\nd Mukama\nd* abeere omujulirwa ow’amazima era omwesigwa gye tuli, bwe tutalikola kyonna \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo ky’anaakutuma okutugamba.  
\v 6 Oba kyangu oba kikalubo tujja kugondera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe, gye tukutuma kaakano, tulyoke tufune emirembe, kubanga tujja kugondera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe.” 
\p  
\v 7 Bwe waayitawo ennaku kkumi ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya.  
\v 8 N’alyoka ayita Yokanaani omwana wa Kaleya n’abaduumizi b’eggye lya Yuda bonna abaali naye, n’abantu bonna okuva ku asokerwako wansi okutuuka ku akomererayo waggulu.  
\v 9 N’abagamba nti, “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri, gye mwantuma okubabuuliza nti,  
\v 10 ‘Bwe munaasigala mu nsi eno, nzija kubazimba era siibaleke kugwa. Nzija kubasimba so si kubasimbula, kubanga nnumiddwa olw’ekikangabwa kye mbatuusizzaako.  
\v 11 Temutya kabaka w’e Babulooni, kaakano gwe mutya. Temumutya, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, kubanga ndi nammwe era nzija kubalokola, mbanunule mu mukono gwa kabaka oyo.  
\v 12 Nzija kubalaga ekisa alyoke abakwatirwe ekisa, abakomyewo mu nsi yammwe.’ 
\p  
\v 13 “Wabula bwe mugamba nti, ‘Tetuusigale mu nsi eno gye mbakomezzaamu,’ olwo munaaba temugondedde \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wammwe.  
\v 14 Bwe mugamba nti, ‘Nedda, tujja kugenda tubeere e Misiri, gye tutaalabe ntalo wadde okuwulira ekkondeere nga livuga oba okubulwa omugaati ogw’okulya,’  
\v 15 kale nno muwulire ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*, mmwe abaasigalawo mu Yuda. Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Bwe munaamalirira okugenda e Misiri era ne mugenda okubeererayo ddala,  
\v 16 olwo ekitala kye mutya kijja kubasanga eyo, n’enjala gye mutya ejja kubagoberera e Misiri era eyo gye mulifiira.  
\v 17 Mumanyire ddala nti, Abo bonna abamaliridde okugenda e Misiri okusenga eyo balifa kitala, n’enjala ne kawumpuli; tewaliba n’omu alisigalawo wadde okuwona ekikangabwa kye ndibaleetako.’  
\v 18 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, ‘Ng’obusungu bwange n’ekiruyi bwe bifukiddwa ku abo abali mu Yerusaalemi, bwe kityo ekiruyi kyange bwe kinaafukibwa ku mmwe bwe munaagenda e Misiri. Munaabeera kya kukolimirwa, era kya ntiisa, era kya kusalirwa musango era kivume: temuliraba kifo kino nate.’ 
\p  
\v 19 “Mmwe abafisseewo ku Yuda, \nd Mukama\nd* abagambye nti, ‘Temugenda Misiri.’ Mumanye kino nga mbalabula leero  
\v 20 nti, Mwakola ekisobyo kinene bwe mwantuma eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wammwe ne mugamba nti, ‘Tusabire eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe: tubuulire byonna by’agamba tujja kubikola.’  
\v 21 Mbabuulidde leero, naye era temugondedde \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wammwe mu byonna bye yantuma okubagamba.  
\v 22 Kale nno mutegeerere ddala kino nga mulittibwa na kitala, oba njala oba kawumpuli mu nsi gye mwagala okugenda okusengamu.” 
\c 43  
\p  
\v 1 Yeremiya bwe yamala okutegeeza abantu ebigambo byonna \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe bye yamutuma okubagamba,  
\v 2 Azaliya mutabani wa Kosaaya ne Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’abasajja bonna ab’amalala ne bagamba Yeremiya nti, “Olimba! \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda wo takutumye kugamba nti, ‘Temugenda Misiri kusenga eyo.’  
\v 3 Naye Baluki mutabani wa Neriya y’akusendasenda otugabule mu mukono gw’Abakaludaaya, batutte oba batutwale mu buwaŋŋanguse e Babulooni.” 
\p  
\v 4 Awo Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’abaduumizi ba magye bonna n’abantu bonna ne bajeemera ekiragiro kya \nd Mukama\nd* eky’okusigala mu nsi ya Yuda.  
\v 5 Yokanaani mutabani wa Kaleya n’abaduumizi ba magye ga Yuda bonna ne bakulembera abantu ba Yuda abaali basigaddewo nga bakomyewo okuva mu mawanga gonna gye baali baddukidde okubeera mu nsi ya Yuda.  
\v 6 Ne batwala n’abasajja bonna, n’abakazi n’abaana n’abawala ba kabaka, Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’eggye lya kabaka w’e Babulooni be yali alekedde Gedaliya mutabani wa Akikamu, mutabani wa Safani, ne nnabbi Yeremiya ne Baluki mutabani wa Neriya.  
\v 7 Awo ne bayingira e Misiri nga bajeemedde \nd Mukama\nd*, ne bagenda okutuukira ddala e Tapaneese. 
\p  
\v 8 Bwe baba bali e Tapaneese, ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* ne kijjira Yeremiya nti,  
\v 9 “Twala amayinja amanene ogaziike mu bbumba mu lubalaza olw’amatoffaali ku mulyango gw’olubiri lwa Falaawo e Tapaneese, ng’Abayudaaya bonna balaba.  
\v 10 Obagambe nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Nditumya omuddu wange Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni, era nditeeka entebe ye ey’obwakabaka ku mayinja gano ge nziise wano. Ku go kwalikuba eweema ye ey’obwakabaka.  
\v 11 Alijja n’alumba Misiri, atte abo ab’okufa, awambe n’abo ab’okuwambibwa, n’ab’okuttibwa n’ekitala battibwe n’ekitala.  
\v 12 Alikoleeza omuliro ku masabo ga bakatonda b’e Misiri, n’abatwala mu busibe nga alese amasabo gaabwe agookezza. Ng’omulunzi w’endiga bwe yeezingirira ekyambalo kye, bw’atyo bw’alyezingirira ensi y’e Misiri n’avaayo nga tewali kabi konna kamutuuseeko.  
\v 13 Alimenyamenya empagi ezaawongebwa mu ssabo ly’enjuba mu Misiri, n’ayokya n’amasabo ga bakatonda b’e Misiri.’ ” 
\c 44  
\p  
\v 1 Ekigambo ne kijjira Yeremiya ekikwata ku Bayudaaya bonna abaali mu nsi y’e Misiri e Migudooli n’e Tapaneese n’e Noofu ne mu nsi ey’e Pasuloosi nga kigamba nti,  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Mwalaba ekikangabwa ekinene kye naleeta ku Yerusaalemi ne ku bibuga byonna ebya Yuda. Leero matongo  
\v 3 olw’ebibi bye baakola. Bankwasa obusungu olw’okwotereza bakatonda abalala obubaane n’okusinza, bo newaakubadde mmwe wadde bajjajjammwe be batamanyangako.  
\v 4 Emirundi mingi natuma abaddu bange bannabbi, abaabagamba nti, ‘Temukola bintu bino eby’omuzizo bye nkyawa!’  
\v 5 Naye tebaawulira wadde okufaayo; tebaalekayo mpisa zaabwe embi wadde okulekayo okwotereza bakatonda abalala obubaane.  
\v 6 Noolwekyo, obusungu bwange obungi ennyo kyebwava bubabuubuukira; ne buzinda ebibuga bya Yuda n’enguudo za Yerusaalemi era ne bifuuka amatongo, ne leero. 
\p  
\v 7 “Kale kaakano bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Lwaki mweretako akabi akanene bwe kati nga musala ku Yuda abasajja n’abakazi, n’abaana abato n’abawere aba Yuda ne mutalekaawo muntu?  
\v 8 Lwaki munsunguwaza olw’ebyo emikono gyammwe bye gikoze, nga mwotereza bakatonda abalala obubaane e Misiri, gye mwajja okubeera? Mujja kwezikiriza mufuuke eky’omuzizo n’eky’okukolimirwa mu mawanga gonna ag’omu nsi.  
\v 9 Mwerabidde ebibi bakitammwe ne bakabaka ba Yuda ne bakazi bammwe bye baakola era n’ebibi bye mwakola mmwe ne bakazi bammwe mu nsi ya Yuda ne mu nguudo za Yerusaalemi?  
\v 10 Naye n’okutuusa leero tebeetoowazizza wadde okutya, wadde okugondera amateeka gange n’ebiragiro bye nabateekerawo mmwe ne bajjajjammwe. 
\p  
\v 11 “Noolwekyo, bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, Mmaliridde okubazikiriza mmwe ne Yuda yonna.  
\v 12 Ndiggyawo abaasigalira mu Yuda abaamalirira okugenda e Misiri okusenga eyo. Bonna balizikiririra mu Misiri, balifa ekitala oba enjala. Okuva ku muto okutuuka ku mukulu asingayo balifa era balifuuka ekyenyinyalwa n’eky’okusekererwa era n’okukolimirwa.  
\v 13 Ndibonereza abo ababeera mu Misiri, bafe ekitala, n’enjala ne kawumpuli, nga bwe nabonereza Yerusaalemi.  
\v 14 Tewali n’omu ku baasigalawo mu Yuda eyaddukira e Misiri, aliwona oba alisigalawo okudda mu nsi ya Yuda, gye beegomba okudda, tewali aliddayo okuggyako abatono ennyo.” 
\p  
\v 15 Awo abasajja bonna abaali bamanyi nga bakazi baabwe baali bootereza bakatonda abalala obubaane, n’abakazi abalala abaaliwo, olukuŋŋaana nga lunene n’abantu bonna abaali babeera mu Misiri e Pasuloosi, ne baddamu Yeremiya nga boogera nti,  
\v 16 “Tetujja kuwulira bubaka bw’oyogedde naffe mu linnya lya \nd Mukama\nd*!  
\v 17 Tujja kukola byonna bye twagambye okukola. Tujja kwotereza kabaka omukazi ow’eggulu obubaane, tuweeyo n’ebiweebwayo ebyokunywa nga bwe twakolanga, ffe ne bakitaffe, ne bakabaka baffe n’abakungu baffe mu bibuga bya Yuda ne mu nguudo z’e Yerusaalemi. Mu biseera ebyo twalina emmere nnyingi era nga tuli bulungi nga tetutuukibwako kabi.  
\v 18 Naye okuva lwe twalekeraawo okwotereza kabaka omukazi ow’eggulu obubaane, n’okumuwa ekiweebwayo ekyokunywa, tetubadde na kantu konna era tubadde tuzikirira n’ekitala n’enjala.” 
\p  
\v 19 Abakazi ne bongerako nti, “Bwe twayotereza kabaka omukazi ow’eggulu obubaane ne tumuwa n’ekiweebwayo ekyokunywa, abaami baffe tebaamanya nti twali tumukolera obugaati obuliko ekifaananyi kye ne tumuwa n’ekiweebwayo ekyokunywa?” 
\p  
\v 20 Awo Yeremiya n’agamba abantu bonna, abasajja n’abakazi n’abantu bonna abaali bamuzzeemu nti,  
\v 21 “Obubaane bwammwe bwe mwayotereza mu bibuga bya Yuda ne mu nguudo za Yerusaalemi, mmwe ne bakitammwe, ne bakabaka bammwe, n’abakungu n’abantu bonna mu nsi, ebyo \nd Mukama\nd* si bye yajjukira n’alowoozaako?  
\v 22 \nd Mukama\nd* nga takyayinza kugumiikiriza bikolwa byammwe bibi n’eby’emizizo bye mwakola, ensi yammwe kyeyava efuuka ekikolimo n’ekyenyinyalwa era eteriimu bantu, nga bweri leero.  
\v 23 Kubanga mwotereza obubaane abalala era ne mukola ebibi mu maaso ga \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ne mutamugondera wadde okugoberera amateeka ge oba ebiragiro bye oba bye yategeeza, emitawaana gibagidde nga kaakano bwe mulabye.” 
\p  
\v 24 Awo Yeremiya n’agamba abantu bonna, ng’ogasseeko abakazi nti, “Muwulire ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, abantu mwenna aba Yuda mu Misiri.  
\v 25 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, mmwe ne bakazi bammwe mulaze mu bikolwa byammwe ebyo bye mwasuubiza nti, ‘Tujja kukola nga bwe tweyama okwotereza kabaka omukazi ow’eggulu obubaane era n’okumuwa ekiweebwayo ekyokunywa.’ 
\p “Mugende mu maaso, mukole bye mwasuubiza! Mutuukirize obweyamo bwammwe!  
\v 26 Naye muwulire ekigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd*, mmwe Abayudaaya mwenna abali mu Misiri. ‘Ndayira mu linnya lyange ekkulu,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Tewali n’omu ku abo abaava mu Yuda ababeera mu Misiri, aliddayo okuyita erinnya lyange wadde okulayira nti, “Nga \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda bw’ali omulamu.”  
\v 27 Kubanga mbawaddeyo eri akabi, si lwa bulungi; Abayudaaya abali mu Misiri balimalibwawo n’ekitala n’enjala okutuusa bonna lwe baliggwaawo.  
\v 28 Abo abaliwona ekitala ne baddayo mu Yuda okuva e Misiri baliba batono nnyo. Olwo abalisigalawo bonna okuva mu Yuda abajja okubeera mu Misiri, balitegeera ekigambo ekirikola, ekyange oba ekyabwe. 
\p  
\v 29 “ ‘Kano ke kanaabeera akabonero gye muli nti ndibabonerereza mu kifo kino,’ bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, ‘Mulyoke mumanye nga okulabula kwange okw’okubabonereza kujja kutuukirira.’  
\v 30 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, ‘Ŋŋenda kuwaayo Falaawo Kofera kabaka w’e Misiri eri abalabe be abanoonya okumutta, nga bwe n’awaayo Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda eri Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni, omulabe eyamunoonya okumutta.’ ” 
\c 45  
\s1 Obubaka eri Baluki 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo nnabbi Yeremiya kye yagamba Baluki mutabani wa Neriya mu mwaka ogwokuna ogw’obufuzi bwa Yekoyakimu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda, nga Baluki amaze okuwandiika ku muzingo nti,  
\v 2 “Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, Katonda wa Isirayiri gy’oli, ggwe Baluki nti,  
\v 3 Wagamba nti, ‘Zinsanze. \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda agasse ennaku ku bulumi bwange; mpweddemu endasi era zijjudde okusinda n’obutawummula.’ ”  
\v 4 \nd Mukama\nd* yagamba nti, “Mugambe bw’oti nti, ‘Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti: ndimenya bye nazimba, nkuule bye nasimba, mu ggwanga lyonna.  
\v 5 Kale lwaki weenoonyeza ebintu ebirungi? Tobinoonya. Kubanga ndireeta akabi ku bantu bonna, bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, naye buli gy’olaga nnaakuyambanga osigale ng’oli mulamu.’ ” 
\c 46  
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Misiri 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ekyajjira nnabbi Yeremiya ekikwata ku mawanga: 
\b  
\p  
\v 2 Ebikwata ku Misiri: 
\b  
\p Buno bwe bubaka obukwata ku ggye lya Falaawo Neko kabaka w’e Misiri, eryawangulwa e Kalukemisi, Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni lye yakuba mu mwaka ogwokuna ogw’obufuzi bwa Yekoyakimu mutabani wa Yosiya kabaka wa Yuda ku Mugga Fulaati. 
\q1  
\v 3 “Mutegeke engabo zammwe, 
\q2 ennene n’entono mukumbe okugenda mu lutalo! 
\q1  
\v 4 Mutegeke embalaasi 
\q2 muzeebagale! 
\q1 Muyimirire mu bifo byammwe 
\q2 n’esseppeewo zammwe! 
\q1 Muzigule amafumu, 
\q2 mwambale ebizibaawo eby’ebyuma! 
\q1  
\v 5 Kiki kye ndaba? 
\q2 Batidde, 
\q1 badda ennyuma, 
\q2 abalwanyi baabwe bawanguddwa. 
\q1 Badduka mu bwangu 
\q2 awatali kutunula mabega, 
\q2 era waliwo okufa ku buli luuyi,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 6 “Abawenyusi b’embiro tebasobola kuwona 
\q2 n’ab’amaanyi tebasobola kwewonya. 
\q1 Beesittala 
\q2 ne bagwa mu bukiikakkono obw’Omugga Fulaati. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 7 “Ani oyo ayimuka ng’omugga Kiyira, 
\q2 ng’emigga egy’amazzi agabimba? 
\q1  
\v 8 Misiri eyimuka nga Kiyira, 
\q2 ng’emigga egy’amazzi agabimba. 
\q1 Agamba nti, ‘Ndisituka ne mbuutikira ensi yonna. 
\q2 Ndizikiriza ebibuga n’abantu baabyo.’ 
\q1  
\v 9 Mulumbe, mmwe embalaasi! 
\q2 Muzidduse n’amaanyi, mmwe abalwanyi b’oku mbalaasi! 
\q1 Mukumbe mmwe abalwanyi, 
\q2 abasajja b’e Kuusi ne Puuti\f + \fr 46:9 \ft Puuli ne Puuti bye bimu. Puuti ye Libiya oba ekitundu ekyetoolodde n’okutuukira ddala ku Somaliya\f* abeettika engabo, 
\q2 abasajja b’e Luudi abakozesa obusaale. 
\q1  
\v 10 Naye olunaku olwo lwa Mukama, \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, 
\q2 olunaku olw’okuwalanirako eggwanga, olw’okusalira abalabe omusango. 
\q1 Ekitala kijja kulya nga kimaliddwa, 
\q2 okutuusa nga kyemazeeko ennyonta y’omusaayi. 
\q1 Kubanga Mukama, \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, 
\q2 alibawaayo babeere ng’ekiweebwayo mu nsi ey’obukiikakkono ku Mugga Fulaati. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 “Genda e Gireyaadi ofune eddagala ery’okusaaba, 
\q2 ggwe Omuwala Embeerera owa Misiri. 
\q1 Naye mwongerera bwereere obujjanjabi; 
\q2 temujja kuwonyezebwa. 
\q1  
\v 12 Amawanga gajja kuwulira obuswavu bwammwe; 
\q2 emiranga gyammwe gijja kujjuza ensi. 
\q1 Omulwanyi omu alitomera omulala 
\q2 bombi ne bagwa.” 
\p  
\v 13 Buno bwe bubaka \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda bwe yayogera eri nnabbi Yeremiya ku bikwata ku kujja kwa Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni okulumba Misiri: 
\q1  
\v 14 “Langirira kino mu Misiri, era okyogere e Migudooli; 
\q2 kirangirire e Tapaneese ne Noofu nti, 
\q1 ‘Muyimirire mu bifo byammwe mwetegeke 
\q2 kubanga ekitala kirya abo ababeetoolodde.’ 
\q1  
\v 15 Lwaki abalwanyi bo bagudde wansi? 
\q2 Tebasobola kuyimirira, kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ajja kubasindika wansi. 
\q1  
\v 16 Balyesittala emirundi egiwera; 
\q2 baligwiragana. 
\q1 Bagambe nti, ‘Yimuka, tuddeyo 
\q2 eri abantu baffe era n’ensi zaffe, 
\q2 tuve awali ekitala ky’oyo atunyigiriza.’ 
\q1  
\v 17 Eyo gye baliwowogganira nti, 
\q2 ‘Falaawo kabaka w’e Misiri mulekaanyi bulekaanyi 
\q2 afiiriddwa omukisa gwe.’  
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 “Nga bwe ndi omulamu,” bw’ayogera oyo Kabaka 
\q2 ayitibwa \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, 
\q1 “Waliwo alijja ali nga Taboli wakati mu nsozi, 
\q2 nga Kulumeeri ku nnyanja. 
\q1  
\v 19 Musibe engugu zammwe muwaŋŋanguke, 
\q2 mmwe abali mu Misiri 
\q1 kubanga Noofu kirifuuka matongo, 
\q2 ekiryaawo omutali bantu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 “Misiri nte nduusi nnungi nnyo, 
\q2 naye kawawa avudde mu bukiikakkono azze okumulumba. 
\q1  
\v 21 N’abajaasi be abapangise 
\q2 bagezze ng’ennyana. 
\q1 Nabo bajja kukyuka badduke, 
\q2 tebaasobole kuyimirirawo, 
\q1 kubanga olunaku olw’ekikangabwa lubajjira, 
\q2 ekiseera kyabwe eky’okubonerezebwa kisembedde. 
\q1  
\v 22 Misiri alikaaba ng’omusota ogudduka, 
\q2 omulabe alimulumba mu maanyi, 
\q1 amujjire n’embazzi, 
\q2 ng’abatemi b’emiti. 
\q1  
\v 23 Balitema ekibira kye,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q2 “newaakubadde nga kikutte nnyo. 
\q1 Bangi n’okusinga enzige, 
\q2 tebasobola kubalika. 
\q1  
\v 24 Muwala wa Misiri aliswazibwa, 
\q2 aweebweyo mu mukono gw’abo abava mu bukiikakkono.” 
\p  
\v 25 \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri, agamba nti, “Nnaatera okuleeta ekibonerezo ku Amoni katonda w’e Tebeesi, ne ku Falaawo, ne ku Misiri, ne ku bakatonda be, ne ku bakabaka be, ne ku abo abeesiga Falaawo.  
\v 26 Ndibawaayo eri abo abaagala okubatta, eri Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni n’abakungu be. Wabula oluvannyuma, Misiri eribeeramu abantu nga bwe yali edda,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 27 “Totya, ggwe Yakobo omuweereza wange; 
\q2 toggwaamu maanyi, ggwe Isirayiri. 
\q1 Ddala ddala ndikununula okuva mu kifo eky’ewala, 
\q2 n’ezzadde lyo ndinunule okuva mu nsi ey’obuwaŋŋanguse bwalyo. 
\q1 Yakobo aliddamu okufuna emirembe n’atebenkera, 
\q2 era tewali alimutiisa. 
\q1  
\v 28 Totya, ggwe Yakobo omuddu wange, 
\q2 kubanga ndi naawe,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 “Wadde nga nazikiririza ddala amawanga gonna 
\q2 gye nabasaasaanyiza, 
\q2 naye mmwe siribazikiririza ddala. 
\q1 Ndibabonereza naye mu bwenkanya; 
\q2 siribaleka nga temubonerezebbwa.” 
\c 47  
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Bafirisuuti 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ekyajjira nnabbi Yeremiya ekikwata ku Bafirisuuti nga Falaawo tannalumba Gaza nga kigamba nti: 
\b  
\p  
\v 2 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, 
\q1 “Laba amazzi agatumbira mu bukiikakkono, 
\q2 galifuuka omugga ogwanjaala. 
\q1 Galyanjaala ku nsi 
\q2 ne mu bibuga byonna ebigirimu n’ababituulamu. 
\q1 Abantu balikaaba; 
\q2 bonna abali mu nsi baliwowoggana. 
\q1  
\v 3 Olw’emisinde gy’embalaasi ezidduka 
\q2 n’okufuumuuka kw’amagaali g’omulabe 
\q2 era n’okuwuuma kwa nnamuziga, 
\q1 bakitaabwe tebajja kukyuka kuyamba baana baabwe, 
\q2 emikono gyabwe gya kulebera. 
\q1  
\v 4 Kubanga olunaku lutuuse 
\q2 okuzikiriza Abafirisuuti bonna, 
\q1 n’okusalako bonna abandisigaddewo 
\q2 abandiyambye Ttuulo ne Sidoni. 
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* wa kuzikiriza Abafirisuuti 
\q2 abaasigalawo ku mbalama z’ekizinga Kafutoli. 
\q1  
\v 5 Gaza alimwa omutwe gwe ng’akungubaga. 
\q2 Asukulooni alisirisibwa. 
\q1 Ggwe eyasigala mu kiwonvu, 
\q2 olituusa ddi okwesalaasala? 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 “ ‘Ayi ggwe ekitala kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, okaaba, 
\q2 obudde bunaatuuka ddi owummule? 
\q1 Ddayo mu kiraato kyo 
\q2 sirika teweenyeenya.’ 
\q1  
\v 7 Naye kiyinza kitya okuwummula 
\q2 nga \nd Mukama\nd* y’akiragidde, 
\q1 ng’akiragidde 
\q2 okulumba Asukulooni n’olubalama lw’ennyanja?” 
\c 48  
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Mowaabu 
\p  
\v 1 Ebikwata ku Mowaabu: 
\b  
\p Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, 
\q1 “Zikisanze Nebo, kubanga kijja kuzikirizibwa, 
\q2 Kiriyasayimu kiswale kiwambibwe, 
\q2 ekigo eky’amaanyi kijja kuswala kimenyebwe. 
\q1  
\v 2 Mowaabu taddeyo kutenderezebwa; 
\q2 mu Kesuboni abantu balitegeka okugwa kwe, nga boogera nti, 
\q2 ‘Mujje, tumalewo ensi eyo.’ 
\q1 Nammwe, mmwe Madumeni mulisirisibwa, 
\q2 n’ekitala kirikugoberera. 
\q1  
\v 3 Muwulirize emiranga egiva e Kolonayimu, 
\q2 okwonoonekerwa n’okuzikirizibwa okunene. 
\q1  
\v 4 Mowaabu alimenyebwa; 
\q2 abawere ne bakaaba. 
\q1  
\v 5 Bakwata ekkubo erigenda e Lukisi, 
\q2 nga bwe bakungubaga 
\q1 ku luguudo olugenda e Kolonayimu, 
\q2 emiranga egy’okuzikirizibwa giwulirwa. 
\q1  
\v 6 Mudduke! Muwonye obulamu bwammwe; 
\q2 mubeere ng’ebisaka mu ddungu. 
\q1  
\v 7 Kubanga mwesiga ebikolwa byammwe n’obugagga bwammwe, 
\q2 nammwe mulitwalibwa ng’abaddu, 
\q1 ne Kemosi alitwalibwa mu buwaŋŋanguse 
\q2 awamu ne bakabona be n’abakungu be. 
\q1  
\v 8 Omuzikiriza alirumba buli kibuga, 
\q2 era tewali kibuga kiriwona. 
\q1 Ekiwonvu kiryonoonebwa 
\q2 n’olusenyu luzikirizibwe 
\q2 kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* ayogedde. 
\q1  
\v 9 Muwe Mowaabu ebiwaawaatiro abuuke agende 
\q2 kubanga alifuuka matongo, 
\q1 ebibuga bye birizikirizibwa, 
\q2 nga tewali abibeeramu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 “Akolimirwe oyo agayaalira omulimu gwa \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q2 Akolimirwe oyo aziyiza ekitala kye okuyiwa omusaayi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 “Mowaabu abadde mirembe okuva mu buvubuka bwe, 
\q2 nga wayini gwe batasengezze, 
\q1 gwe bataggye mu kibya ekimu okumuyiwa mu kirala, 
\q2 tagenzeko mu buwaŋŋanguse. 
\q1 Kale awooma ng’edda, 
\q2 n’akawoowo ke tekakyukanga. 
\q1  
\v 12 Naye ennaku zijja,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q1 “lwe ndituma basajja bange abaggya wayini mu bibya, 
\q2 era balimuyiwa ebweru; 
\q1 balittulula ensuwa ze 
\q2 baase n’ebibya bye. 
\q1  
\v 13 Awo Mowaabu alikwatibwa ensonyi olwa Kemosi, 
\q2 ng’ennyumba ya Isirayiri bwe yaswala 
\q2 bwe yeesiga Beseri. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 “Oyinza otya okugamba nti, ‘Tuli balwanyi, 
\q2 abasajja abazira mu ntalo?’ 
\q1  
\v 15 Mowaabu alizindibwa n’ebibuga bye ne bizikirizibwa; 
\q2 abavubuka be abato bagende battibwe,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera Kabaka, erinnya lye ye \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye. 
\q1  
\v 16 “Okugwa kwa Mowaabu kusembedde; 
\q2 akabi katuuse. 
\q1  
\v 17 Mumubeesebeese mwenna abamwetoolodde, 
\q2 mwenna abamanyi ettutumu lye; 
\q1 mugambe nti, ‘Ng’Omuggo ogw’amaanyi ogw’obwakabaka gumenyese, 
\q2 ng’oluga olw’ekitiibwa lumenyese!’  
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 “Mukke muve mu kitiibwa kyammwe 
\q2 mutuule ku ttaka, 
\q2 mmwe abatuuze b’Omuwala w’e Diboni, 
\q1 kubanga oyo azikiriza Mowaabu 
\q2 alibajjira azikirize ebibuga byammwe ebya bbugwe. 
\q1  
\v 19 Muyimirire ku luguudo mulabe, 
\q2 mmwe ababeera mu Aloweri. 
\q1 Mubuuze omusajja adduka, n’omukazi atoloka, 
\q2 mubabuuze nti, ‘Kiki ekiguddewo?’ 
\q1  
\v 20 Mowaabu aswadde kubanga amenyesemenyese. 
\q2 Mukaabe muleekaane! 
\q1 Mulangiririre mu Alunoni 
\q2 nti Mowaabu kizikiridde. 
\q1  
\v 21 Okusala omusango kutuuse mu nsi ey’ensenyi 
\q2 ku Koloni ne ku Yaza ne ku Mefaasi, 
\q2  
\v 22 ne ku Diboni, ne ku Nebo ne ku Besudibulasayimu, 
\q2  
\v 23 ne ku Kiriyasayimu ne ku Besugamuli ne ku Besumyoni; 
\q2  
\v 24 ne ku Keriyoosi ne ku Bozula 
\q2 ne ku bibuga byonna eby’omu nsi ya Mowaabu ebiri ewala n’ebiri okumpi. 
\q1  
\v 25 Ejjembe lya Mowaabu lisaliddwako, 
\q2 n’omukono gwe gumenyese,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 26 “Mumutamiize; 
\q2 kubanga ajeemedde \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 Ka Mowaabu yekulukuunyize mu bisesemye bye, 
\q2 era asekererwe. 
\q1  
\v 27 Isirayiri tewagisekereranga? 
\q2 Baali bamukutte mu bubbi, 
\q1 olyoke onyeenye omutwe gwo ng’omusekerera 
\q2 buli lw’omwogerako? 
\q1  
\v 28 Muve mu bibuga byammwe mubeere mu njazi, 
\q2 mmwe ababeera mu Mowaabu. 
\q1 Mubeere ng’ejjiba erikola ekisu kyalyo 
\q2 ku mumwa gw’empuku. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 29 “Tuwulidde amalala ga Mowaabu 
\q2 amalala ge agayitiridde n’okwemanya, 
\q1 okwewulira kwe era n’okweyisa kwe 
\q2 era n’okwegulumiza kwe okw’omutima. 
\q1  
\v 30 Mmanyi obusungu bwe obutaliimu,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q2 “okwenyumiriza kwe okutaliiko kye kugasa. 
\q1  
\v 31 Noolwekyo nkaabirira Mowaabu, 
\q2 olwa Mowaabu yenna nkaaba, 
\q2 nkungubagira abasajja ab’e Kirukeresi. 
\q1  
\v 32 Nkukaabira ggwe amaziga, nga Yazeri bw’akaaba, 
\q2 ggwe omuzabbibu gw’e Sibuna. 
\q1 Amatabi gammwe geegolola okutuuka ku nnyanja; 
\q2 gatuuka ku nnyanja y’e Yazeri. 
\q1 Omuzikiriza agudde ku bibala byo 
\q2 ebyengedde era n’emizabbibu. 
\q1  
\v 33 Essanyu n’okujaguza biggiddwa ku nnimiro 
\q2 ne ku bibanja bya Mowaabu. 
\q1 Nziyizza okukulukuta kwa wayini mu masogolero; 
\q2 tewali asogola ng’aleekaana olw’essanyu. 
\q1 Newaakubadde nga waliyo okuleekaana, 
\q2 okuleekaana okwo si kwa ssanyu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 34 “Amaloboozi g’okukaaba kwabwe galinnye 
\q2 okuva e Kesuboni okutuuka ku Ereyale, n’okutuuka ku Yakazi. 
\q1 Okuva e Zowaali okutuuka e Kolanayimu n’e Egulasuserisiya, 
\q2 kubanga n’amazzi g’e Nimulimu gakalidde. 
\q1  
\v 35 Ndiggyawo 
\q2 abo abawaayo ebiweebwayo mu bifo ebigulumivu e Mowaabu, 
\q2 ne bootereza n’obubaane eri bakatonda baabwe,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 36 “Noolwekyo omutima gwange gukaabira Mowaabu ng’endere; 
\q2 gukaaba ng’endere olw’abasajja b’e Kirukesi. 
\q2 Obugagga bwe baafuna buweddewo. 
\q1  
\v 37 Buli mutwe mumwe 
\q2 na buli kirevu kisaliddwako; 
\q1 buli mukono gutemeddwako 
\q2 na buli kiwato kisibiddwamu ebibukutu. 
\q1  
\v 38 Ku buli kasolya ka nnyumba e Mowaabu 
\q2 ne mu bifo awakuŋŋaanirwa, 
\q1 tewaliwo kintu kirala wabula okukungubaga, 
\q2 kubanga njasizzayasizza Mowaabu 
\q2 ng’ekibya ekitaliiko akyagala,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 39 “Ng’amenyeddwamenyeddwa! Nga bakaaba! 
\q2 Mowaabu ng’akyusa omugongo gwe olw’obuswavu! 
\q1 Mowaabu afuuse kyakusekererwa, 
\q2 ekyekango eri bonna abamwetoolodde.” 
\q1  
\v 40 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti: 
\q1 “Laba! Empungu ekka, 
\q2 ng’eyanjuluza ebiwaawaatiro byayo ku Mowaabu. 
\q1  
\v 41 Ebibuga birikwatibwa 
\q2 n’ebigo biwambibwe. 
\q1 Ku lunaku olwo emitima gy’abalwanyi ba Mowaabu 
\q2 giribeera ng’omutima gw’omukazi alumwa okuzaala. 
\q1  
\v 42 Mowaabu alizikirizibwa, 
\q2 kubanga yajeemera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 43 Entiisa n’obunnya n’omutego bibalindiridde, 
\q2 mmwe abantu ba Mowaabu,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 44 “Buli alidduka entiisa 
\q2 aligwa mu bunnya, 
\q1 n’oyo aliba avudde mu bunnya 
\q2 alikwatibwa omutego; 
\q1 kubanga ndireeta ku Mowaabu 
\q2 omwaka gw’okubonaabona kwe,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 45 “Mu kisiikirize kya Kesuboni, 
\q2 abadduka mwe bayimirira nga tebalina maanyi, 
\q1 kubanga omuliro guvudde mu Kesuboni, 
\q2 ennimi z’omuliro wakati mu Sikoni, 
\q1 era gw’okezza ebyenyi bya Mowaabu, 
\q2 n’obuwanga bw’abo abaleekaana nga beewaanawaana. 
\q1  
\v 46 Zikusanze ggwe, Mowaabu. 
\q2 Abantu b’e Kemosi bazikiridde, 
\q1 batabani bo batwaliddwa mu buwaŋŋanguse 
\q2 ne bawala bammwe mu busibe. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 47 “Ndikomyawo nate obugagga bwa Mowaabu 
\q2 mu nnaku ezijja,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\p Omusango Mowaabu gw’asaliddwa gukoma wano. 
\c 49  
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Amoni 
\p  
\v 1 Ebikwata ku baana ba Amoni bye bino. 
\p Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, 
\q1 “Isirayiri terina baana balenzi? 
\q2 Terina basika? 
\q1 Lwaki Malukamu atutte Gaadi? 
\q2 Lwaki abantu be batutte ebibuga by’e Gaadi? 
\q1  
\v 2 Naye ennaku zijja,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q1 “lwe ndiraya eŋŋoma ezirangirira olutalo 
\q2 ku Labba eky’abawala ba Amoni. 
\q1 Kirifuuka ntuumu ya mafunfugu, 
\q2 n’ebyalo ebiriraanyeewo byokebwe omuliro. 
\q1 Isirayiri eryoke egobere ebweru 
\q2 abo abagigoba,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 3 “Kaaba, ggwe Kesuboni, kubanga Ayi kizikiridde! 
\q2 Mukaabe mmwe abatuuze b’omu Labba! 
\q1 Mwesibe ebibukutu mukungubage. 
\q2 Mudduke mudde eno n’eri mu bisenge by’ekibuga, 
\q1 kubanga Malukamu alitwalibwa mu busibe, 
\q2 awamu ne bakabona n’abakungu. 
\q1  
\v 4 Lwaki mwenyumiriza olw’ebiwonvu byammwe, 
\q2 ne mwenyumiriza olw’ebiwonvu ebigimu? 
\q1 Ggwe omuwala atali mwesigwa, 
\q2 weesiga obugagga bwo n’ogamba nti, 
\q2 ‘Ani alinnumba?’ 
\q1  
\v 5 Ndikuleetako entiisa, 
\q2 okuva mu abo bonna abakwetoolodde,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera Mukama, \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye. 
\q1 “Buli omu ku mmwe aligobebwa, 
\q2 era tewali n’omu alikuŋŋaanya abadduka. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 “Naye oluvannyuma ndikomyawo nate omukisa gy’abaana ba Amoni,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Edomu 
\p  
\v 7 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Tewakyali magezi mu Temani? 
\q2 Abeegendereza babuliddwa okutegeera? 
\q2 Amagezi gaabwe gaweddemu ensa? 
\q1  
\v 8 Mukyuke mudduke mwekweke mu mpuku eziri ewala 
\q2 mmwe abatuuze b’e Dedani, 
\q1 kubanga ndireeta ekikangabwa ku Esawu, 
\q2 mu kiseera bwe ndimubonerereza. 
\q1  
\v 9 Abanozi b’emizabbibu singa bazze gy’oli, 
\q2 tebandikuleseeko mizabbibu mibale bubazi? 
\q1 Singa ababbi bazze ekiro, 
\q2 tebandibbye byonna bye beetaaga? 
\q1  
\v 10 Naye ndyambula Esawu mwerule; 
\q2 ndizuula ebifo bye mwe yeekweka, 
\q2 aleme kwekweka. 
\q1 Abaana be, n’ab’eŋŋanda ze n’ab’omuliraano baakuzikirira, 
\q2 era wa kuggwaawo. 
\q1  
\v 11 Bamulekwa mu mmwe mubaleke, ndibalabirira. 
\q2 Ne bannamwandu mu mmwe banneesige.” 
\p  
\v 12 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, “Obanga abo abatandinywedde ku kikompe bawaliriziddwa okukinywako, lwaki mmwe temubonerezebwa? Temuuleme kubonerezebwa, mulina okukinywa.  
\v 13 Neerayirira,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, “Bozula alifuuka matongo era ekibuga ekijjudde entiisa, ekinyoomebwa era ekikolimire, era ebibuga bye byonna biriba matongo emirembe gyonna.” 
\q1  
\v 14 Mpulidde obubaka okuva eri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q2 Omubaka yatumibwa eri amawanga okugamba nti, 
\q1 “Mwekuŋŋaanye mukirumbe! 
\q2 Mugolokoke mukole olutalo!” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 “Kaakano ndibafuula aba wansi ennyo mu mawanga, 
\q2 abanyoomebwa mu bantu. 
\q1  
\v 16 Entiisa gy’oleeta 
\q2 n’amalala g’omutima gwo bikulimbye, 
\q1 mmwe ababeera mu bunnya bw’amayinja, 
\q2 mmwe ababeera waggulu mu nsozi. 
\q1 Wadde nga muzimba ebisu byammwe okubeera waggulu nga eby’empungu, 
\q2 ndibawanulayo ne mbasuula wansi,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 17 “Edomu kirifuuka kyerolerwa, 
\q2 abo bonna abayitawo balyewuunya batye 
\q2 olw’ebiwundu bye byonna. 
\q1  
\v 18 Nga Sodomu ne Ggomola bwe byayonoonebwa, 
\q2 wamu n’ebibuga ebirala ebiriraanyeewo,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q1 “tewaliba n’omu abibeeramu; 
\q2 tewali musajja alikituulamu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 “Ng’empologoma eva mu bisaka by’omu Yoludaani 
\q2 okugenda mu muddo omugimu, 
\q1 ndigoba Edomu mu nsi ye amangu n’embiro. 
\q2 Ani oyo omulonde gwe nnaateekawo akole kino? 
\q1 Ani ali nga nze era ani ayinza okunsomooza? 
\q2 Era musumba wa ndiga ki ayinza okunjolekera?” 
\q1  
\v 20 Noolwekyo, muwulire \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda kyategese okuleeta ku Edomu, 
\q2 kyategekedde abo abatuula mu Temani. 
\q1 Endiga ento mu bisibo za kuwalulwa, 
\q2 alyonoonera ddala ebisibo byazo ku lwabwe. 
\q1  
\v 21 Bwe baligwa ensi erikankana, 
\q2 emiranga gyabwe giriwulirwa mu Nnyanja Emyufu. 
\q1  
\v 22 Laba, alibuuka mu bire ng’empungu n’atumbiira, 
\q2 n’alyoka akka ng’ayanjululiza ebiwaawaatiro bye ku Bozula. 
\q1 Ku lunaku olwo emitima gy’abalwanyi ba Edomu 
\q2 giribeewanika ng’ogw’omukazi alumwa okuzaala. 
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Damasiko 
\p  
\v 23 Ebikwata ku Damasiko: 
\q1 “Kamasi ne Alupaadi biweddemu amaanyi, 
\q2 kubanga biwulidde amawulire amabi. 
\q1 Bakeŋŋentereddwa, 
\q2 batabuddwa ng’ennyanja esiikuuse, tebasobola kutereera. 
\q1  
\v 24 Ddamasiko ayongobedde, 
\q2 akyuse adduke 
\q2 era okutya kumukutte; 
\q1 obubalagaze n’obuyinike bimunyweezezza, 
\q2 obulumi nga obw’omukazi alumwa okuzaala. 
\q1  
\v 25 Lwaki ekibuga ekimanyiddwa tebakidduse, 
\q2 ekibuga mwe nsanyukira? 
\q1  
\v 26 Ddala abavubuka baakyo baligwa mu nguudo, 
\q2 n’abalwanyi baakyo bonna ku olwo baakusirisibwa,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye. 
\q1  
\v 27 “Ndiyokya bbugwe wa Ddamasiko omuliro; 
\q2 gwakumalawo n’embiri za Benukadaadi.” 
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Kedali ne Kazoli 
\p  
\v 28 Bino bye bikwata ku Kedali n’obwakabaka bwa Kazoli, obwalumbibwa Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni. 
\p Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda nti, 
\q1 “Golokoka, olumbe Kedali 
\q2 ozikirize abantu be bugwanjuba. 
\q1  
\v 29 Weema zaabwe n’ebisibo byabwe bya kutwalibwa; 
\q2 enju zaabwe ziryetikkibwa 
\q2 n’ebintu byabwe byonna n’eŋŋamira zaabwe. 
\q1 Abasajja balibakanga nga bawowoggana nti, 
\q2 ‘Akabi kavudde ku buli ludda!’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 30 “Mudduke mwekukume mangu! 
\q2 Mubeere mu mpuku empanvu, mmwe abatuuze b’omu Kazoli,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1 “Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni abasalidde olukwe; 
\q2 ategese okubalumba. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 31 “Golokoka olumbe eggwanga eriri mu ggandaalo, 
\q2 eriri mu kweyagala,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q1 “eggwanga eritalina miryango gisibwa wadde ebyuma; 
\q2 abantu baalyo babeera awo bokka. 
\q1  
\v 32 Eŋŋamira zaabwe zaakunyagibwa, 
\q2 n’amagana gaabwe amanene gatwalibwe. 
\q1 Ndibasaasaanya eri empewo, abo abali mu bifo eby’ewala, 
\q2 mbaleeteko akabi okuva ku buli ludda,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 33 “Kazoli alifuuka kifo kya bibe, 
\q2 ekifo eky’amatongo eky’emirembe n’emirembe. 
\q1 Tewali alikibeeramu; 
\q2 tewali muntu alikituulamu.” 
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Eramu 
\p  
\v 34 Kino kye kigambo kya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ekyajjira nnabbi Yeremiya ekikwata ku Eramu, nga Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda kyajje alye obwakabaka. 
\b  
\p  
\v 35 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Laba, ndimenya omutego gwa Eramu, 
\q2 amaanyi gaabwe mwe gasinga okwesigibwa. 
\q1  
\v 36 Era ndireeta ku Eramu empewo ennya, 
\q2 okuva mu bitundu ebina eby’eggulu; 
\q1 ndibasaasaanyiza eri empewo ezo ennya, 
\q2 era tewaliba nsi n’emu 
\q2 abawaŋŋanguse ba Eramu gye bataliddukiramu. 
\q1  
\v 37 Ndimenyeramenyera Eramu mu maaso g’abalabe be, 
\q2 mu maaso gaabo abamunoonya okumutta; 
\q1 ndibatuusaako ekikangabwa, 
\q2 n’obusungu bwange obungi ennyo,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1 “Ndibawondera n’ekitala 
\q2 okutuusa lwe ndibamalirawo ddala. 
\q1  
\v 38 Nditeeka entebe yange ey’obwakabaka mu Eramu 
\q2 era nzikirize kabaka we n’abakungu be,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 39 “Wabula ekiseera kijja, 
\q2 lwe ndiddiramu Eramu,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\c 50  
\s1 Obubaka Obukwata ku Babulooni 
\p  
\v 1 Kino kye kigambo \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda kye yayogerera mu nnabbi Yeremiya ekikwata ku Babulooni n’ensi ey’Abakaludaaya. 
\q1  
\v 2 “Buulira mu mawanga era olangirire, 
\q2 yimusa bendera olangirire, 
\q2 tolekaayo kintu kyonna ogambe nti, 
\q1 ‘Babulooni eriwambibwa; 
\q2 Beri kiswale, 
\q2 ne Meroddaaki kijjule entiisa. 
\q1 Ebifaananyi bya bakatonda abakole n’emikono bijja kuswala 
\q2 era bitye.’ 
\q1  
\v 3 Eggwanga okuva mu bukiikakkono lijja kukirumba 
\q2 lyonoone ensi y’Abakaludaaya. 
\q1 Tewali muntu alisigalamu; 
\q2 abantu bonna balikiddukamu era n’ensolo zonna. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 “Mu nnaku ezo, era mu kiseera ekyo,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q1 “abantu ba Isirayiri awamu n’abantu ba Yuda 
\q2 balikaaba amaziga nga banoonya \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waabwe. 
\q1  
\v 5 Balibuuza ekkubo eridda e Sayuuni 
\q2 era bakyuse obwenyi bwabwe okukitunuulira, nga boogera nti, 
\q1 Mujje twesibe ku \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda 
\q2 mu ndagaano ey’emirembe gyonna 
\q2 etegenda kwerabirwa. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 “Abantu bange babadde ndiga ezibuze; 
\q2 abasumba baabwe babawabizza 
\q2 ne babatuusa ku kutaataaganira ku nsozi. 
\q1 Baava ku lusozi ne badda ku kasozi 
\q2 ne beerabira ekifo kyabwe eky’okuwummuliramu. 
\q1  
\v 7 Buli eyabasanganga nga abatulugunya; 
\q2 abalabe baabwe ne bagamba nti, ‘Tetulina musango gwe tuzza, 
\q1 kubanga baajeemera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, obuddukiro bwabwe obwa nnama ddala, 
\q2 ye \nd Mukama\nd*, essuubi lya bakitaabwe.’  
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 “Mudduke okuva e Babulooni; 
\q2 muleke ensi y’Abakaludaaya, 
\q2 mubeere ng’embuzi ezikulembera ekisibo. 
\q1  
\v 9 Kubanga, laba, ndigolokosa ekibiina ky’amawanga amanene 
\q2 okuva mu nsi ey’obukiikakkono okulumba Babulooni. 
\q1 Baliyimirira mu nnyiriri zaabwe bakirumbe, 
\q2 bakiwambe nga basinzira mu bukiikakkono. 
\q1 Obusaale bwabwe buliba ng’obw’abalwanyi abakugu, 
\q2 abataddira awo ngalo nsa. 
\q1  
\v 10 Noolwekyo ensi y’Abakaludaaya erinyagibwa; 
\q2 abo bonna abaliginyaga balitwala byonna bye baagala,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 “Kubanga musanyuka ne mujaguza, 
\q2 mmwe abaanyaga omugabo gwabwe, 
\q1 kubanga muligita ng’ente enduusi ewuula emmere ey’empeke, 
\q2 ne muleekaana ng’embalaasi ennume enkulu, 
\q1  
\v 12 nnyammwe alikwatibwa ensonyi; 
\q2 oyo eyakuzaala aliswazibwa. 
\q1 Aliba ensi esemberayo ddala, 
\q2 ensiko, ensi enkalu, eddungu. 
\q1  
\v 13 Olw’obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda tajja kubeeramu bantu, 
\q2 naye alisigala matongo. 
\q1 Bonna abayita e Babulooni balyewuunya batye era bakisooze 
\q2 olw’ebiwundu bye byonna. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 14 “Musimbe ennyiriri okwetooloola Babulooni, 
\q2 mwenna abanaanuula omutego. 
\q1 Mumulase! Temulekaawo kasaale n’akamu, 
\q2 kubanga yajeemera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 15 Mumukube olube ku buli ludda. 
\q2 Ajeemulukuse, eminaala gye gigwa, 
\q2 n’ebisenge bye bimenyeddwa. 
\q1 Kubanga kuno kwe kwesasuza kwa \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, 
\q2 mumwesasuzeeko; 
\q2 mumukole nga bw’akoze abalala. 
\q1  
\v 16 Asiga mumuggye mu Babulooni, 
\q2 n’omukunguzi oyo akwata ekiwabyo mumuggye mu makungula. 
\q1 Olw’ekitala ky’omujoozi, 
\q2 leka buli omu addukire mu nsi y’ewaabwe, 
\q2 buli muntu adde eri abantu be. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 “Isirayiri kisibo kya ndiga ezisaasaanye, 
\q2 empologoma kye zigobye. 
\q1 Eyasooka okumulya 
\q2 yali kabaka wa Bwasuli; 
\q1 eyasembayo okumenya amagumba ge 
\q2 yali Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni.” 
\p  
\v 18 Noolwekyo bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, 
\q1 “Ndibonereza kabaka w’e Babulooni n’ensi ye 
\q2 nga bwe nabonereza kabaka w’e Bwasuli. 
\q1  
\v 19 Naye ndikomyawo Isirayiri mu kisibo kye 
\q2 era aliriira ku Kalumeeri ne Basani; 
\q1 alikuttira 
\q2 ku busozi bwa Efulayimu, ne mu Gireyaadi. 
\q1  
\v 20 Mu nnaku ezo, era mu biseera ebyo,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda, “omusango ku Isirayiri gulinoonyezebwa, naye tegulibaawo, era n’ebibi bya Yuda birinoonyezebwa, naye tewaliba na kimu, kubanga ndisonyiwa abo bendeseewo. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 21 “Mulumbe ensi ye Merasayimu 
\q2 n’abo abali mu Pekodi. 
\q1 Mubagoberere mubatte, mubazikiririze ddala,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q2 “Mukole byonna bye mbalagidde. 
\q1  
\v 22 Oluyoogaano lw’olutalo luwulirwa mu ggwanga, 
\q2 eddoboozi ery’okuzikiriza okunene! 
\q1  
\v 23 Ennyondo y’ensi yonna 
\q2 ng’ekubiddwa n’emenyeka! 
\q1 Babulooni kifuuse matongo 
\q2 mu mawanga! 
\q1  
\v 24 Nakutegera omutego, ggwe Babulooni, 
\q2 babagwiikiriza ne babakwata nga tebategedde, 
\q1 baakukwata ne bakuwamba 
\q2 kubanga wawakanya \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 25 \nd Mukama\nd* agguddewo etterekero ly’ebyokulwanyisa bye 
\q2 naggyamu ebyokulwanyisa eby’ekiruyi kye, 
\q1 kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye alina omulimu ogw’okukola 
\q2 mu nsi y’Abakaludaaya. 
\q1  
\v 26 Mujje mumulumbe mmwe abava mu buli nsonda, 
\q2 mumenye ebyagi eby’emmere y’empeke, 
\q2 mumukuŋŋaanye abe ng’entuumo y’emmere y’empeke. 
\q1 Mumuzikiririze ddala; 
\q2 waleme kusigalawo n’omu ku bo. 
\q1  
\v 27 Mutte ennume zaabwe zonna, 
\q2 muzitwale zittibwe. 
\q1 Zibasanze kubanga olunaku lwabwe lutuuse, 
\q2 kye kiseera kyabwe eky’okubonerezebwa. 
\q1  
\v 28 Muwulire eby’abadduka n’abanoonyi b’obubudamu okuva mu Babulooni 
\q2 nga balangirira mu Sayuuni 
\q1 engeri \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe gye yeesasuzza, 
\q2 gye yeesasuzza olwa yeekaalu ye. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 29 “Koowoola abalasi b’obusaale balumbe Babulooni, 
\q2 ne bonna abanaanuula omutego. 
\q1 Mumwetooloole yenna; 
\q2 tewaba n’omu awona. 
\q1 Mumusasule olw’ebikolwa bye byonna; 
\q2 mumukole nga bwe yakola banne. 
\q1 Kubanga yanyooma \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 Omutukuvu wa Isirayiri. 
\q1  
\v 30 Noolwekyo, abavubuka be baligwa mu nguudo; 
\q2 abaserikale be balisirisibwa ku lunaku olwo,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda. 
\q1  
\v 31 “Laba, ndi mulabe wo, ggwe ow’amalala,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera Mukama, \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, 
\q1 “Kubanga olunaku lwo lutuuse, 
\q2 ekiseera ky’on’obonerezebwamu. 
\q1  
\v 32 Oyo ow’amalala alyesittala agwe 
\q2 era teri n’omu alimuyamba kuyimuka; 
\q1 Ndikoleeza omuliro mu bibuga bye 
\q2 oguliyokya bonna abamwetoolodde.” 
\p  
\v 33 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Abantu ba Isirayiri banyigirizibwa 
\q2 awamu n’abantu ba Yuda; 
\q1 Bonna ababawambye babanywezezza, 
\q2 bagaanye okubata. 
\q1  
\v 34 Omununuzi waabwe w’amaanyi, 
\q2 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye lye linnya lye. 
\q1 Alirwanirira ensonga zaabwe awatali kubuusabuusa, 
\q2 alyoke aleete emirembe mu nsi yaabwe; 
\q2 wabula alireeta okutabukatabuka mu bantu ba Babulooni. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 35 “Ekitala kyolekedde Abakaludaaya,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q1 “n’eri abo ababeera mu Babulooni, 
\q2 n’abakungu baabwe n’abasajja baabwe abajjudde amagezi! 
\q1  
\v 36 Ekitala kyolekedde bannabbi baabwe ab’obulimba! 
\q2 Balifuuka balisiriwala, 
\q1 ekitala kyolekedde abalwanyi baabwe. 
\q2 Balijjula entiisa. 
\q1  
\v 37 Ekitala kyolekedde embalaasi ze n’amagaali 
\q2 n’abagwira bonna abamubeeramu! 
\q2 Balifuuka banafu ng’abakazi. 
\q1 Ekitala kyolekedde eby’obugagga bwe! 
\q2 Birinyagibwa! 
\q1  
\v 38 Ekyeya kyolekedde amazzi gaamu! 
\q2 Galikalira. 
\q1 Kubanga ggwanga erisinza ebifaananyi, 
\q2 ebifaananyi ebirigwa eddalu olw’entiisa. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 39 “Noolwekyo ensolo z’omu nsiko ziribeera eyo n’empisi, 
\q2 era eyo ekiwuugulu nakyo gye kiribeera. 
\q1 Ekibuga ekyo tekiriddamu kubeeramu bantu 
\q2 wadde kutuulwamu bantu emirembe gyonna. 
\q1  
\v 40 Katonda nga bwe yazikiriza Sodomu ne Ggomola 
\q2 n’ebibuga ebiriraanyeewo,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q1 “bw’atyo bw’alikikola ne mutaba muntu n’omu alikibeeramu; 
\q2 tewaliba n’omu alikisigalamu. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 41 “Laba, eggye liva mu bukiikakkono; 
\q2 ensi ey’amaanyi ne bakabaka bangi, 
\q2 bakuŋŋaana okuva ku nkomerero y’ensi. 
\q1  
\v 42 Balina obusaale n’amafumu, 
\q2 bakambwe si ba kisa. 
\q1 Beebagadde embalaasi zaabwe 
\q2 ne baba ng’amayengo agawuluguma mu nnyanja; 
\q1 bali ng’abasajja abalwanyi abajjira mu nnyiriri z’entalo 
\q2 okukulumba, ggwe Muwala wa Babulooni. 
\q1  
\v 43 Kabaka w’e Babulooni afunye amawulire agabafaako, 
\q2 n’emikono gye girebedde. 
\q1 Entiisa emugwiridde, 
\q2 ng’omukazi alumwa okuzaala. 
\q1  
\v 44 Ng’empologoma eva mu kibira kya Yoludaani 
\q2 okugenda mu ddundiro eggimu, 
\q1 Babulooni ndimugoba mu nsi ye awatali kutemya kikowe. 
\q2 Ani oyo omulonde gwe nnaawa okukola kino? 
\q1 Ani ali nga nze, era ani ayinza okunsomooza? 
\q2 Era musumba ki ayinza okuyimirirawo okumpakanya?” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 45 Noolwekyo, wulira \nd Mukama\nd* ky’ategekedde Babulooni, 
\q2 ky’ategese okuleeta ku nsi y’Abakaludaaya. 
\q1 Obwana bw’ebisibo byabwe bulitwalibwa, 
\q2 alizikiririza ddala ebisibo byabwe ng’abalanga obujeemu bwabwe. 
\q1  
\v 46 Olw’oluyoogaano lw’okuwambibwa kwa Babulooni, ensi erikankana; 
\q2 okukaaba kwe kuliwulirwa mu mawanga. 
\c 51  
\s1 Ekibonerezo kya Babulooni 
\p  
\v 1 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* nti, 
\q1 “Laba, ndiyimusa omwoyo gw’omuzikiriza 
\q2 alumbe Babulooni n’abantu ba Lebukamaayi. 
\q1  
\v 2 Ndituma abagwira e Babulooni 
\q2 bamuwewe era bazikirize ensi ye; 
\q1 balimulumba ku buli luuyi 
\q2 ku lunaku olw’okuzikirira kwe. 
\q1  
\v 3 Omulasi talikuba busaale bwe, 
\q2 taliyambala wadde ebyambalo bye ebyokulwanyisa. 
\q1 Temusonyiwa batabani be; 
\q2 muzikiririze ddala amaggye ge. 
\q1  
\v 4 Baligwa nga battiddwa e Babulooni, 
\q2 nga batuusiddwako ebiwundu eby’amaanyi mu nguudo ze. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kubanga Yuda ne Isirayiri tebinnalekebwa 
\q2 Katonda waabwe, oyo \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye, 
\q1 wadde ng’ensi yaabwe esingiddwa omusango 
\q2 mu maaso g’Omutukuvu wa Isirayiri. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 “Mudduke Babulooni. 
\q2 Mudduke okuwonya obulamu bwammwe. 
\q2 Temusaanawo olw’ebibi bye. 
\q1 Kiseera kya \nd Mukama\nd* okwesasuza; 
\q2 alimusasula ekyo ekimusaanira. 
\q1  
\v 7 Babulooni yali kikompe kya zaabu mu mukono gwa \nd Mukama\nd*; 
\q2 yatamiiza ensi yonna. 
\q1 Amawanga gaanywa wayini we, 
\q2 kyegavudde galaluka. 
\q1  
\v 8 Babulooni kirigwa mangu ago ne kimenyekamenyeka. 
\q2 Mukikungubagire. 
\q1 Munoonye eddagala olw’obulumi bw’akyo 
\q2 oboolyawo anaawonyezebwa. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 “ ‘Twandiwonyezza Babulooni, 
\q2 naye tayinza kuwonyezeka. 
\q1 Leka tumuleke buli muntu adde mu nsi ye, 
\q2 kubanga omusango gwe gutuuse mu bwengula, 
\q2 gusituse gulinnye okutuuka ku bire.’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 “ ‘\nd Mukama\nd* atulwaniridde, 
\q2 mujje tukitegeeze mu Sayuuni 
\q2 ekyo \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda waffe ky’akoze.’  
\b  
\q1  
\v 11 “Muwagale obusaale, 
\q2 mukwate engabo! 
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* ayungudde bakabaka ab’e Bumeedi, 
\q2 kubanga ekigendererwa kye kuzikiriza Babulooni. 
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* aliwalana eggwanga, 
\q2 aliwalana eggwanga olwa yeekaalu ye. 
\q1  
\v 12 Muyimuse bendera mwolekere bbugwe wa Babulooni! 
\q2 Mwongereko abakuumi, 
\q1 muteekeko abaserikale, 
\q2 mutegeke okulumba mbagirawo! 
\q1 \nd Mukama\nd* alituukiriza ekigendererwa bye, 
\q2 ensala ye okwolekera abantu ba Babulooni. 
\q1  
\v 13 Gwe abeera okumpi n’amazzi amangi, 
\q2 omugagga mu bintu eby’omuwendo, 
\q1 enkomerero yo etuuse, 
\q2 ekiseera kyo eky’okuzikirizibwa kituuse. 
\q1  
\v 14 \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye yeerayiridde ku lulwe; 
\q2 ddala ndikujjuza abasajja, ng’ebibinja by’enzige, 
\q2 era balireekaana nga bakuwangudde. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 “Ensi yagikola n’amaanyi ge; 
\q2 yagiteekawo n’amagezi ge, 
\q2 n’ayanjuluza eggulu n’okutegeera kwe. 
\q1  
\v 16 Bw’abwatuka, amazzi ag’omu ggulu gawuluguma; 
\q2 ayimusa ebire okuva ku nkomerero y’ensi. 
\q1 Amyansisa eggulu mu nkuba 
\q2 era n’aggya empewo mu mawanika ge. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 “Buli muntu talina magezi wadde okutegeera; 
\q2 Buli muweesi aswadde olw’ebifaananyi bya bakatonda by’akoze n’emikono gye. 
\q1 Ebifaananyi bye bya bulimba; 
\q2 tebirina mukka. 
\q1  
\v 18 Tebiriiko kye bigasa, ebisaanye okunyoomebwa 
\q2 ebirizikirizibwa nga \nd Mukama\nd* azze okusala omusango. 
\q1  
\v 19 Oyo omugabo gwa Yakobo tali nga bano, 
\q2 kubanga yakola ebintu byonna, 
\q1 nga mwotwalidde n’eggwanga ly’omugabo gwe, 
\q2 n’erinnya lye ye \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 “Muli mbazzi yange, 
\q2 ekyokulwanyisa kyange eky’olutalo, 
\q1 mmwe be nkozesa okubetenta amawanga, 
\q2 mmwe be nkozesa okuzikiriza obwakabaka, 
\q1  
\v 21 era ggwe gwe ndikozesa okubetenta embalaasi n’omwebagazi, 
\q2 ggwe gwe ndikozesa okubetenta ekigaali n’omuvuzi waakyo, 
\q1  
\v 22 era ggwe gwe ndikozesa okubetenta omusajja n’omukazi, 
\q2 era ggwe ndikozesa okubetenta omukadde n’omuvubuka, 
\q2 era ggwe gwe ndikozesa okubetenta omuvubuka n’omuwala omuto. 
\q1  
\v 23 Ggwe gwe ndikozesa okubetenta omusumba n’ekisibo kye, 
\q2 ggwe gwe ndikozesa okubetenta omulimi n’ente ennume, 
\q2 ggwe gwe ndikozesa okubetenta bagavana n’abakungu. 
\p  
\v 24 “Ndisasula Babulooni ne bonna ababeeramu nga mulaba olw’ebibi byonna bye baakola mu Sayuuni,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 25 “Mbalinako ensonga, ggwe olusozi oluzikiriza, 
\q2 mmwe abazikiriza ensi yonna,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1 “Ndikugolererako omukono gwange, 
\q2 nkusuule ku mayinja g’ensozi, 
\q2 nkufuule olusozi olutakyayaka. 
\q1  
\v 26 Tewali jjinja lirikuggibwako kukola jjinja lya ku nsonda, 
\q2 wadde ejjinja lyonna okukola omusingi, 
\q2 kubanga olibeera matongo emirembe gyonna,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 27 “Yimusa bendera mu ggwanga! 
\q2 Fuuwa omulere mu mawanga! 
\q1 Tegeka amawanga okumulwanyisa; 
\q2 koowoola obwakabaka buno bumulumbe: 
\q2 obwa Alalati ne Mini ne Asukenaazi. 
\q1 Londa omuduumizi amulumba, 
\q2 weereza embalaasi eziri ng’ekibinja ky’enzige. 
\q1  
\v 28 Teekateeka amawanga okumulwanyisa; 
\q2 bakabaka Abameedi, 
\q1 bagavana baabwe era n’abakungu baabwe bonna, 
\q2 n’amawanga ge bafuga. 
\q1  
\v 29 Ensi ekankana ne yeenyola olw’obulumi, 
\q2 kubanga ebigendererwa bya \nd Mukama\nd* eri Babulooni tebikyuka, 
\q1 okuzikiriza ensi ya Babulooni 
\q2 waleme kubaawo agibeeramu. 
\q1  
\v 30 Abalwanyi ba Babulooni balekedde awo okulwana; 
\q2 basigadde mu bigo byabwe. 
\q1 Baweddemu amaanyi; 
\q2 bafuuse nga bakazi. 
\q1 Ebifo bye mw’abeera byokeddwa omuliro; 
\q2 emitayimbwa gy’oku nzigi ze gimenyeddwa. 
\q1  
\v 31 Matalisi omu agoberera omulala, 
\q2 omubaka omu n’agoberera munne, 
\q1 okulangirira eri kabaka w’e Babulooni nti 
\q2 ekibuga kye kyonna kiwambiddwa, 
\q1  
\v 32 entindo z’emigga baziwambye, 
\q2 ensenyi ziyidde omuliro, 
\q2 n’abaserikale batidde.” 
\p  
\v 33 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* ow’Eggye, Katonda wa Isirayiri nti, 
\q1 “Muwala wa Babulooni ali ng’egguuliro, 
\q2 mu kiseera w’analinnyiririrwa; 
\q2 ebiseera eby’okumukungula binaatera okutuuka.” 
\q1  
\v 34 “Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni atukubyekubye, 
\q2 atutabudde, 
\q2 tufuuse ekikompe ekyereere. 
\q1 Atumize ng’omusota 
\q2 n’olubuto lwe n’alujjuza ebyassava byaffe ebiwooma, 
\q2 ffe n’atusesema. 
\q1  
\v 35 Leka okubonaabona okututuuseeko kubeere ku Babulooni,” 
\q2 bwe boogera abatuula mu Sayuuni. 
\q1 “Leka omusaayi gubeere ku abo ababeera mu Babulooni,” 
\q2 bwayogera Yerusaalemi. 
\p  
\v 36 \nd Mukama\nd* kyava ayogera nti, 
\q1 “Laba ndikulwanirira era ndikuwolerera eggwanga; 
\q1 Ndikaliza ennyanja ye 
\q2 n’ensulo ze. 
\q1  
\v 37 Babulooni kirifuuka bifunvu, 
\q2 mpuku ya bibe, 
\q1 ekintu ekyenyinyalwa n’okusekererwa, 
\q2 ekifo omutali abeeramu. 
\q1  
\v 38 Abantu baakyo bonna bawuluguma ng’empologoma ento, 
\q2 bavuumira wamu ng’abaana b’empologoma. 
\q1  
\v 39 Naye nga bakyabuguumirira, 
\q2 ndibategekera ekijjulo, 
\q2 mbatamiize 
\q1 balyoke balekaane nga baseka, 
\q2 olwo beebake emirembe gyonna nga tebazuukuse,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\q1  
\v 40 “Ndibaserengesa 
\q2 ng’abaana b’endiga, battibwe, 
\q2 ng’endiga n’embuzi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 41 “Sesaki nga kiriwambibwa, 
\q2 okujaguza kw’ensi yonna kugwewo. 
\q1 Babulooni kifuuse matongo eri amawanga! 
\q1  
\v 42 Ennyanja eribuutikira Babulooni; 
\q2 amayengo gaayo agawuluguma galigisaanikira. 
\q1  
\v 43 Ebibuga bye birisigala matongo, 
\q2 ensi enkalu ey’eddungu, 
\q1 ensi eteriimu muntu, 
\q2 eteyitamu muntu yenna. 
\q1  
\v 44 Ndibonereza Beri mu Babulooni, 
\q2 mmusesemye bye yali amize. 
\q1 Amawanga nga tegakyesomba kugenda gyali. 
\q2 Ne bbugwe wa Babulooni aligwa. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 45 “Mukiveemu, abantu bange! 
\q2 Mudduke muwonye obulamu bwammwe! 
\q2 Mudduke muwone obusungu bwa \nd Mukama\nd* obubuubuuka. 
\q1  
\v 46 Temutya wadde okuggwaamu amaanyi 
\q2 ng’eŋŋambo ziyitiŋŋana mu nsi; 
\q1 olugambo olumu lujja omwaka guno, olulala omwaka ogujja, 
\q2 eŋŋambo z’entalo mu ggwanga, 
\q2 era ez’omufuzi ng’alwana ne mufuzi munne. 
\q1  
\v 47 Kubanga ekiseera kijja 
\q2 lwe ndibonereza ebifaananyi bya bakatonda ba Babulooni abaakolebwa n’emikono; 
\q1 ensi eyo yonna eritabanguka, 
\q2 n’emirambo gy’abantu baayo abattiddwa gyonna gibeere omwo. 
\q1  
\v 48 Eggulu n’ensi ne byonna ebibirimu 
\q2 birireekana olw’essanyu olwa Babulooni, 
\q1 abalimuzikiriza balimulumba 
\q2 okuva mu bukiikakkono,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 49 “Babulooni kirigwa olw’Abayisirayiri abaafa, 
\q2 nga bonna abaafa mu nsi yonna 
\q2 bwe baweddewo olwa Babulooni. 
\q1  
\v 50 Mmwe abawonye ekitala, 
\q2 mwanguwe okugenda! 
\q1 Mujjukire \nd Mukama\nd* nga muli mu nsi ey’ewala, 
\q2 mulowooze ku Yerusaalemi.” 
\q1  
\v 51 “Tuweddemu amaanyi 
\q2 kubanga tuvumiddwa 
\q2 era tukwatiddwa ensonyi, 
\q1 kubanga abagwira bayingidde 
\q2 mu bifo ebitukuvu eby’ennyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd*.” 
\b  
\q1  
\v 52 “Naye ennaku zijja,” bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*, 
\q2 “lwe ndibonereza ebifaananyi bya bakatonda be, be yakola n’emikono, 
\q1 era mu nsi ye yonna, 
\q2 abaliko ebisago balisinda. 
\q1  
\v 53 Newaakubadde nga Babulooni atuuka ku bire 
\q2 era ne yeenyweza n’ebigo bye eby’amaanyi, 
\q2 ndimusindikira abazikiriza,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd*. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 54 “Eddoboozi ly’okukaaba liva mu Babulooni, 
\q2 eddoboozi ery’okuzikirira okunene 
\q2 okuva mu nsi y’Abakaludaaya. 
\q1  
\v 55 \nd Mukama\nd* alizikiriza Babulooni, 
\q2 alizikiza oluyoogaano lwakyo olunene. 
\q1 Amayengo g’abalabe galijja ng’amazzi amangi; 
\q2 okuwuluguma kw’amaloboozi kuliwulirwa. 
\q1  
\v 56 Omuzikiriza alirumba Babulooni; 
\q2 abalwanyi be baliwambibwa, 
\q2 n’emitego gyabwe girimenyebwa. 
\q1 Kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda asasula, 
\q2 alisasula mu bujjuvu. 
\q1  
\v 57 Nditamiiza abakungu be n’abasajja be abajjudde amagezi, 
\q2 ne bagavana, ab’ebitongole awamu n’abalwanyi; 
\q1 balyebaka emirembe gyonna era tebalizuukuka,” 
\q2 bw’ayogera Kabaka ayitibwa \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye. 
\p  
\v 58 Bw’ati bw’ayogera \nd Mukama\nd* Katonda ow’Eggye nti, 
\q1 “Bbugwe wa Babulooni omunene alisendebwa 
\q2 era n’emiryango gye emiwanvu gyokebwe; 
\q1 abantu beetawanyiza bwerere nga bafuba, 
\q2 okutawaana kw’eggwanga kuliba nku za muliro.” 
\p  
\v 59 Buno bwe bubaka Yeremiya bwe yawa omukungu Seraya mutabani wa Neriya, mutabani wa Maseya, bwe yagenda e Babulooni ne Zeddekiya kabaka wa Yuda, nga Zeddekiya afuga mu mwaka gwe ogwokuna. Seraya ye yali omu ku bakungu abakulu.  
\v 60 Yeremiya yali awandiise mu muzingo ebikangabwa byonna ebyali bigenda okutuuka ku Babulooni, byonna ebyali biwandiikiddwa ebyali bikwata ku Babulooni.  
\v 61 Yagamba Seraya nti, “Bw’otuuka mu Babulooni, laba ng’osoma mu ddoboozi ery’omwanguka ebigambo bino byonna.  
\v 62 Olwo ogambe nti, ‘Ayi \nd Mukama\nd*, ogambye nti olizikiriza ekifo kino, nti tewali nsolo oba muntu alikibeeramu; kibeere matongo emirembe gyonna.’  
\v 63 Bw’omalanga okusoma omuzingo guno gusibeeko ejjinja ogukanyuge mu mugga Fulaati.  
\v 64 Olyoke ogambe nti, ‘Bw’ati Babulooni bwalisaanawo aleme kubbulukuka olw’akabi ke ndimuleetako. N’abantu be balizikirira.’ ” 
\p Ebigambo bya Yeremiya bikoma awo. 
\c 52  
\s1 Okugwa kwa Yerusaalemi 
\p  
\v 1 Zeddekiya yali wa myaka amakumi abiri mu gumu egy’obukulu we yafuukira kabaka, n’afugira emyaka kkumi na gumu mu Yerusaalemi. Nnyina yayitibwanga Kamutali muwala wa Yeremiya ow’e Libuna.  
\v 2 Zeddekiya n’akola eby’omuzizo mu maaso ga \nd Mukama\nd*, nga Yekoyakimu bwe yali akoze.  
\v 3 Abalabe ba Yerusaalemi ne Yuda ne babalumba kubanga \nd Mukama\nd* yali abanyiigidde. Ku nkomerero n’abagobamu mu nsi. Ebyo byonna ne bituuka ku Yerusaalemi ne ku Yuda, \nd Mukama\nd* n’okubagoba n’abagoba mu maaso ge, ne Zeddekiya n’ajeemera kabaka w’e Babulooni. 
\p  
\v 4 Mu mwaka ogw’omwenda ogw’obufuzi bwa Zeddekiya, ku lunaku olw’ekkumi mu mwezi ogw’ekkumi, Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni n’eggye lye lyonna, n’alumba Yerusaalemi, ekibuga ekyo n’akizingiza n’akizimbako ebifunvu okukyetooloola.  
\v 5 Ekibuga ne bakizimbako ebifunvu okutuusa mu mwaka ogw’ekkumi n’ogumu ogw’obufuzi bwa kabaka Zeddekiya. 
\p  
\v 6 Ku lunaku olw’omwenda olw’omwezi ogwokuna enjala n’eba nnyingi nnyo mu kibuga nga tewaali kyakulya.  
\v 7 Bbugwe w’ekibuga yamenyebwa Abakaludaaya. Eggye lyonna erya Yerusaalemi ne lidduka okuva mu kibuga kiro nga bayita mu mulyango oguli wakati w’ebisenge ebibiri ebiri okumpi n’ennimiro lwa kabaka, newaakubadde ng’Abakaludaaya baali beetoolodde ekibuga. Badduka ne bagenda mu Alaba.  
\v 8 Eggye ly’Abakaludaaya ne ligoba kabaka Zeddekiya ne bamukwatira mu nsenyi ez’e Yeriko, Abaserikale be bonna ne bamuvaako ne basaasaana.  
\v 9 N’akwatibwa. 
\p Zeddekiya n’atwalibwa eri kabaka w’e Babulooni e Libuna mu nsi ey’e Kamasi; n’amusalira omusango ne gumusinga.  
\v 10 Awo kabaka w’e Babulooni n’atta batabani ba Zeddekiya nga kitaabwe alaba; n’atta n’abakungu bonna aba Yuda.  
\v 11 N’alyoka aggyamu Zeddekiya amaaso n’amusiba mu masamba ag’ebikomo n’amutwala e Babulooni, gye yamuteeka mu kkomera okutuusa lwe yafa. 
\p  
\v 12 Ku lunaku olw’ekkumi olw’omwezi ogwokutaano, mu mwaka ogw’ekkumi ogw’obufuzi bwa Nebukadduneeza kabaka w’e Babulooni, Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’eggye erikuuma kabaka, eyaweerezanga kabaka w’e Babulooni, yajja e Yerusaalemi.  
\v 13 Nebukadduneeza n’ayokya yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd* n’olubiri lwa kabaka, n’ennyumba zonna eza Yerusaalemi. Buli kizimbe kyonna eky’omugaso n’akyokya.  
\v 14 Eggye lya Babulooni lyonna eryali liduumirwa omuduumizi w’abakuumi bakabaka ne limenyera ddala ebisenge bya Yerusaalemi.  
\v 15 Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’abakuumi n’atwala abamu ku baavu ennyo n’abo abaasigala mu kibuga, awamu n’abaweesi n’abaali beewaddeyo, mu buwaŋŋanguse eri kabaka w’e Babulooni.  
\v 16 Naye Nebuzaladaani n’asigazaayo abamu ku baavu ennyo mu ggwanga okulabiriranga emizabbibu n’okulimanga. 
\p  
\v 17 Abakaludaaya ne bamenya empagi ez’ebikomo, n’ebikondo ebyali biseetulwa, n’Ennyanja ey’ekikomo, ebyali mu nnyumba ya \nd Mukama\nd* ne batwala ekikomo kyonna e Babulooni.  
\v 18 Ne batwala n’entamu, n’ebisena, n’ebisalako ebisirinza, n’ebibya, n’ebijiiko, n’ebintu byonna eby’ekikomo ebyakozesebwanga mu kuweereza mu Yeekaalu.  
\v 19 Omuduumizi w’abakuumi ba kabaka n’atwala ebensani n’ebibya by’obubaane, n’ebijiiko, n’ebikondo bye ttaala, n’ebibya, n’entamu ebikozesebwa mu kiweebwayo ekyokunywa, byonna ebyali byakolebwa mu zaabu ne ffeeza. 
\p  
\v 20 Ekikomo okuva ku mpagi ebbiri, n’Ennyanja, n’ennume ekkumi n’ebbiri ez’ebikomo wansi waayo, n’ebikondo kabaka Sulemaani bye yali akoledde yeekaalu ya \nd Mukama\nd*, byali bizito nnyo ebitapimika.  
\v 21 Buli emu ku mpagi yali obuwanvu mita munaana ne desimoolo emu; n’obwetoolovu mita ttaano ne desimoolo nnya; n’omubiri gwayo gwali nga sentimita musanvu nga yamuwuluka.  
\v 22 Yaliko n’omutwe gw’ekikomo, n’omutwe gumu ng’obuwanvu bwayo nga mita bbiri ne desimoolo ssatu, omutwe nga guliko ebitimbe n’amakomamawanga enjuuyi zonna, byonna nga bya bikomo; empagi eyookubiri nayo yaliko ebifaanana ebyo n’amakomamawanga.  
\v 23 Mu buli mbiriizi za buli mpagi kwaliko amakomamawanga kyenda mu mukaaga era gonna awamu okwetooloola empagi gaali amakomamawanga kikumi. 
\p  
\v 24 Omuduumizi w’abakuumi n’atwala Seraaya kabona asinga obukulu ne Sefaniya kabona owookubiri n’abaggazi abasatu nga basibe.  
\v 25 Abo abaali bakyali mu kibuga, n’atwalako omukungu akulira eggye, n’abawi b’amagezi omusanvu. N’atwala n’omuwandiisi eyali omukungu omukulu avunaanyizibwa okuwandiika abayingira mu magye ne basajja be nkaaga abaasangibwa mu kibuga.  
\v 26 Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi n’abatwala bonna n’abaleeta eri kabaka w’e Babulooni e Libuna.  
\v 27 Kabaka n’abattira eyo e Libuna, mu Kamasi. 
\p Bw’atyo Yuda n’awaŋŋangusibwa, okuva mu nsi ya boobwe. 
\b  
\li4  
\v 28 Buno bwe bungi bw’abantu Nebukadduneeza be yatwala mu buwaŋŋanguse: 
\b  
\li1 mu mwaka ogw’omusanvu ogw’obufuzi bwe: 
\li2 Abayudaaya enkumi ssatu mu amakumi abiri mu basatu; 
\li1  
\v 29 mu mwaka ogw’omunaana ogwa Nebukadduneeza, 
\li2 n’atwala lunaana mu asatu mu babiri okuva e Yerusaalemi; 
\li1  
\v 30 mu mwaka gwe ogw’amakumi abiri mu esatu, 
\li2 Abayudaaya lusanvu mu ana mu bataano be baatwalibwa Nebuzaladaani omuduumizi w’abakuumi wa kabaka. 
\b  
\li4 Bonna awamu ne baba abantu enkumi nnya mu lukaaga. 
\s1 Yekoyakini Asumululwa 
\p  
\v 31 Awo mu mwaka ogw’amakumi asatu mu omusanvu ogw’okusibibwa kwa Yekoyakini kabaka wa Yuda, mu mwaka Evirumerodaki lwe yafuuka kabaka w’e Babulooni, n’ata Yekoyakini kabaka wa Yuda, n’amuggya mu kkomera ku lunaku olw’amakumi abiri mu etaano olw’omwezi ogw’ekkumi n’ebiri.  
\v 32 N’ayogera naye n’ekisa n’amuwa entebe ey’ekitiibwa eya waggulu okusinga eza bakabaka abalala abaali naye e Babulooni.  
\v 33 Yekoyakini n’akyusa okuva mu ngoye ez’ekkomera era obulamu bwe obusembayo n’aliranga ku mmeeza ya kabaka.  
\v 34 Era kabaka w’e Babulooni yawanga Yekoyakini ensako eya buli lunaku, obulamu bwe bwonna okutuusa lwe yafa.